window.KINMUKU_DATA = {"meta":{"title":"金無垢","romaji":"KINMUKU","tagline_en":"Pure gold, untainted — the Night Parade of Edo","tagline_cn":"純金無瑕 — 江戶百鬼夜行","part_en":"Part One — The Night Parade","part_cn":"第一部｜百鬼夜行"},"characters":[{"id":"01","kanji":"赤座玄鬼","romaji":"Akaza Genki","species_cn":"鬼","species_en":"Oni","archetype_cn":"重力型","archetype_en":"Gravity","archetypeKey":"gravity","color":"#8b2f28","color2":"#c0453b","priority":"T0","active":true,"roleline":"Male lead · walks at the head of the Night Parade","sections":[{"cn":"基本資料","en":"Basic Information","pairs":[{"cn":"全名：赤座玄鬼（あかざ げんき），日文羅馬拼音 Akaza Genki，行文中稱「玄鬼」。","en":"Full name: Akaza Genki (赤座玄鬼); referred to as \"Genki\" in running text.","proposal":false},{"cn":"物種：鬼（Oni）。","en":"Species: oni.","proposal":false},{"cn":"原型分類：重力型（Gravity）。","en":"Archetype: Gravity type.","proposal":false},{"cn":"角色定位：男主角，百鬼夜行的隊首。","en":"Role: male lead; walks at the head of the Night Parade.","proposal":false},{"cn":"首次登場：序章｜夜行之常，於百鬼夜行行進之中，面對一名不畏懼他的孩童而遲疑半拍。","en":"First appearance: Prologue — The Way of the Night Parade, marching at the head of the Night Parade, hesitating a half-beat before a child's unafraid gaze.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第一部結局狀態：所有其他角色皆已離開後，獨自留守江戶橋頭多年，最終走入金寂——是全書中最後離開的角色。","en":"Status at end of Part One: remains alone as bridge-keeper of Edo for years after everyone else has departed, then finally crosses into Golden Stillness — the very last character to leave.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"名字由來","en":"Name Etymology","pairs":[{"cn":"「赤座」意為「血紅之座」，指被定義為惡的那個位置——他是被安置在惡之座上的存在。","en":"\"Akaza\" (赤座) means \"the seat of blood-red\" — the one seated in the place defined as evil.","proposal":false},{"cn":"「玄鬼」意為「深不可測的鬼」，暗示他遠比夜行賦予他的角色更深邃、更難測度。","en":"\"Genki\" (玄鬼) means \"the unfathomable oni\" — hinting he is far deeper and harder to gauge than the role the Parade assigns him.","proposal":false},{"cn":"名字整體暗示：他是一個被放在「惡的位置」上、卻本質深不可測的存在——這正是他第一部故事線的核心張力。","en":"Together, the name signals a being placed in \"evil's seat\" whose true nature is unfathomable — the central tension of his Part One arc.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"氣質與性格","en":"Temperament & Personality","pairs":[{"cn":"氣質：沉重、寡言。","en":"Temperament: heavy, taciturn.","proposal":false},{"cn":"他的沉默不是空白，而是長期承擔的重量所致——話語對他而言是稀缺且昂貴的東西。","en":"His silence is not emptiness but the weight of long-term bearing — words are scarce and costly to him.","proposal":false},{"cn":"他厭倦「定義別人」，這份厭倦是他一切行動的起點，而非一時的情緒。","en":"He is weary of \"defining others\" — that weariness is the starting point of everything he does, not a passing mood.","proposal":false},{"cn":"面對質疑與攻擊，他的第一反應始終是承受，而非反擊——這既是他的修行，也是他最深的本能。","en":"Faced with doubt or attack, his first instinct is always to bear it rather than strike back — both his Practice and his deepest instinct.","proposal":false},{"cn":"他給予他人的從不是命令，而是選擇——這使他在夜行的階序裡顯得格格不入。","en":"What he offers others is never command but choice — which makes him feel out of place within the Parade's hierarchy.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"外貌與視覺設計","en":"Appearance & Visual Design","pairs":[{"cn":"身形高如城門，肩寬背直，步伐沉重。","en":"Tall as a gate; broad shoulders, straight back, a heavy stride.","proposal":false},{"cn":"站姿如石像般筆直，不是武士的姿態。","en":"The straightness of a stone statue, not a samurai's bearing.","proposal":false},{"cn":"雙角內斂，如同從眉骨生出的兩道陰影。","en":"His horns are understated, like two shadows grown from the brow.","proposal":false},{"cn":"皮膚呈暗紅色，如同被燒過又冷卻的鐵。","en":"Dark-red skin, like iron burned and then cooled.","proposal":false},{"cn":"身披深色布袍，袍上蒙著一層說不清的灰霧。","en":"He wears a dark cloth robe, dusted with something indistinct.","proposal":false},{"cn":"不著鎧甲，卻比鎧甲更難以靠近。","en":"He wears no armor, yet is harder to approach than armor.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第十三章終局異變：雙角漸淡，赤色漸退，「幾乎像個普通人」，而後化為金光。","en":"Chapter 13 end-state transformation: his horns fade, the red recedes, \"almost like an ordinary man\" — then he becomes golden light.","proposal":false},{"cn":"色彩指定：氧化鐵紅、炭黑、灰燼灰為主色調；金色僅從第十一章起緩緩進入他的視覺語彙。","en":"Color direction: oxidized iron red, charcoal, and ash grey as the dominant palette; gold enters his visual vocabulary only from Chapter 11 onward.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"背景與象徵","en":"Background & Symbolism","pairs":[{"cn":"玄鬼的功能是走在百鬼夜行的最前方，作為江戶將其命名之惡傾注而入的容器。","en":"Genki's function is to walk at the head of the Night Parade, the vessel into which Edo pours its named evil.","proposal":false},{"cn":"他面對一名孩童不畏懼的注視時，出現了半拍的遲疑——這個「錯誤」是全書故事的起點。","en":"His half-beat hesitation before a child's unafraid gaze is the \"error\" that sets the entire story in motion.","proposal":false},{"cn":"序章中，他選擇遲疑並收回那一步。","en":"In the Prologue, he hesitates and withdraws the step.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第一章，他明確選擇了退開——「舉起手是本能，收回是選擇」——夜行在無他的情況下繼續前行，留下他「不被需要」的空虛。","en":"In Chapter 1, he chooses withdrawal outright — \"lifting the hand is instinct; drawing it back is choice\" — and the Parade moves on without him, leaving the emptiness of being unneeded.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第二章，他拒絕吞下剩餘的恐懼，轉而將其消解——「我沒有替他們承擔——我只是不讓它成形。」","en":"In Chapter 2, he refuses to swallow the leftover fear; instead he unforms it — \"I did not bear it for them — I kept it from taking shape.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"他的存在象徵一種「被放在惡之座卻拒絕成為惡之定義者」的悖論——這正是整部作品修行主題的化身。","en":"His existence symbolizes the paradox of one seated in evil's place who refuses to become evil's definer — the living embodiment of the work's Practice theme.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"第一部故事線","en":"Part One Story Arc","pairs":[{"cn":"序章：面對孩童不畏懼的注視，玄鬼遲疑，收回抬起的手。","en":"Prologue: facing the child's unafraid gaze, Genki hesitates and withdraws his raised hand.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第一章：他選擇退開——「舉起手是本能；收回是選擇」——夜行無他而行，他嚐到不被需要的空虛。","en":"Chapter 1: he chooses withdrawal — \"lifting the hand is instinct; drawing it back is choice\" — the Parade moves on without him, and he tastes the emptiness of being unneeded.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第二章：他拒絕吞下遺留的恐懼，而是將其消解——「我沒有替他們承擔——我只是不讓它成形。」","en":"Chapter 2: he refuses to swallow the leftover fear, choosing instead to unform it — \"I did not bear it for them — I kept it from taking shape.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"第三章：面對烏嶽的審判，他誠實答以動機為「厭倦」；並說「那就讓它崩」；隨後向白蓮詢問何謂修行。","en":"Chapter 3: before Ugaku's judgment he answers honestly that his motive is weariness; he says \"Then let it collapse,\" then asks Byakuren what the Practice is.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第四章：他站在暴民與碧吉之間，不出手攻擊，只是讓人們看見自己的恐懼；並說「我厭倦定義別人。」","en":"Chapter 4: he stands between the mob and Aokichi without attacking, letting people see their own fear; he says, \"I am weary of defining others.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"第五章：碧吉被夜行命名圍攻時，玄鬼選擇將命名的陰影從他身上撕下，而非代為吞下——比承擔更痛。","en":"Chapter 5: when Aokichi is swarmed by the Naming, Genki tears the naming-shadows off him rather than swallowing them himself — more painful than bearing.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第六章：他目睹炎馬以空洞的雙眼吞下恐懼，體悟到整個舊秩序本身也已疲憊。","en":"Chapter 6: he witnesses Enma swallow fear with empty eyes and realizes the old regime itself is weary.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第七章：他承受義牙的攻擊而不還手，並將「選擇」這個難以承受的詞語交給義牙。","en":"Chapter 7: he absorbs Giga's blows without striking back, offering him the unbearable word \"choice.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"第八章：他給予綾女承認而不加定義——「你的怨，不是錯。」「若你不憤怒，你仍然存在。」","en":"Chapter 8: he gives Ayame acknowledgment without definition — \"Your resentment is not wrong.\" \"If you are not angry, you still exist.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"第九章：他接受白嶺提出的賭注——若他成功，多數妖怪將失去存在的理由；他答「若消失是代價，那我會最後一個。」","en":"Chapter 9: he accepts Hakurei's stakes — if he succeeds, most yokai will lose their reason to exist; he answers, \"If disappearance is the price, then I will be the last.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"第十章：他與夜行的集體意識正面相對，不否認它——「你是結果。但不是唯一的結果。」","en":"Chapter 10: face-to-face with the Parade's collective mind, he does not deny it — \"You are a result. But not the only result.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"第十一章：他請白蓮提醒全城「承認，不是爆發」；並目睹綾女的離去。","en":"Chapter 11: he asks Byakuren to remind the city that \"acknowledgment, not eruption\" is the way; he witnesses Ayame's departure.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第十二章：他接受眾王提出的條件；最後一波大規模命名匯聚於他；他站在火中，既不吞下也不反擊——以承認的方式承擔。","en":"Chapter 12: he accepts the kings' terms; the final mass Naming converges on him; he stands in the fire, neither swallowing nor pushing back — bearing through acknowledgment.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第十三章：眾人皆離去後，他成為江戶的守橋人多年；對碧吉留下最後一句「不。我只是晚一點。」最終走入金寂，橋頭空無一人。","en":"Chapter 13: after everyone else departs, he becomes Edo's bridge-keeper for years; his last words to Aokichi are, \"No. I am only later.\" He finally crosses into Golden Stillness, leaving the bridge empty.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"人物關係","en":"Relationships","pairs":[{"cn":"那名孩童——他第一個接收到的無懼注視，是整個故事的催化劑。","en":"The child — the first unafraid gaze he receives, the catalyst for the entire story.","proposal":false},{"cn":"九條白蓮——從觀察者，到引路人，到某種無法言說的存在；她是倒數第二個離開的人。","en":"Kujō Byakuren — observer, then guide, then something wordless; she is the second-to-last to depart.","proposal":false},{"cn":"碧吉——他的第一個追隨者；玄鬼搭在他肩上的手，是玄鬼第一次「支持」而非「命令」的舉動。","en":"Aokichi — his first follower; Genki's hand on his shoulder is Genki's first act of support rather than command.","proposal":false},{"cn":"黑緣——她的「被拋棄」與玄鬼的處境彼此共鳴。","en":"Kuroberi — her experience of abandonment resonates with Genki's own.","proposal":false},{"cn":"綾女——玄鬼給她的證明是修行第一次真正解放一個人的證據。","en":"Ayame — his first proof that the Practice can truly free someone.","proposal":false},{"cn":"大江炎馬——他的鏡像：另一個同樣疲憊的承擔者。","en":"Ōe Enma — his mirror: the other weary bearer.","proposal":false},{"cn":"茨木義牙——那份考驗他的忠誠。","en":"Ibaraki Giga — the loyalty that tests him.","proposal":false},{"cn":"鞍馬烏嶽與鞍馬白嶺——審判他的人。","en":"Kurama Ugaku and Kurama Hakurei — the judges who weigh him.","proposal":false},{"cn":"百鬼夜行本身——他自己過去的樣子，被外化為一個群體意識。","en":"The Night Parade itself — his own past self, externalized as a collective mind.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"關鍵台詞","en":"Key Lines","pairs":[{"cn":"「我沒有替他們承擔。」","en":"\"I did not bear it for them.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「那就讓它崩。」","en":"\"Then let it collapse.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「我厭倦定義別人。」","en":"\"I am weary of defining others.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「你的怨，不是錯。」","en":"\"Your resentment is not wrong.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「若消失是代價，那我會最後一個。」","en":"\"If disappearance is the price, then I will be the last.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「有人必須留下。」","en":"\"Someone must remain.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「不。我只是晚一點。」","en":"\"No. I am only later.\"","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"聲音與表演備註","en":"Voice & Performance Notes","pairs":[{"cn":"嗓音低沉、緩慢，話語間留有長停頓。","en":"Voice: low, slow, with long pauses between words.","proposal":true},{"cn":"語調幾乎沒有上揚，直到第十三章那唯一一次笑聲才出現變化。","en":"Almost no rising intonation, until the single laugh in Chapter 13 breaks the pattern.","proposal":true},{"cn":"表演基調應是「重量感先於情緒」——他的情緒藏在停頓與呼吸裡，而非臉部表情的劇烈變化。","en":"Performance baseline: weight precedes emotion — his feelings live in pauses and breath rather than in dramatic facial shifts.","proposal":true},{"cn":"肢體動作應保持石像般的穩定，即使承受攻擊(如第七章義牙的拳頭)，身體也不應大幅晃動。","en":"Physicality should stay statue-still; even under attack (e.g. Giga's fists in Chapter 7), his body should not sway dramatically.","proposal":true},{"cn":"第十三章的笑聲是全劇唯一一次，應設計為短促、近乎意外於自己會笑的音色。","en":"The Chapter 13 laugh is the only one in the whole work; it should be brief, almost surprised at itself.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"未來發展掛鉤","en":"Future Hooks","pairs":[{"cn":"玄鬼在江戶橋頭獨自守候多年的空白歲月，可作為第二部前傳短篇的素材，描繪「最後一人」的日常。","en":"The blank years Genki spends alone as bridge-keeper of Edo could seed a Part Two prequel short depicting the daily life of \"the last one remaining.\"","proposal":true},{"cn":"他與大江炎馬「兩個疲憊承擔者」的鏡像關係，可延伸為描寫舊秩序崩解前夕的支線。","en":"His mirror relationship with Ōe Enma as \"two weary bearers\" could be expanded into a side story set on the eve of the old order's collapse.","proposal":true},{"cn":"金寂彼岸的樣貌從未直接展示，玄鬼作為最後跨越者，是揭示「彼岸」視覺設計的最佳切入角色。","en":"The far shore of Golden Stillness is never directly shown; as the last to cross, Genki is the ideal character through whom to finally reveal its visual design.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"製作資產清單","en":"Production Asset Checklist","pairs":[{"cn":"概念設定圖：需呈現赤紅鐵鏽膚色與內斂雙角的最終定裝，含第十三章角色褪色前後的雙版本。","en":"Concept art: final design showing the iron-red skin and understated horns, including before/after versions of the Chapter 13 fading transformation.","proposal":false},{"cn":"三視圖：需標示「城門般高大」的比例基準，肩寬背直的骨架線條。","en":"Character turnaround: must establish scale against the \"tall as a gate\" reference, with straight-backed, broad-shouldered skeletal lines.","proposal":false},{"cn":"表情表：重點在極簡表情下的細微差異——尤其是承受攻擊與給予承認時的眼神差異。","en":"Expression sheet: focus on subtle variation within a minimalist range — especially the difference between his eyes under attack versus giving acknowledgment.","proposal":false},{"cn":"服裝道具表：深色布袍及其「說不清的灰霧」質感，需明確不可與鎧甲混淆。","en":"Costume & prop sheet: the dark robe and its \"indistinct dust\" texture, explicitly distinct from armor.","proposal":false},{"cn":"色彩指定：氧化鐵紅、炭黑、灰燼灰為基礎，金色僅自第十一章起漸次滲入。","en":"Color script: oxidized iron red, charcoal, and ash grey as the base, with gold gradually introduced only from Chapter 11.","proposal":false},{"cn":"動態參考：步伐沉重卻不遲緩的走路節奏，以及石像般靜止的站姿參考。","en":"Motion reference: a heavy but unhurried walking cadence, plus reference for his stone-statue-still standing pose.","proposal":false},{"cn":"聲優試音方向：低音域、長停頓、極少音調起伏，第十三章需保留一次意外的輕笑。","en":"VO casting direction: low register, long pauses, minimal pitch variation, reserving one unexpected soft laugh for Chapter 13.","proposal":true},{"cn":"分集出場表：序章至第十三章全數在場，為第一部出場密度最高的角色。","en":"Episode appearance list: present from the Prologue through Chapter 13 — the highest appearance density of any character in Part One.","proposal":false}]}]},{"id":"02","kanji":"九條白蓮","romaji":"Kujō Byakuren","species_cn":"九尾狐","species_en":"Nine-tailed fox","archetype_cn":"理性型","archetype_en":"Reason","archetypeKey":"reason","color":"#4f7398","color2":"#9cc0e0","priority":"T0","active":true,"roleline":"Female lead · the Observer who names the rules","sections":[{"cn":"基本資料","en":"Basic Information","pairs":[{"cn":"全名：九條白蓮（くじょう びゃくれん），日文羅馬拼音 Kujō Byakuren，行文中稱「白蓮」。","en":"Full name: Kujō Byakuren (九條白蓮); referred to as \"Byakuren\" in running text.","proposal":false},{"cn":"物種：九尾狐（kyūbi no kitsune）。","en":"Species: nine-tailed fox (kyūbi no kitsune).","proposal":false},{"cn":"原型分類：理性型（Reason）。","en":"Archetype: Reason type.","proposal":false},{"cn":"角色定位：女主角，夜行的觀察者與規則命名者。","en":"Role: female lead; the Observer and rule-namer of the Night Parade.","proposal":false},{"cn":"首次登場：序章｜夜行之常，站在屋脊陰影中，指出「錯誤，出現了」。","en":"First appearance: Prologue — The Way of the Night Parade, standing in roof-ridge shadow, pronouncing, \"An error has appeared.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"第一部結局狀態：走入金光之中，先玄鬼一步離去——是全書倒數第二個離開的角色。","en":"Status at end of Part One: walks into the golden light ahead of Genki — the second-to-last character to depart in the entire work.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"名字由來","en":"Name Etymology","pairs":[{"cn":"「九條」是古代貴族姓氏，暗示她出身高貴、疏離於凡俗秩序之外。","en":"\"Kujō\" (九條) is an old aristocratic surname, hinting at noble origin and detachment from ordinary order.","proposal":false},{"cn":"「白蓮」意為「潔白之蓮」，象徵不染塵埃——與她所追尋的「無垢界」概念直接呼應。","en":"\"Byakuren\" (白蓮) means \"white lotus, unstained\" — a direct echo of the Immaculate Realm she seeks.","proposal":false},{"cn":"姓名整體構成一種矛盾：貴族血統的疏離與蓮花般的潔淨理想，共同定義她「觀察而不涉入」的位置。","en":"Together the name forms a paradox: aristocratic detachment paired with lotus-like purity, defining her stance of observing without intervening.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"氣質與性格","en":"Temperament & Personality","pairs":[{"cn":"氣質：優雅、理性、疏離。","en":"Temperament: elegant, rational, detached.","proposal":false},{"cn":"她將「觀察」視為自己唯一不會被奪走的權利，理性是她保護自己的方式。","en":"She treats observation as the one right that can never be taken from her — reason is her means of self-protection.","proposal":false},{"cn":"她的疏離並非冷漠，而是源於過去一次錯誤所付出的代價——她曾相信引導恐懼能穩定世界。","en":"Her detachment is not coldness but the cost of a past error — she once believed that directing fear could stabilize the world.","proposal":false},{"cn":"她是全書中唯一聽起來會「感到有趣」的角色，理性之下藏著細微的幽默感。","en":"She is the only character who ever sounds amused — a fine thread of humor beneath the reason.","proposal":false},{"cn":"隨著故事推進，她冷靜的觀察逐漸出現動搖，顯示她並非真正無涉其中。","en":"As the story progresses, her cool observation begins to waver, revealing she was never truly uninvolved.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"外貌與視覺設計","en":"Appearance & Visual Design","pairs":[{"cn":"站立於屋脊陰影之中，衣袖靜止不動。","en":"She stands in roof-ridge shadow, her sleeves unmoving.","proposal":false},{"cn":"長髮如墨水般垂流而下。","en":"Long hair flows down like ink-water.","proposal":false},{"cn":"月光似乎刻意避開落在她身上。","en":"Moonlight seems to avoid falling on her.","proposal":false},{"cn":"雙眼如兩片薄冰。","en":"Her eyes are like two slivers of thin ice.","proposal":false},{"cn":"步下月光時，彷彿踩著隱形的階梯。","en":"She steps down moonlight as if descending invisible stairs.","proposal":false},{"cn":"木屐無聲。","en":"Her clogs make no sound.","proposal":false},{"cn":"九尾始終只以陰影形式出現，從未直接顯現實體。","en":"Her nine tails are only ever shown as shadow, never directly revealed.","proposal":false},{"cn":"色彩指定：以白色、月銀、墨黑為主色調，呼應「白蓮」與月光意象。","en":"Color direction: white, moon-silver, and ink black as the dominant palette, echoing the \"white lotus\" and moonlight imagery.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"背景與象徵","en":"Background & Symbolism","pairs":[{"cn":"她掌握全書兩個核心關鍵詞：「無垢界」與「金寂」。","en":"She holds the two key words of the entire work: the Immaculate Realm and Golden Stillness.","proposal":false},{"cn":"她依玄鬼逐步領悟修行而宣告修行八條的內容。","en":"She pronounces the Eight Precepts one by one, as Genki earns them.","proposal":false},{"cn":"她過去的錯誤是全書公認的正史：她曾相信引導恐懼能穩定世界，而玉藻静香正是那套安排的重大失敗案例。","en":"Her past error is established canon: she once believed directing fear could stabilize the world, and Tamamo Shizuka was that arrangement's great failure.","proposal":false},{"cn":"那套舊方法的本質是「將罪推到一個名字上，好讓所有人得以繼續假裝清白」。","en":"The essence of that old method was to \"push the sin onto one name, so that everyone may keep pretending innocence.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"她的存在象徵理性主義式的救贖嘗試，以及該嘗試失敗後所背負的責任與重新學習。","en":"She embodies a rationalist attempt at salvation, and the responsibility and relearning she carries after that attempt failed.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"第一部故事線","en":"Part One Story Arc","pairs":[{"cn":"序章：她指出「錯誤，出現了」，標記玄鬼那半拍遲疑的意義。","en":"Prologue: she declares, \"An error has appeared,\" marking the significance of Genki's half-beat hesitation.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第一章：她確認法則——「若你不再承擔，他們就會更用力地把它塞進你裡面」——並計算追隨者的數目。","en":"Chapter 1: she confirms the law — \"If you no longer bear it, they will force it into you harder\" — and counts the followers.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第三章：她向玄鬼定義修行——「修行，是讓自己在不被需要的時候，仍然存在。」","en":"Chapter 3: she defines the Practice to Genki — \"The Practice is learning to still exist when you are no longer needed.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"第八至九章：她一貫冷靜的觀察開始動搖；她向白嶺道出他真正恐懼的事物。","en":"Chapters 8–9: her habitually cool observation begins to waver; she tells Hakurei what he truly fears.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第十一章：她的聲音穿透每一戶人家——「你們可以看見。你們可以承認。」","en":"Chapter 11: her voice threads through every house — \"You may see. You may acknowledge.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"第十二章：她宣告修行第八條——不怨。","en":"Chapter 12: she names the Eighth Precept — Do not resent.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第十三章：她與玄鬼有最後一次對話——「無垢界在彼岸。但彼岸不在遠方。」隨後在他面前走入金光之中，未道別。","en":"Chapter 13: her last exchange with Genki — \"The Immaculate Realm lies on the far shore. But the far shore is not far away.\" She then walks into the golden light before him, without saying goodbye.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"人物關係","en":"Relationships","pairs":[{"cn":"赤座玄鬼——她所等待的那個「錯誤」，也是她最終與之同行的道路。","en":"Akaza Genki — the \"error\" she has been waiting for, and ultimately the road she walks alongside.","proposal":false},{"cn":"玉藻静香——她深埋的失敗，也是前傳故事的伏筆。","en":"Tamamo Shizuka — her buried failure, and a hook for prequel material.","proposal":false},{"cn":"眾王(炎馬、義牙、烏嶽、白嶺等)——彼此相互承認，但無從屬關係。","en":"The kings (Enma, Giga, Ugaku, Hakurei, etc.) — mutual recognition between them, but no allegiance.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"關鍵台詞","en":"Key Lines","pairs":[{"cn":"「觀察，是我唯一不會被奪走的權利。」","en":"\"Observation is the one right that can never be taken from me.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「錯誤，出現了。」","en":"\"An error has appeared.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「世界需要鬼。因為世界需要一個能承擔『惡』的容器。」","en":"\"The world needs an oni. Because the world needs a vessel that can bear 'evil.'\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「修行，是讓自己在不被需要的時候，仍然存在。」","en":"\"The Practice is learning to still exist when you are no longer needed.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「金寂不是逃離。是純淨。」","en":"\"Golden Stillness is not escape. It is purity.\"","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"聲音與表演備註","en":"Voice & Performance Notes","pairs":[{"cn":"嗓音應安靜、精準，語速從不倉促。","en":"Voice: quiet, precise, never hurried.","proposal":true},{"cn":"她是全劇唯一聽起來會感到「有趣」的角色，語氣中應保留一絲若隱若現的幽默。","en":"As the only character who ever sounds amused, her tone should carry a faint, barely-there thread of humor.","proposal":true},{"cn":"肢體語言應強調「無聲」——木屐無聲、衣袖不動，任何動作都應如踏在看不見的階梯上般精確。","en":"Physicality should emphasize silence — soundless clogs, unmoving sleeves — every motion as precise as stepping on invisible stairs.","proposal":true},{"cn":"第八至九章動搖的表演需極度克制，僅以極細微的停頓或眼神偏移暗示裂縫，不可外顯激動。","en":"Her wavering in Chapters 8–9 should be performed with extreme restraint — only the faintest pause or shift of gaze hinting at the crack, never visible agitation.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"未來發展掛鉤","en":"Future Hooks","pairs":[{"cn":"白蓮與玉藻静香的前傳篇章，可揭示無垢界理念誕生的完整過程，以及静香「退場」究竟去向何方的懸念。","en":"A Byakuren × Tamamo Shizuka prequel episode could reveal the full origin of the Immaculate Realm concept, and resolve the open mystery of where Shizuka's \"exit\" actually led.","proposal":true},{"cn":"她與眾王「相互承認，無從屬」的關係，可延伸描寫她在舊秩序中的真實地位與過去權力結構。","en":"Her relationship of \"mutual recognition, no allegiance\" with the kings could be expanded to depict her true standing and past power structure within the old order.","proposal":true},{"cn":"無垢界彼岸的具體樣貌從未展示，白蓮作為率先抵達者，適合作為第二部揭曉彼岸視覺設計的引路角色。","en":"The far shore of the Immaculate Realm has never been shown on page; as the first of the two leads to arrive, Byakuren is well-suited to guide its visual reveal in Part Two.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"製作資產清單","en":"Production Asset Checklist","pairs":[{"cn":"概念設定圖：需捕捉「月光避開她」的獨特光影效果與屋脊陰影中的站姿。","en":"Concept art: must capture the distinctive lighting effect of \"moonlight avoiding her\" and her stance within roof-ridge shadow.","proposal":false},{"cn":"三視圖：需標示墨水般垂流長髮的動態範圍，以及九尾陰影的隱藏比例基準。","en":"Character turnaround: must define the dynamic range of ink-flowing long hair and the hidden proportion baseline for her shadow-only nine tails.","proposal":false},{"cn":"表情表：重點在薄冰般雙眼下的極細微裂縫——尤其第八至九章動搖時刻的眼神變化。","en":"Expression sheet: focus on hairline cracks beneath her thin-ice eyes — especially the shift in gaze during her Chapter 8–9 wavering.","proposal":false},{"cn":"服裝道具表：衣袖與無聲木屐的材質設定，需明確標示衣袖「靜止不動」的視覺規則。","en":"Costume & prop sheet: material specs for her sleeves and soundless clogs, explicitly noting the visual rule that her sleeves remain motionless.","proposal":false},{"cn":"色彩指定：白色、月銀、墨黑為基礎，九尾僅以陰影形式呈現，不使用實體色彩。","en":"Color script: white, moon-silver, and ink black as the base; the nine tails appear only as shadow, never in solid color.","proposal":false},{"cn":"動態參考：「步下月光如踩隱形階梯」的移動方式，需獨立於一般行走參考另行設計。","en":"Motion reference: her \"stepping down moonlight as if on invisible stairs\" movement style, to be designed separately from standard walking reference.","proposal":false},{"cn":"聲優試音方向：安靜精準，語速平穩，需保留全劇唯一「聽得出來的一絲趣味」的語氣層次。","en":"VO casting direction: quiet and precise, steady pacing, retaining the one audible thread of amusement unique to her among the whole cast.","proposal":true},{"cn":"分集出場表：序章、第一、三、八、九、十一、十二、十三章在場，出場密度僅次於玄鬼。","en":"Episode appearance list: present in the Prologue and Chapters 1, 3, 8, 9, 11, 12, and 13 — second only to Genki in appearance density.","proposal":false}]}]},{"id":"03","kanji":"大江炎馬","romaji":"Ōe Enma","species_cn":"酒吞童子","species_en":"Shuten-dōji","archetype_cn":"野性型","archetype_en":"Feral","archetypeKey":"feral","color":"#c0682a","color2":"#eb9a44","priority":"T1","active":true,"roleline":"The oldest, weariest king of the Parade","sections":[{"cn":"基本資料","en":"Basic Information","pairs":[{"cn":"全名：大江炎馬（おおえ　えんま），羅馬拼音 Ōe Enma，日常稱呼「炎馬」。","en":"Full name: Ōe Enma (大江炎馬), romanized Ōe Enma; referred to in running text as \"Enma.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"物種：酒吞童子（Shuten-dōji）。","en":"Species: Shuten-dōji.","proposal":false},{"cn":"原型：野性型，夜行最古老的重量之一，秩序方的「王」之一。","en":"Archetype: Feral type; one of the Night Parade's oldest weights, one of the ruling \"kings.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"角色定位：秩序的執行者與示範者，玄鬼疲憊的鏡像。","en":"Role: Enforcer and demonstrator of order; a weary mirror of Genki.","proposal":false},{"cn":"初登場：第六章｜王的視線。","en":"First appearance: Chapter 6 — The King's Gaze.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第一部結局時的狀態：於第十三章說出「夜行，停」，在夜行諸王中第一個離開。","en":"Status at end of Part One: speaks \"The Parade, stop\" in Chapter 13 and is the first among the kings to depart.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"名字由來","en":"Name Etymology","pairs":[{"cn":"「大江」取自大江山傳說之地名。","en":"\"Ōe\" draws on the place-name legend of Mount Ōe.","proposal":false},{"cn":"「炎馬」意為「火焰之馬」，指向火與暴力。","en":"\"Enma\" means \"flame horse,\" pointing to fire and violence.","proposal":false},{"cn":"氣質為「豪放卻空虛」——外顯豪邁，內裡空洞。","en":"Temperament: \"bold and expansive, yet hollow\" — outwardly magnanimous, inwardly empty.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"氣質與性格","en":"Temperament & Personality","pairs":[{"cn":"豪放：以王者之姿現身，不與玄鬼爭辯，只以行動示範。","en":"Expansive: he arrives with a king's bearing, never arguing with Genki — only demonstrating through action.","proposal":false},{"cn":"空虛：吞噬恐懼時眼神空洞，不是權力也不是驕傲，而是長久重複後的疲憊。","en":"Hollow: his eyes go empty as he swallows fear — not power, not pride, but the weariness of long repetition.","proposal":false},{"cn":"對玄鬼的態度不是敵意，而是某種疲憊的共鳴：「你終於說出來了。」","en":"His attitude toward Genki is not hostility but a kind of weary resonance: \"You finally said it.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"說話低沉如酒罈滾動，陳述多於質問，笑聲中帶著某種認可。","en":"He speaks low, like a rolling sake cask; statements more than questions, his laughter carrying a kind of recognition.","proposal":false},{"cn":"對規律的忠誠是一種選擇後的承擔，而非盲目——他知道自己在維持秩序，而非證明善。","en":"His loyalty to the law is a chosen burden, not blindness — he knows he is maintaining order, not proving goodness.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"外貌與視覺設計","en":"Appearance & Visual Design","pairs":[{"cn":"火焰般的長髮垂落肩頭。","en":"Flame-like long hair falls over his shoulders.","proposal":false},{"cn":"身軀魁梧如山石。","en":"His body is massive as mountain rock.","proposal":false},{"cn":"他不是走來——是讓空氣讓開。","en":"He does not walk toward you — the air steps aside.","proposal":false},{"cn":"聲音低沉，像酒罈滾動。","en":"His voice is low, like a rolling sake cask.","proposal":false},{"cn":"吞噬恐懼時，將尚未成形的黑影在手中凝成一顆暗紅色的球體，張口吸入。","en":"When he swallows fear, he condenses the unformed shadow in his hand into a dark-red sphere and draws it in through his open mouth.","proposal":false},{"cn":"色彩指定：餘燼橙、漆黑、酒杯金，用於區分他與玄鬼的「重」色階。","en":"Color script: ember orange, lacquer black, sake-cup gold — distinguishing his register of \"weight\" from Genki's.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"背景與象徵","en":"Background & Symbolism","pairs":[{"cn":"他是夜行最古老的重量之一，象徵秩序內部早已存在的倦意。","en":"He is one of the Night Parade's oldest weights, embodying a weariness that already exists inside the order itself.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第六章他當場示範「你不吞，我來吞」，證明玄鬼若不承擔，會有他人承擔——但這不代表規律正確。","en":"In Chapter 6 he demonstrates on the spot — \"If you won't swallow it, I will\" — proving that if Genki does not bear it, someone else will; but that does not make the law right.","proposal":false},{"cn":"玄鬼看穿他：「他厭倦了。」「他吞下時，沒有喜悅。」——這是第二幕真正的轉折：規律內部本身就有倦意。","en":"Genki sees through him: \"He is weary.\" \"There was no joy when he swallowed it.\" — this is the true turning point of Act Two: weariness already lives inside the law.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第十一章綾女進入金寂時，他第一次真正沉默，隨後低語「原來如此」。","en":"In Chapter 11, when Ayame enters Golden Stillness, he falls truly silent for the first time, then murmurs, \"So that's how it is.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"第十二章他代表夜行諸王前來會面，宣布「我們討論過」，承認修行可以減少夜行的重量。","en":"In Chapter 12 he comes as the kings' representative, announcing \"We have discussed this,\" acknowledging that the Practice can reduce the Parade's weight.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"第一部故事線","en":"Part One Story Arc","pairs":[{"cn":"第六章：夜行提早降臨，炎馬現身橋頭，指出「你讓夜行變慢」；他當場吞下未成形的黑影，證明夜行不需要玄鬼；玄鬼識破他的空洞與疲憊。","en":"Chapter 6: the Parade arrives early; Enma appears at the bridge and states \"You are slowing the Parade down.\" He swallows the unformed shadow himself, proving the Parade does not need Genki; Genki sees through his hollowness and weariness.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第十一章：夜行以全部重量前壓，炎馬步出隊伍要求「現在讓他們承認」；綾女化為金光離開時，他仰頭沉默，只說「原來如此」。","en":"Chapter 11: the Parade presses forward with its full weight; Enma steps out of the ranks demanding \"Now let them acknowledge it.\" When Ayame departs into golden light, he looks up in silence, saying only \"So that's how it is.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"第十二章：炎馬率白嶺、義牙、烏嶽前來會面，帶來夜行諸王的裁定：「你不是王，卻選擇了王的結局。」聽玄鬼確認留到最後後，說「那就開始」。","en":"Chapter 12: Enma arrives with Hakurei, Giga, and Ugaku to deliver the kings' verdict: \"You are not a king, yet you have chosen a king's ending.\" Hearing Genki confirm he will stay until the last, he says, \"Then let it begin.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"第十三章：他在遠處低聲說出「夜行，停」，作為一種確認而非命令；隨後在夜行諸王中第一個離開。","en":"Chapter 13: from a distance he speaks the words \"The Parade, stop\" — not a command but a confirmation — and is the first among the kings to depart.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"人物關係","en":"Relationships","pairs":[{"cn":"與義牙：義牙是他忠誠的爪牙；炎馬的疲憊，正是義牙不敢正視的事。","en":"With Giga: Giga is his devoted fang; Enma's weariness is exactly what Giga cannot afford to see.","proposal":false},{"cn":"與玄鬼：唯一看穿他空洞的存在——玄鬼點出「他厭倦了」，兩人成為彼此的鏡像。","en":"With Genki: the only being who saw his emptiness — Genki names it, \"He is weary,\" and the two become mirrors of each other.","proposal":false},{"cn":"與白嶺：秩序的共同持有者，第十二章一同前來宣告裁定。","en":"With Hakurei: co-holder of order; together they arrive in Chapter 12 to deliver the verdict.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"關鍵台詞","en":"Key Lines","pairs":[{"cn":"「你終於說出來了。」","en":"\"You finally said it.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「你不吞，我來吞。」","en":"\"If you won't swallow it, I will.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「夜行不需要你。」","en":"\"The Parade does not need you.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「原來如此。」","en":"\"So that's how it is.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「你不是王，卻選擇了王的結局。」","en":"\"You are not a king, yet you have chosen a king's ending.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「那就開始。」","en":"\"Then let it begin.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「夜行，停。」","en":"\"The Parade, stop.\"","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"聲音與表演備註","en":"Voice & Performance Notes","pairs":[{"cn":"聲線：宏大、溫暖，底下藏著疲憊；笑聲總在該收的前一拍就停下。","en":"Voice: big and warm, weariness underneath; his laughter stops one beat too early.","proposal":true},{"cn":"節奏：陳述句多於疑問句，語速不急，如同酒罈滾動般帶有重量感。","en":"Pacing: statements outnumber questions; unhurried delivery with the rolling weight of a sake cask.","proposal":true},{"cn":"關鍵情緒轉折：吞噬恐懼那一刻，眼神必須是空的，不能演成享受或得意。","en":"Key emotional beat: in the moment he swallows fear, the eyes must read as empty — never played as enjoyment or triumph.","proposal":true},{"cn":"第十三章「夜行，停」一句需極輕、極低，是確認而非宣告。","en":"The Chapter 13 line \"The Parade, stop\" should be delivered extremely quiet and low — a confirmation, not a proclamation.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"未來發展掛鉤","en":"Future Hooks","pairs":[{"cn":"炎馬作為「最古老的重量」，其成王之前的來歷（大江山時代）可作前傳素材。","en":"As \"one of the oldest weights,\" Enma's history before becoming a king (the Mount Ōe era) could serve as prequel material.","proposal":true},{"cn":"他與義牙的主從情感，可在後續集數延伸為關於「放手」的支線。","en":"His lord-and-retainer bond with Giga could be extended in later episodes into a subplot about \"letting go.\"","proposal":true},{"cn":"他離開後的金寂狀態未在正文詳寫，留白可供後續補完。","en":"His state within Golden Stillness after departure is not detailed on the page — the gap is open for future elaboration.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"製作資產清單","en":"Production Asset Checklist","pairs":[{"cn":"概念設定圖：重點呈現「身軀魁梧如山石」與「讓空氣讓開」的壓迫感。","en":"Concept art: emphasize the \"body massive as mountain rock\" quality and the sense that the air itself steps aside for him.","proposal":false},{"cn":"三視圖：需標示火焰般長髮的垂落走向與肩頸比例。","en":"Character turnaround: mark the flow of the flame-like long hair over the shoulders and the neck-to-shoulder proportions.","proposal":false},{"cn":"表情表：核心表情為「吞噬時的空洞眼神」與「笑聲提前收住的半笑」。","en":"Expression sheet: core expressions are \"the hollow gaze while swallowing\" and the \"half-laugh that cuts off early.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"服裝道具表：包含酒罈意象的配件與王者衣袍的磨損質感。","en":"Costume & prop sheet: include accessories evoking the sake cask motif and a worn, kingly-robe texture.","proposal":false},{"cn":"色彩指定：餘燼橙、漆黑、酒杯金，吞噬恐懼時暗紅色球體為關鍵動畫元素。","en":"Color script: ember orange, lacquer black, sake-cup gold; the dark-red sphere formed when swallowing fear is a key animation element.","proposal":false},{"cn":"動態參考：「不是走來，是讓空氣讓開」的移動方式需要專屬的运镜与运动参考。","en":"Motion reference: his \"does not walk — the air steps aside\" movement needs dedicated camera and motion reference.","proposal":false},{"cn":"聲優試音方向：低沉如滾動酒罈的聲線，需能在陳述句與一拍未盡的笑聲間切換。","en":"VO casting direction: a low voice like a rolling sake cask, able to shift between flat statements and a laugh that stops one beat short.","proposal":false},{"cn":"分集出場表：第六、十一、十二、十三章為必要出場集數。","en":"Episode appearance list: Chapters 6, 11, 12, and 13 are his required appearance episodes.","proposal":false}]}]},{"id":"04","kanji":"茨木義牙","romaji":"Ibaraki Giga","species_cn":"茨木童子","species_en":"Ibaraki-dōji","archetype_cn":"野性型","archetype_en":"Feral","archetypeKey":"feral","color":"#c0682a","color2":"#eb9a44","priority":"T1","active":true,"roleline":"Enma's devoted fang; loyalty on trial","sections":[{"cn":"基本資料","en":"Basic Information","pairs":[{"cn":"全名：茨木義牙（いばらき　ぎが），羅馬拼音 Ibaraki Giga，日常稱呼「義牙」。","en":"Full name: Ibaraki Giga (茨木義牙), romanized Ibaraki Giga; referred to in running text as \"Giga.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"物種：茨木童子（Ibaraki-dōji）。","en":"Species: Ibaraki-dōji.","proposal":false},{"cn":"原型：野性型，炎馬麾下最忠誠的追隨者。","en":"Archetype: Feral type; Enma's most loyal follower.","proposal":false},{"cn":"角色定位：忠誠之牙——以攻擊玄鬼的方式，測試「忠誠」本身的定義。","en":"Role: the fang of loyalty — his assault on Genki becomes a test of what loyalty itself means.","proposal":false},{"cn":"初登場：第七章｜忠誠的牙（核心章節）。","en":"First appearance: Chapter 7 — The Fang of Loyalty (his centerpiece chapter).","proposal":false},{"cn":"第一部結局時的狀態：第十三章垂下頭，理解忠誠即懂得放手，隨後離開。","en":"Status at end of Part One: in Chapter 13 he lowers his head, having understood that loyalty means knowing when to release, then departs.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"名字由來","en":"Name Etymology","pairs":[{"cn":"「義牙」意為「忠義之牙」。","en":"\"Giga\" means \"the fang of loyalty.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"氣質為「衝動忠誠」——行動先於思考，忠誠是他存在的根基。","en":"Temperament: \"impulsive, loyal\" — action precedes thought; loyalty is the foundation of his existence.","proposal":false},{"cn":"物種名「茨木童子」呼應其攻擊時如荊棘般不容退讓的姿態。","en":"The species name \"Ibaraki-dōji\" (\"thorn-tree child\") echoes his thorn-like, unyielding stance in combat.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"氣質與性格","en":"Temperament & Personality","pairs":[{"cn":"步伐走得很直、很快、很不容質疑，性格與此一致。","en":"He walks straight, fast, unquestionable — his character matches his gait.","proposal":false},{"cn":"對炎馬的忠誠近乎信仰，容不下「王也會疲憊」的可能。","en":"His loyalty to Enma is almost a faith; he cannot accommodate the possibility that even a king can grow weary.","proposal":false},{"cn":"憤怒之下是恐懼：若鬼可以拒絕，那義牙整段追隨的歷史可能只是一場漫長的誤解。","en":"Beneath his fury is fear: if the oni may refuse, then his entire history of loyalty might have been one long misunderstanding.","proposal":false},{"cn":"「選擇」二字是他最怕聽見的詞，因為忠誠本身就是放棄選擇。","en":"The word \"choice\" is what he fears most to hear, because loyalty itself is the surrender of choice.","proposal":false},{"cn":"表面強硬，實則第一個在玄鬼面前顯露動搖的追隨者。","en":"Outwardly hard-edged, he is in fact the first follower to show visible wavering in front of Genki.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"外貌與視覺設計","en":"Appearance & Visual Design","pairs":[{"cn":"走路方式與炎馬的沉穩、玄鬼的沉重都不同——直、快、不容質疑。","en":"His way of walking differs from both Enma's steadiness and Genki's heaviness — straight, fast, unquestionable.","proposal":false},{"cn":"眼神像磨亮的刃。","en":"His eyes are like a polished blade.","proposal":false},{"cn":"拳頭能震裂石橋。","en":"His fists can crack stone bridges.","proposal":false},{"cn":"出手分兩階段：先是試探性的拳風，後轉為帶著怒意的全力攻擊。","en":"His attacks unfold in two stages: first a testing blow, then a full-force strike carrying real fury.","proposal":false},{"cn":"色彩指定：荊棘般的墨綠與鋼灰，呼應「牙」與「刃」的意象。","en":"Color script: thorn-like green-black and steel grey, echoing the imagery of \"fang\" and \"blade.\"","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"背景與象徵","en":"Background & Symbolism","pairs":[{"cn":"他象徵「忠誠」本身的重量——忠誠不是溫順，而是放棄選擇後的行動。","en":"He embodies the weight of \"loyalty\" itself — not docility, but action taken after surrendering choice.","proposal":false},{"cn":"他從大江山起便追隨炎馬，歷經無數次夜行，用牙撕裂恐懼、用力氣護住王，從不曾質疑。","en":"He has followed Enma since Mount Ōe, through countless Parades, tearing fear apart with his fangs and shielding his king with his strength — never once questioning.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第七章他指控玄鬼「你讓炎馬大人親自出手」，實為忠誠外殼下的恐懼：怕王動搖、怕夜行失衡、怕自己的追隨只是一場誤解。","en":"In Chapter 7 he accuses Genki, \"You made Lord Enma act himself\" — beneath the loyalty is fear: fear the king is wavering, fear the Parade is unbalanced, fear his own following was one long misunderstanding.","proposal":false},{"cn":"玄鬼的「你可以選擇」擊中他最深的恐懼——忠誠之人最怕的兩個字。","en":"Genki's words \"You can choose\" strike his deepest fear — the two words the loyal fear most.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第十三章他終於垂下頭，理解忠誠不是盲從，而是懂得何時放手。","en":"In Chapter 13 he finally lowers his head, understanding that loyalty is not blind obedience but knowing when to let go.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"第一部故事線","en":"Part One Story Arc","pairs":[{"cn":"第七章：義牙踏夜而出，指控玄鬼「你讓炎馬大人親自出手」，兩度出拳，玄鬼皆未反擊，只承受；玄鬼一句「你可以選擇」令他動作停住；他留下「我會看著你」後消失於夜中。","en":"Chapter 7: Giga steps out of the night and accuses Genki, \"You made Lord Enma act himself.\" He strikes twice; Genki does not retaliate, only endures. Genki's line \"You can choose\" stops him cold; he leaves with \"I will be watching you\" and vanishes into the night.","proposal":false},{"cn":"白蓮在此章宣告修行第五條：「面對忠誠，不摧毀。」","en":"In this chapter Byakuren pronounces the Fifth Precept: \"Faced with loyalty, do not destroy it.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"第九章：白嶺列出夜行諸王的角色分工，提及「義牙會測試」，確立他日後仍將持續考驗玄鬼。","en":"Chapter 9: Hakurei lists the kings' roles, noting \"Giga will test,\" establishing that he will continue to challenge Genki going forward.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第十二章：義牙隨炎馬、白嶺、烏嶽前來會面，聽聞修行將使夜行逐年減少後，握緊拳頭，說出「而我們，將逐一離開」。","en":"Chapter 12: Giga arrives with Enma, Hakurei, and Ugaku for the meeting; on hearing that the Practice will shrink the Parade year by year, he clenches his fist and says, \"And we — will leave, one by one.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"第十三章：夜行逐漸消散的歲月裡，義牙離開；他垂下頭，第一次明白忠誠不是盲從，而是理解何時放手。","en":"Chapter 13: as the Parade gradually fades over the years, Giga departs; he lowers his head, understanding for the first time that loyalty is not blind obedience but knowing when to release.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"人物關係","en":"Relationships","pairs":[{"cn":"與炎馬：主從關係——他的忠誠是一種以警惕表達的愛。","en":"With Enma: a lord-and-retainer bond — his loyalty is love expressed as vigilance.","proposal":false},{"cn":"與玄鬼：從敵對出發，逐漸成為彼此的鏡像；玄鬼承受他的攻擊而不還手，讓他第一次看見自己的動搖。","en":"With Genki: begins as an adversary, gradually becomes a mirror; Genki absorbs his blows without retaliating, letting him see his own wavering for the first time.","proposal":false},{"cn":"與白蓮：她在第七章當場宣告修行第五條「面對忠誠，不摧毀」，等同為義牙的處境立下規則。","en":"With Byakuren: in Chapter 7 she pronounces the Fifth Precept, \"Faced with loyalty, do not destroy it,\" on the spot — effectively setting the rule that governs Giga's situation.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"關鍵台詞","en":"Key Lines","pairs":[{"cn":"「你讓炎馬大人親自出手。」","en":"\"You made Lord Enma act himself.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「反擊！證明你仍有資格站在前面！」","en":"\"Strike back! Prove you still have the right to stand at the front!\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「你若錯，炎馬大人會先崩。」","en":"\"If you are wrong, Lord Enma will break first.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「我會看著你。」","en":"\"I will be watching you.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「而我們，將逐一離開。」","en":"\"And we — will leave, one by one.\"","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"聲音與表演備註","en":"Voice & Performance Notes","pairs":[{"cn":"聲線：快、短促，音量在不確定時反而升高，藉此掩蓋恐懼。","en":"Voice: fast, clipped; volume rises when he is uncertain, using loudness to mask fear.","proposal":true},{"cn":"戰鬥表演：第一拳為試探性、克制的力道，第二拳需明顯轉為情緒失控的全力一擊。","en":"Combat performance: the first strike should read as a restrained probe; the second must clearly shift into an emotionally unrestrained full-force blow.","proposal":true},{"cn":"關鍵轉折「你可以選擇」出現時，需要一個完整的靜止拍——身體先停，表情才跟上。","en":"At the pivotal line \"You can choose,\" allow one full beat of stillness — the body freezes first, the expression catches up after.","proposal":true},{"cn":"第十三章垂頭的動作要慢、要輕，與早期的直、快、不容質疑形成對比。","en":"The head-lowering gesture in Chapter 13 should be slow and quiet, contrasting with his earlier straight, fast, unquestionable bearing.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"未來發展掛鉤","en":"Future Hooks","pairs":[{"cn":"義牙在大江山時代如何開始追隨炎馬，可作為與炎馬共通的前傳素材。","en":"How Giga began following Enma back on Mount Ōe could serve as prequel material shared with Enma.","proposal":true},{"cn":"「忠誠即放手」的主題可延伸為後續集數中其他追隨者角色的參照範本。","en":"The theme \"loyalty is knowing when to release\" could extend as a reference template for other follower characters in later episodes.","proposal":true},{"cn":"義牙離開後的去向未在正文明示，留白可供後續集數補完其「離開後如何生活」的故事。","en":"Giga's destination after departing is not stated on the page, leaving room for a future episode on \"what life looks like after leaving.\"","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"製作資產清單","en":"Production Asset Checklist","pairs":[{"cn":"概念設定圖：強調「磨亮的刃」般的眼神與緊繃的肌肉線條。","en":"Concept art: emphasize the \"polished blade\" gaze and taut, tensed musculature.","proposal":false},{"cn":"三視圖：需標示能震裂石橋的拳頭比例與姿態。","en":"Character turnaround: mark the proportions and stance of fists capable of cracking stone bridges.","proposal":false},{"cn":"表情表：核心表情為「試探性攻擊時的冷笑」到「動搖時的愣住」的漸變。","en":"Expression sheet: core progression from \"the cold smirk of a testing strike\" to \"the frozen look of wavering.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"服裝道具表：需呼應「茨木」的荊棘意象，設計帶刺質感的護具或紋飾。","en":"Costume & prop sheet: should echo the \"Ibaraki\" thorn imagery with barbed-textured armor or motifs.","proposal":false},{"cn":"色彩指定：荊棘墨綠與鋼灰，攻擊特效可用裂石的白色碎屑作為點綴。","en":"Color script: thorn green-black and steel grey; attack effects can use white stone-shard debris as an accent.","proposal":false},{"cn":"動態參考：直、快、不容質疑的步伐與兩階段出拳需要專屬的武打動作參考。","en":"Motion reference: the straight, fast, unquestionable gait and the two-stage strike sequence need dedicated fight-choreography reference.","proposal":false},{"cn":"聲優試音方向：快而清晰的吐字，情緒升溫時音量上揚而非低沉。","en":"VO casting direction: fast, crisp diction; volume rises rather than deepens as emotion escalates.","proposal":false},{"cn":"分集出場表：第七、九、十二、十三章為必要出場集數。","en":"Episode appearance list: Chapters 7, 9, 12, and 13 are his required appearance episodes.","proposal":false}]}]},{"id":"05","kanji":"鞍馬烏嶽","romaji":"Kurama Ugaku","species_cn":"天狗","species_en":"Tengu","archetype_cn":"理性型","archetype_en":"Reason","archetypeKey":"reason","color":"#4f7398","color2":"#9cc0e0","priority":"T1","active":true,"roleline":"The judge; first institutional response","sections":[{"cn":"基本資料","en":"Basic Information","pairs":[{"cn":"全名：鞍馬烏嶽（くらま　うがく），羅馬拼音 Kurama Ugaku，日常稱呼「烏嶽」。","en":"Full name: Kurama Ugaku (鞍馬烏嶽), romanized Kurama Ugaku; referred to in running text as \"Ugaku.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"物種：天狗（tengu）。","en":"Species: tengu.","proposal":false},{"cn":"原型：理性型，秩序體系最早出面的機構性回應者、審判者。","en":"Archetype: Reason type; the order's first institutional respondent and judge.","proposal":false},{"cn":"角色定位：夜行的審判者與監視者，代表規律對玄鬼「裂縫」的正式追究。","en":"Role: the Parade's judge and watcher, representing the law's formal reckoning with the \"crack\" Genki has caused.","proposal":false},{"cn":"初登場：第三章｜觀察者的條件。","en":"First appearance: Chapter 3 — The Observer's Terms.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第一部結局時的狀態：第十三章隨眾王離開。","en":"Status at end of Part One: departs along with the other kings in Chapter 13.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"名字由來","en":"Name Etymology","pairs":[{"cn":"「鞍馬」取自鞍馬山傳說之地名。","en":"\"Kurama\" draws on the place-name legend of Mount Kurama.","proposal":false},{"cn":"「烏嶽」意為「烏鴉之峰／黑翼之峰」。","en":"\"Ugaku\" means \"crow peak / black-winged peak.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"氣質為「嚴肅、審判者」——是秩序體系裡的法官角色。","en":"Temperament: \"stern; the judge\" — he occupies the judge's role within the order's system.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"氣質與性格","en":"Temperament & Personality","pairs":[{"cn":"出場先於其形，以自上而下的空氣壓力宣告存在。","en":"His presence arrives before his form — announced by pressure descending from above.","proposal":false},{"cn":"審視多於敵意：看向玄鬼時，不帶敵意，也不帶善意，只有審視。","en":"Scrutiny rather than hostility: when he looks at Genki, there is no malice and no kindness — only judgment.","proposal":false},{"cn":"語速不快，聲音不大，卻清晰地落在每個人耳邊——一種法庭般的節奏。","en":"He does not speak quickly or loudly, yet his words land clearly in every ear — a courtroom cadence.","proposal":false},{"cn":"對「厭倦」這個理由的判定極為嚴格：「厭倦，不足以支撐修行。」","en":"His judgment of \"weariness\" as a motive is severe: \"Weariness is not enough to sustain the Practice.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"不隨意動手，先以言語與凝視施壓，給出明確的挑戰而非威脅。","en":"He does not act rashly — he first applies pressure through words and gaze, issuing a clear challenge rather than a threat.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"外貌與視覺設計","en":"Appearance & Visual Design","pairs":[{"cn":"現身時先是自上而下壓來的氣流，如同重量本身先於身形抵達。","en":"He arrives first as a downward pressure of air, as if the weight itself precedes the body.","proposal":false},{"cn":"披風如羽翼般展開，卻沒有真正的翅膀。","en":"His cloak spreads like wings, though he has no true wings.","proposal":false},{"cn":"眼神冷得像冬日的石階。","en":"His eyes are cold as winter stone steps.","proposal":false},{"cn":"聲音不大，卻清晰地落在每個人耳邊。","en":"His voice is not loud, yet it lands clearly in every ear.","proposal":false},{"cn":"與另一道影子（白嶺）一高一矮並立於屋瓦之上初次登場。","en":"He first appears standing atop the rooftiles beside another shadow (Hakurei) — one tall, one shorter.","proposal":false},{"cn":"色彩指定：鴉羽黑、風暴灰，點綴一線山脈的白，呼應鞍馬山意象。","en":"Color script: crow-feather black, storm grey, with one line of mountain white, echoing the Mount Kurama imagery.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"背景與象徵","en":"Background & Symbolism","pairs":[{"cn":"他是秩序體系對玄鬼「裂縫」的第一個機構性回應，象徵規律開始正式追究責任。","en":"He is the order's first institutional response to Genki's \"crack,\" marking the moment the law begins to formally seek accountability.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第三章他質問玄鬼的動機，判定「厭倦，不足以支撐修行」，並下達挑戰「那就證明」。","en":"In Chapter 3 he interrogates Genki's motive, rules that \"weariness is not enough to sustain the Practice,\" and issues the challenge, \"Then prove it.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"第九章白嶺列出諸王分工時提及「烏嶽會監視」，確立他成為此後持續觀察玄鬼的固定角色。","en":"In Chapter 9, when Hakurei lists the kings' roles, he notes \"Ugaku will watch,\" establishing Ugaku as the ongoing observer of Genki from that point on.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第十二章他隨眾王前來，見證修行成立與夜行諸王「將逐一離開」的裁定。","en":"In Chapter 12 he arrives with the other kings, witnessing the ruling that the Practice stands and that the kings \"will leave, one by one.\"","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"第一部故事線","en":"Part One Story Arc","pairs":[{"cn":"第三章：烏嶽與白嶺自屋瓦上方現身，質問玄鬼「夜行出現裂縫。原因是你。」；追問其停下的動機，判定「厭倦，不足以支撐修行」；玄鬼答以「那就讓它崩」，烏嶽最終留下挑戰「那就證明」後離去。","en":"Chapter 3: Ugaku and Hakurei appear above the rooftiles and confront Genki: \"A crack has appeared in the Parade. The cause is you.\" He presses for Genki's motive and rules \"Weariness is not enough to sustain the Practice.\" Genki answers, \"Then let it collapse.\" Ugaku departs, leaving the challenge: \"Then prove it.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"同章白蓮宣告修行第二條：「承受質疑，而不反擊。」直接呼應烏嶽帶來的質問。","en":"In the same chapter, Byakuren pronounces the Second Precept: \"Bear doubt without striking back\" — a direct response to the questioning Ugaku brings.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第九章：白嶺分派諸王職責時明言「烏嶽會監視」，將他定位為此後持續在場的審判與監視者。","en":"Chapter 9: as Hakurei assigns the kings' roles, he states plainly, \"Ugaku will watch,\" positioning him as the ongoing judge-and-watcher figure from this point forward.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第十二章：烏嶽隨炎馬、白嶺、義牙一同前來會面，共同見證並確認修行成立後夜行將逐年減少的裁定。","en":"Chapter 12: Ugaku arrives together with Enma, Hakurei, and Giga for the meeting, jointly witnessing and confirming the ruling that the Parade will diminish year by year now that the Practice stands.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第十三章：隨眾王一同離開，融入夜行逐漸消散的最終階段。","en":"Chapter 13: departs together with the other kings, part of the Parade's final gradual dissolution.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"人物關係","en":"Relationships","pairs":[{"cn":"與白嶺：階級上的下位者，兩人並肩現身，白嶺為更高階的秩序持有者。","en":"With Hakurei: his senior in rank; the two appear side by side, with Hakurei holding the higher position in the order.","proposal":false},{"cn":"與玄鬼：他必須審判的案件——烏嶽對玄鬼不帶敵意亦不帶善意，只有審視與追究。","en":"With Genki: the case he must judge — Ugaku regards him with neither malice nor kindness, only scrutiny and pursuit of accountability.","proposal":false},{"cn":"與碧吉、黑縁：他掃視兩人「你們選擇留下？」一句，將旁觀的追隨者也一併納入審視範圍。","en":"With Aokichi and Kuroberi: his sweeping glance and the line \"You two have chosen to stay?\" draws even the bystanding followers into his scrutiny.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"關鍵台詞","en":"Key Lines","pairs":[{"cn":"「夜行出現裂縫。原因是你。」","en":"\"A crack has appeared in the Parade. The cause is you.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「厭倦，不足以支撐修行。」","en":"\"Weariness is not enough to sustain the Practice.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「那就證明。」","en":"\"Then prove it.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「你若不走，秩序會崩。」","en":"\"If you do not walk on, order will collapse.\"","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"聲音與表演備註","en":"Voice & Performance Notes","pairs":[{"cn":"聲線：法庭般的節奏，從不重複自己說過的話，用詞精確、不帶贅語。","en":"Voice: courtroom cadence; never repeats himself, with precise, economical word choice.","proposal":true},{"cn":"音量控制：全程音量不大，卻要求配音以「清晰穿透」而非「音量壓迫」的方式呈現存在感。","en":"Volume control: never loud throughout — the performance should convey presence through \"clarity that cuts through\" rather than volume.","proposal":true},{"cn":"肢體：先以氣壓（風聲、環境反應）暗示登場，本人現身時反而克制、少動作。","en":"Physicality: his entrance should be signaled first by air pressure (wind, environmental reaction), with restrained, minimal movement once he actually appears.","proposal":true},{"cn":"與烏嶽對話的角色（尤其碧吉、黑縁）需演出被「審視」壓迫的生理反應，如喘氣、汗毛豎起。","en":"Characters speaking with him (especially Aokichi, Kuroberi) should physically react to the pressure of being \"scrutinized\" — gasping, hair standing on end.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"未來發展掛鉤","en":"Future Hooks","pairs":[{"cn":"烏嶽作為監視者的職責在夜行縮減後如何轉變，可作為後續集數的支線素材。","en":"How Ugaku's watcher duties change as the Parade shrinks could serve as subplot material for later episodes.","proposal":true},{"cn":"他與白嶺的上下級關係、與鞍馬山體系的更多背景，可作為前傳或外傳素材。","en":"His senior-junior relationship with Hakurei and further background on the Mount Kurama hierarchy could serve as prequel or side-story material.","proposal":true},{"cn":"烏嶽「證明」的挑戰貫穿全書卻未見他親自宣判結果，後續集數可補上他對玄鬼最終裁決的反應。","en":"Ugaku's challenge to \"prove it\" runs through the whole story without his ever personally pronouncing a final verdict — a future episode could show his reaction to Genki's ultimate outcome.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"製作資產清單","en":"Production Asset Checklist","pairs":[{"cn":"概念設定圖：強調「冷得像冬日石階」的眼神與如羽翼展開卻無真翼的披風。","en":"Concept art: emphasize the \"cold as winter stone steps\" gaze and the wing-like cloak that spreads without true wings.","proposal":false},{"cn":"三視圖：需標示披風展開時的輪廓線與天狗形制的比例。","en":"Character turnaround: mark the silhouette when the cloak spreads and the proportions of his tengu form.","proposal":false},{"cn":"表情表：核心表情為「審視」——不帶敵意也不帶善意的中性凝視，及宣判瞬間的細微鋒利。","en":"Expression sheet: core expression is \"scrutiny\" — a neutral gaze without malice or kindness, with a faint sharpness at the moment of verdict.","proposal":false},{"cn":"服裝道具表：需設計出羽翼意象的披風結構與鞍馬山信仰相關的配飾。","en":"Costume & prop sheet: design the wing-motif cloak structure and accessories tied to Mount Kurama iconography.","proposal":false},{"cn":"色彩指定：鴉羽黑、風暴灰、一線山脈白，用以與白嶺的雪白區隔。","en":"Color script: crow-feather black, storm grey, one line of mountain white — distinguished from Hakurei's snow white.","proposal":false},{"cn":"動態參考：自上而下的氣壓式登場與屋瓦上的定點站姿需要專屬分鏡與動態參考。","en":"Motion reference: the top-down pressure-based entrance and the fixed rooftile stance require dedicated storyboard and motion reference.","proposal":false},{"cn":"聲優試音方向：法庭式節奏，語速平穩、用詞精確，不重複台詞用語。","en":"VO casting direction: courtroom-cadence delivery, steady pacing, precise word choice, never repeating phrasing.","proposal":false},{"cn":"分集出場表：第三、九、十二、十三章為必要出場集數。","en":"Episode appearance list: Chapters 3, 9, 12, and 13 are his required appearance episodes.","proposal":false}]}]},{"id":"06","kanji":"鞍馬白嶺","romaji":"Kurama Hakurei","species_cn":"大天狗","species_en":"Daitengu","archetype_cn":"重力型","archetype_en":"Gravity","archetypeKey":"gravity","color":"#8b2f28","color2":"#c0453b","priority":"T1","active":true,"roleline":"Order's load-bearer; the philosophical antagonist","sections":[{"cn":"基本資料","en":"Basic Information","pairs":[{"cn":"全名：鞍馬白嶺（くらま　はくれい），羅馬拼音 Kurama Hakurei，日常稱呼「白嶺」。","en":"Full name: Kurama Hakurei (鞍馬白嶺), romanized Kurama Hakurei; referred to in running text as \"Hakurei.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"物種：大天狗（daitengu）。","en":"Species: daitengu.","proposal":false},{"cn":"原型：重力型，秩序體系的最高持有者之一，全書的哲學對手。","en":"Archetype: Gravity type; one of the highest holders of order, and the story's philosophical antagonist.","proposal":false},{"cn":"角色定位：秩序即承重的代言者，玄鬼所選道路的終極質問者。","en":"Role: the voice of \"order as load-bearing,\" the ultimate interrogator of the path Genki has chosen.","proposal":false},{"cn":"初登場：第九章｜秩序的壓力（核心章節）。","en":"First appearance: Chapter 9 — The Weight of Order (his centerpiece chapter).","proposal":false},{"cn":"第一部結局時的狀態：第十三章在夜行諸王中最後離開（僅早於白蓮），最後回頭一望後化入金色光芒。","en":"Status at end of Part One: the last of the kings to depart in Chapter 13 (before only Byakuren), taking one final look back before dissolving into golden light.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"名字由來","en":"Name Etymology","pairs":[{"cn":"「鞍馬」取自鞍馬山傳說之地名。","en":"\"Kurama\" draws on the place-name legend of Mount Kurama.","proposal":false},{"cn":"「白嶺」意為「白色的高峰」，指向高處。","en":"\"Hakurei\" means \"white peak\" — pointing to the high place.","proposal":false},{"cn":"氣質為「威嚴秩序」——莊嚴而以秩序為本。","en":"Temperament: \"majesty and order\" — dignified, grounded in order itself.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"氣質與性格","en":"Temperament & Personality","pairs":[{"cn":"不帶怒，不帶質問，只有秩序——他的存在本身即是規則的具現。","en":"He carries no anger, no accusation — only order; his very presence is the embodiment of the rule.","proposal":false},{"cn":"聲音清，清得讓人無法躲避，與炎馬的沉形成對比。","en":"His voice is clear — so clear it cannot be evaded — a contrast to Enma's low weight.","proposal":false},{"cn":"信念核心：「秩序不是實驗。秩序是承重。」「不確定，比恐懼更危險。」","en":"His core belief: \"Order is not an experiment. Order is load-bearing.\" \"Uncertainty is more dangerous than fear.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"他所守護的不是規則本身，而是「存在」——若夜行消失，多數妖怪將失去存在理由。","en":"What he protects is not the rule itself but \"existence\" — if the Parade disappears, most yokai will lose their reason to exist.","proposal":false},{"cn":"白蓮是唯一讀出他真正恐懼的人：「你怕的不是混亂。你怕的是秩序失去角色。」","en":"Byakuren is the only one who reads his true fear: \"You are not afraid of chaos. You are afraid order will lose its role.\"","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"外貌與視覺設計","en":"Appearance & Visual Design","pairs":[{"cn":"衣袍如雪。","en":"His robes are white as snow.","proposal":false},{"cn":"他不是墜落，而是降臨。","en":"He does not fall — he descends.","proposal":false},{"cn":"現身時空氣忽然變得乾淨，乾淨得不自然，像有人把所有雜音抽走。","en":"The air turns suddenly clean when he arrives — unnaturally clean, as if all noise had been drawn away.","proposal":false},{"cn":"目光如山。","en":"His gaze is like a mountain.","proposal":false},{"cn":"最後一次退場前，「白嶺最後一次回頭」，是全書少見的、屬於他的情感留白動作。","en":"Before his final exit, \"Hakurei looks back one last time\" — a rare, emotionally charged gesture belonging solely to him.","proposal":false},{"cn":"色彩指定：雪白、高海拔藍、淡金，用以呈現他與烏嶽的雪白／鴉黑對比。","en":"Color script: snow white, high-altitude blue, pale gold — contrasting his snow white against Ugaku's crow black.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"背景與象徵","en":"Background & Symbolism","pairs":[{"cn":"他是全書秩序一方的最終立場：秩序不是為了恐嚇，而是為了平衡；若無承擔者，偏見會尋找無辜之人。","en":"He represents the ultimate position of the order's side: order exists not to intimidate but to balance; without a bearer, prejudice will seek out the innocent.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第九章他揭示真正的賭注：若玄鬼成功，百鬼夜行將消失，夜行中大半存在都將失去存在理由——他所保護的是「存在」，而非單純的規則。","en":"In Chapter 9 he reveals the true stakes: if Genki succeeds, the Night Parade will vanish, and most of its members will lose their reason to exist — what he protects is \"existence\" itself, not mere rules.","proposal":false},{"cn":"他提出條件：「若你要走這條路，你必須承擔所有消失。」並警告：「而我——會在你失控時，斬斷。」","en":"He sets the terms: \"If you walk this path, you must bear all the vanishing.\" And he warns: \"And I — will cut you down, should you lose control.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"第十二章他代表秩序方明言：「我們不阻止。但我們不會幫。」——這不是威脅，而是規則：夜行不能自毀，必須由人類減少，由妖怪褪去。","en":"In Chapter 12 he states plainly on behalf of the order: \"We will not stop you. But we will not help.\" — not a threat, but a rule: the Parade cannot destroy itself; it must be diminished by humans and shed by yokai.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第十三章他是眾王中最後一位離開者，僅早於白蓮，象徵秩序是最後鬆手的力量。","en":"In Chapter 13 he is the last of the kings to depart, before only Byakuren — a symbol that order is the last force to let go.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"第一部故事線","en":"Part One Story Arc","pairs":[{"cn":"第九章：白嶺自空中降臨，質問玄鬼「你改變了流程」，闡述「秩序不是實驗，秩序是承重」；他揭露若玄鬼成功，夜行中大半存在都將消失；提出條件「你必須承擔所有消失」，並警告「會在你失控時，斬斷」。","en":"Chapter 9: Hakurei descends from the sky, confronting Genki with \"You have changed the process,\" articulating \"Order is not an experiment. Order is load-bearing.\" He reveals that if Genki succeeds, most of the Parade's members will vanish; he sets the condition \"You must bear all the vanishing\" and warns, \"I will cut you down, should you lose control.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"同章白蓮指出他真正的恐懼：「你怕的不是混亂。你怕的是秩序失去角色。」","en":"In the same chapter, Byakuren names his true fear: \"You are not afraid of chaos. You are afraid order will lose its role.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"第十二章：白嶺隨炎馬、義牙、烏嶽前來會面，宣布「若修行成立，夜行將逐年減少」，並明言秩序方的立場：「我們不阻止。但我們不會幫。」","en":"Chapter 12: Hakurei arrives with Enma, Giga, and Ugaku for the meeting, announcing \"If the Practice stands, the Parade will diminish year by year,\" and stating the order's position plainly: \"We will not stop you. But we will not help.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"第十三章：夜行漸輕的歲月中，炎馬、義牙、烏嶽相繼離開，白嶺最後一次回頭一望，隨後也消失於金色光芒之中，成為眾王中最後離開者（僅早於白蓮）。","en":"Chapter 13: as the Parade grows lighter over the years, Enma, Giga, and Ugaku depart in turn; Hakurei looks back one final time, then also dissolves into golden light — the last of the kings to leave, before only Byakuren.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"人物關係","en":"Relationships","pairs":[{"cn":"與烏嶽：白嶺是其上位者，烏嶽是他的爪牙與眼睛，執行監視與追究的實務。","en":"With Ugaku: Hakurei is his senior; Ugaku serves as his blade and eyes, carrying out the practical work of watching and pursuing accountability.","proposal":false},{"cn":"與白蓮：唯一讀出他真正恐懼的人——她看穿他所守護的並非秩序本身，而是「存在」。","en":"With Byakuren: the only one who reads his true fear — she sees that what he guards is not order itself but \"existence.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"與玄鬼：他選擇不阻止、卻可能成為終結修行之人——一種克制的對抗關係。","en":"With Genki: he chooses not to prevent him, yet remains the one who could end the Practice by force — a relationship of restrained opposition.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"關鍵台詞","en":"Key Lines","pairs":[{"cn":"「秩序不是實驗。秩序是承重。」","en":"\"Order is not an experiment. Order is load-bearing.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「不確定，比恐懼更危險。」","en":"\"Uncertainty is more dangerous than fear.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「若你要走這條路，你必須承擔所有消失。」","en":"\"If you walk this path, you must bear all the vanishing.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「而我——會在你失控時，斬斷。」","en":"\"And I — will cut you down, should you lose control.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「我們不阻止。但我們不會幫。」","en":"\"We will not stop you. But we will not help.\"","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"聲音與表演備註","en":"Voice & Performance Notes","pairs":[{"cn":"聲線：不急、冰川般、帶終局感——每一句話都像已經想過千百次的定論。","en":"Voice: unhurried, glacial, final — every line should sound like a conclusion already considered a thousand times.","proposal":true},{"cn":"情緒收束：全程幾乎不動怒，唯一的鬆動只在白蓮點破他的恐懼時，以極細微的停頓呈現。","en":"Emotional restraint: he almost never shows anger throughout; the only crack should appear as a barely perceptible pause when Byakuren names his fear.","proposal":true},{"cn":"登場調度：先以「空氣變乾淨」的環境音效與燈光變化建立存在感，本人現身時動作極簡。","en":"Entrance staging: establish his presence first through the \"air turning clean\" sound design and lighting shift, with minimal physical movement once he appears.","proposal":true},{"cn":"第十三章「最後一次回頭」需要一個無台詞的長鏡頭，是全劇賦予他的唯一情感特寫。","en":"The Chapter 13 \"final look back\" needs a wordless extended shot — the one emotional close-up granted to him in the entire story.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"未來發展掛鉤","en":"Future Hooks","pairs":[{"cn":"白嶺所代表的「秩序保護存在」哲學，可作為未來反派或對照角色的思想根基。","en":"The philosophy Hakurei embodies — \"order protects existence\" — could serve as the ideological foundation for future antagonists or contrasting characters.","proposal":true},{"cn":"他與白蓮之間「唯一讀懂彼此恐懼」的關係，可作為前傳或外傳中兩人交手歷史的素材。","en":"His relationship with Byakuren — the only pair who read each other's fears — could provide material for a prequel or side story about their shared history.","proposal":true},{"cn":"「若失控便斬斷」的警告在第一部從未兌現，可作為後續集數中的懸念或衝突引信。","en":"His warning to \"cut down\" Genki if he loses control is never carried out in Part One, and could serve as a suspended threat or conflict trigger in later episodes.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"製作資產清單","en":"Production Asset Checklist","pairs":[{"cn":"概念設定圖：強調「衣袍如雪」與「目光如山」的莊嚴感，及降臨時空氣變乾淨的視覺效果。","en":"Concept art: emphasize the \"robes white as snow\" and \"gaze like a mountain\" dignity, plus the visual effect of the air turning clean on his descent.","proposal":false},{"cn":"三視圖：需標示雪白衣袍的垂墜結構與大天狗形制的比例。","en":"Character turnaround: mark the drape structure of the snow-white robes and the proportions of his daitengu form.","proposal":false},{"cn":"表情表：核心表情為近乎無情緒的莊嚴，及白蓮點破其恐懼時的極微妙鬆動。","en":"Expression sheet: core expression is near-emotionless dignity, with an extremely subtle crack when Byakuren names his fear.","proposal":false},{"cn":"服裝道具表：需設計呼應「白色高峰」意象的雪白袍服與秩序象徵配件。","en":"Costume & prop sheet: design snow-white robes and order-symbolizing accessories echoing the \"white peak\" imagery.","proposal":false},{"cn":"色彩指定：雪白、高海拔藍、淡金，與烏嶽的鴉黑形成主僕對比色階。","en":"Color script: snow white, high-altitude blue, pale gold — forming a senior-junior color contrast against Ugaku's crow black.","proposal":false},{"cn":"動態參考：「不是墜落，是降臨」的下降動態需要專屬的分鏡與速度控制參考。","en":"Motion reference: the \"not falling, but descending\" motion needs dedicated storyboard and pacing-control reference.","proposal":false},{"cn":"聲優試音方向：不急、冰川般、帶終局感的聲線，需能在莊嚴陳述與極細微情感洩漏間切換。","en":"VO c","proposal":false}]}]},{"id":"07","kanji":"霜月澄","romaji":"Shimotsuki Sumi","species_cn":"雪女","species_en":"Yuki-onna","archetype_cn":"情緒型","archetype_en":"Emotion","archetypeKey":"emotion","color":"#7d5aa6","color2":"#b992e0","priority":"T2","active":false,"roleline":"Emotion frozen — reserved for Part Two","sections":[{"cn":"基本資料","en":"Basic Information","pairs":[{"cn":"名字：霜月澄（しもつきすみ）","en":"Name: Shimotsuki Sumi (Shimotsuki: \"frost month\"; Sumi: \"clear, limpid\")","proposal":false},{"cn":"妖怪種類：雪女（ゆきおんな）","en":"Species: yuki-onna (snow woman)","proposal":false},{"cn":"人物原型：情緒型（感情が凍りついた）","en":"Archetype: Emotion (emotion crystallized into frost)","proposal":false},{"cn":"第一部初登場：無","en":"First Appearance in Part One: None","proposal":false},{"cn":"角色身份：保留至後續分集","en":"Status: Reserved for future episodes","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"名字由來","en":"Name Etymology","pairs":[{"cn":"霜月是十一月的舊曆名稱，代表深冬清晨的寒風與霜凍。","en":"Shimotsuki is the old lunar calendar name for the eleventh month, evoking the bitter cold and frost of deep winter mornings.","proposal":false},{"cn":"澄（すみ）意為「清澈」或「澄澈」，帶著透明感卻又冰冷。","en":"Sumi means \"clear\" or \"limpid,\" transparent yet without warmth.","proposal":false},{"cn":"姓名組合象徵一種被冰封的澄明——看得清但感受不到。","en":"The name together suggests a clarity frozen in place: clarity visible but without feeling.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"氣質與性格","en":"Temperament & Personality","pairs":[{"cn":"冷靜而壓抑，習慣於內斂。","en":"Calm and suppressed; habituated to inward containment.","proposal":false},{"cn":"與綾女的對照：綾女是爆發的情緒，澄則是凍結的情緒。","en":"In contrast to Ayame: Ayame is emotion erupting; Sumi is emotion frozen.","proposal":false},{"cn":"她的沉默不是冷漠，而是一種深層的克制——彷彿所有感受都被鎖在冰層下。","en":"Her silence is not indifference but a deep restraint, as if all feeling were sealed beneath ice.","proposal":true},{"cn":"修行第六條對她是未來的戰場：如何承認情緒而不被情緒定義？","en":"The Sixth Precept is her future battlefield: how to acknowledge emotion without being defined by it?","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"外貌與視覺設計","en":"Appearance & Visual Design","pairs":[{"cn":"蒼白的膚色，帶著細微的冰藍色光澤。","en":"Pallid complexion with a subtle ice-blue luminescence.","proposal":true},{"cn":"長黑色頭髮，散落肩頭，卻似乎結著細微的冰晶。","en":"Long black hair falling across her shoulders, adorned with minute ice crystals.","proposal":true},{"cn":"眼睛澄澈如冬日的天空，卻無神情。","en":"Eyes clear as a winter sky, yet without expression.","proposal":true},{"cn":"穿著白色與藍色相間的衣著，顏色調和如雪景。","en":"Wears white and blue garments in harmony, like a snowy landscape.","proposal":true},{"cn":"調色：藍白色、紙白、黑髮。","en":"Palette: blue-white, paper white, black hair.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"背景與象徵","en":"Background & Symbolism","pairs":[{"cn":"雪女的古傳說中，她是冰雪而成的妖，在寒夜現身，帶走人的體溫。","en":"In the classical yuki-onna legend, she is a yokai born of ice and snow, appearing on cold nights to steal human warmth.","proposal":false},{"cn":"在『金無垢』中，澄象徵無法解凍的悲傷——源於對失去的永恆克制。","en":"In Kinmuku, Sumi represents grief that cannot thaw, born of eternal restraint in the face of loss.","proposal":true},{"cn":"她的存在提出一個問題：冷靜本身是不是一種害怕？","en":"Her existence poses a question: is calmness itself a form of fear?","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"第一部故事線","en":"Part One Story Arc","pairs":[{"cn":"霜月澄不出現在第一部故事中。","en":"Shimotsuki Sumi does not appear in Part One.","proposal":false},{"cn":"保留至後續分集。","en":"Reserved for future episodes.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"人物關係","en":"Relationships","pairs":[{"cn":"與綾女的姐妹式對比——綾女的熊熊烈火與澄的寂靜結冰。","en":"Sister-like contrast with Ayame: Ayame's roaring flame against Sumi's silent frost.","proposal":true},{"cn":"與赤座玄鬼的共鳴：都承受著難以言說的寂重感。","en":"Resonance with Akaza Genki: both bearing an unspeakable heaviness.","proposal":true},{"cn":"在後續分集中可能成為修行第六條的活體驗證。","en":"In future episodes, may become the living test of the Sixth Precept.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"關鍵台詞","en":"Key Lines","pairs":[{"cn":"霜月澄在第一部無台詞。","en":"Shimotsuki Sumi has no canonical lines in Part One.","proposal":false},{"cn":"「也許……冷靜就是我唯一的選擇。」","en":"\"Perhaps… calmness is my only choice.\"","proposal":true},{"cn":"「不是不想感受。是不知道感受之後會發生什麼。」","en":"\"It is not that I don't wish to feel. It is that I do not know what would happen if I did.\"","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"聲音與表演備註","en":"Voice & Performance Notes","pairs":[{"cn":"嗓音接近耳語，音量與音調都平坦，直到某個瞬間才會有起伏。","en":"Voice near-whisper; flat in volume and pitch until a single moment brings inflection.","proposal":true},{"cn":"說話速度緩慢，字與字之間留著寒冷的空隙。","en":"Speech slowed; spaces between words filled with cold silence.","proposal":true},{"cn":"當情緒真正浮現時，聲音應該帶著融冰般的顫抖。","en":"When genuine emotion surfaces, the voice should tremble like melting ice.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"未來發展掛鉤","en":"Future Hooks","pairs":[{"cn":"第二部的某一集：徘徊的恐懼化為霜凍——拒絕解凍的悲傷。","en":"A future episode: lingering fear transforms to frost—grief that refuses to thaw.","proposal":true},{"cn":"她的金寂應該是融化，而非破裂。","en":"Her Golden Stillness would be melting, not shattering.","proposal":true},{"cn":"修行第六條的相反入口：從情緒凍結開始，學會承認與釋放。","en":"The inverse path to the Sixth Precept: beginning from frozen emotion, learning to acknowledge and release.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"製作資產清單","en":"Production Asset Checklist","pairs":[{"cn":"概念設定圖","en":"Concept art","proposal":false},{"cn":"三視圖","en":"Character turnaround","proposal":false},{"cn":"表情表","en":"Expression sheet","proposal":false},{"cn":"服裝道具表","en":"Costume & prop sheet","proposal":false},{"cn":"色彩指定","en":"Color script","proposal":false},{"cn":"動態參考","en":"Motion reference","proposal":false},{"cn":"聲優試音方向","en":"VO casting direction","proposal":false},{"cn":"分集出場表","en":"Episode appearance list","proposal":false}]}]},{"id":"08","kanji":"綾女","romaji":"Ayame","species_cn":"般若","species_en":"Hannya","archetype_cn":"情緒型","archetype_en":"Emotion","archetypeKey":"emotion","color":"#7d5aa6","color2":"#b992e0","priority":"T1","active":true,"roleline":"Resentment given form; first to reach Golden Stillness","sections":[{"cn":"基本資料","en":"Basic Information","pairs":[{"cn":"全名：綾女（あやめ），羅馬拼音 Ayame。","en":"Full name: Ayame (綾女), romaji Ayame.","proposal":false},{"cn":"種族：般若（Hannya）。","en":"Species: hannya.","proposal":false},{"cn":"原型分類：情緒型。","en":"Archetype: Emotion.","proposal":false},{"cn":"角色定位：夜行成員；憤怒與存在證明的化身。","en":"Role: member of the Night Parade; the embodiment of rage as proof of existence.","proposal":false},{"cn":"初登場：第八章｜怨的形狀。","en":"First appearance: Chapter 8 — The Shape of Resentment.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第一部結尾狀態：全書第一位抵達金寂者，率先離開。","en":"Status at the end of Part One: the first character in the entire story to reach Golden Stillness — the first to depart.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"名字由來","en":"Name Etymology","pairs":[{"cn":"「綾女」取表面之美與內藏之刃的意象。","en":"\"Ayame\" evokes surface beauty with a blade concealed within.","proposal":false},{"cn":"名字本身即是她的矛盾：外在如綾羅般柔美，內裡是未曾熄滅的怒火。","en":"The name itself is her contradiction: silk-smooth beauty outside, an unextinguished rage within.","proposal":false},{"cn":"這種反差直接對應她的般若面具設定——美與憤怒共存於一身。","en":"This contrast maps directly onto her hannya-mask design — beauty and fury coexisting in a single form.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"氣質與性格","en":"Temperament & Personality","pairs":[{"cn":"性格核心：自尊與怒火。","en":"Core temperament: pride and rage.","proposal":false},{"cn":"她的憤怒不是失控，而是一種自我證明的方式。","en":"Her anger is not loss of control — it is a way of proving herself.","proposal":false},{"cn":"她曾說：「如果我不憤怒，他們就會說我本來就不值得。」","en":"She once said: \"If I do not rage, they will say I never deserved better.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"這句話道出她性格的根本邏輯：憤怒是她抵抗被否定的最後手段。","en":"This line reveals the core logic of her character: rage is her last defense against being erased.","proposal":false},{"cn":"她的自尊極高，卻建立在隨時可能被撕碎的脆弱之上，這使她既強悍又易碎。","en":"Her pride runs high, yet it rests on a fragility that could shatter at any moment — making her both formidable and breakable.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"外貌與視覺設計","en":"Appearance & Visual Design","pairs":[{"cn":"白色長袍，長髮鬆散披落。","en":"A white robe, long hair loose and flowing.","proposal":false},{"cn":"只戴半副般若面具，面具下露出的雙眼帶著紅色眼眶。","en":"She wears only half of a hannya mask; beneath it, her eyes show red-rimmed lids.","proposal":false},{"cn":"她的情緒會實際地扭曲周遭空氣，使地面產生裂痕。","en":"Her emotion physically warps the surrounding air and cracks the ground beneath her.","proposal":false},{"cn":"她流下的淚水會點燃成淡紫色的火焰。","en":"The tears she weeps ignite into a faint violet flame.","proposal":false},{"cn":"隨著真相浮現，面具逐漸出現裂紋，最終於情緒頂點徹底碎裂。","en":"As the truth surfaces, the mask develops cracks, finally shattering completely at her emotional peak.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"背景與象徵","en":"Background & Symbolism","pairs":[{"cn":"她曾被一個聲稱愛她的男人，在眾人面前稱作「妖怪」。","en":"A man who claimed to love her once called her a monster in front of others.","proposal":false},{"cn":"她說：「我沒有想殺他。」「我只是問他，為什麼？」","en":"She said: \"I never meant to kill him.\" \"I only asked him why.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"綾女的怨不是偏見造成的扭曲，而是對背叛最誠實的反應。","en":"Ayame's resentment is not a distortion born of prejudice — it is the most honest possible response to betrayal.","proposal":false},{"cn":"她的存在象徵一個命題：憤怒本身可以是一種存在的證明，而非需要被治療的缺陷。","en":"Her existence embodies one proposition: rage itself can be proof of existence, not a flaw to be cured.","proposal":false},{"cn":"「他們說女人若憤怒，就是妖。」——她的處境同時也是對世俗偏見的直接控訴。","en":"\"They say a woman who rages is a monster.\" — her situation is at once a direct indictment of worldly prejudice.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"第一部故事線","en":"Part One Story Arc","pairs":[{"cn":"第八章為她的核心篇章：綾女摘下面具，怒火與怨氣在她身邊旋轉，裂痕蔓延至地面。","en":"Chapter 8 is her centerpiece: Ayame removes her mask, rage and resentment spinning around her, cracks spreading across the ground.","proposal":false},{"cn":"玄鬼沒有後退，回答她：「你的怨，不是錯。」「但怨不是你全部。」","en":"Genki does not step back. He answers her: \"Your resentment is not a wrongdoing.\" \"But resentment is not all of you.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"面對她「若我不憤怒，他們就會說我本來就不值得」的質問，他答：「若你不憤怒，你仍然存在。」","en":"To her challenge — \"If I do not rage, they will say I never deserved better\" — he answers: \"Even if you are not enraged, you still exist.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"她的面具完全裂開；玄鬼沒有定義她，只是讓她看見有人不因她的怨而退後，於是她留下。","en":"Her mask shatters completely; Genki does not define her — he simply lets her see that someone will not retreat from her resentment, and so she stays.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第十一章：她是全書第一位抵達金寂之人，身上的重量消散，浮現微弱金光。","en":"Chapter 11: she becomes the first person in the entire story to reach Golden Stillness, the weight falling from her as a faint gold light emerges.","proposal":false},{"cn":"她的離去成為夜行運算法則被撼動的第一個實證。","en":"Her departure becomes the first proof-of-concept that shakes the Parade's arithmetic.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"人物關係","en":"Relationships","pairs":[{"cn":"玄鬼：第一個在她盛怒之下沒有退縮的存在，也是她信任的起點。","en":"Genki: the first being who did not step back from her rage — the starting point of her trust.","proposal":false},{"cn":"黒縁：唯一真正理解她的旁觀者，說出：「她不是在失控。她是在證明自己存在。」","en":"Kuroberi: the one bystander who truly understood her, saying: \"She is not losing control. She is proving she exists.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"那個曾說愛她、卻在眾人面前稱她為妖怪的男人：她怨氣的起源，故事未直接描寫其後續。","en":"The man who once claimed to love her, then called her a monster before others: the origin of her resentment; his fate afterward is not depicted on the page.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"關鍵台詞","en":"Key Lines","pairs":[{"cn":"「我沒有想殺他。」","en":"\"I never meant to kill him.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「我只是問他，為什麼？」","en":"\"I only asked him why.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「如果我不憤怒，他們就會說我本來就不值得。」","en":"\"If I do not rage, they will say I never deserved better.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「他們說女人若憤怒，就是妖。」","en":"\"They say a woman who rages is a monster.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「原來……不需要證明。」","en":"\"So… I never had to prove it.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「謝謝。」","en":"\"Thank you.\"","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"聲音與表演備註","en":"Voice & Performance Notes","pairs":[{"cn":"聲音基調：瓷器般平靜的表面，佈滿細微裂紋。","en":"Vocal baseline: a porcelain-calm surface laced with hairline fractures.","proposal":true},{"cn":"她本人幾乎不放聲尖叫——真正崩潰的是她周遭的空間與地面。","en":"She herself almost never screams outright — it is the room around her that breaks instead.","proposal":true},{"cn":"表演上建議以極度克制的語調對比劇烈的環境反應，形成張力。","en":"Performance should pair extremely restrained line delivery against violent environmental reactions, to build tension.","proposal":true},{"cn":"面具摘下前後應有明顯的音色轉變，象徵壓抑到爆發的臨界點。","en":"There should be a clear timbral shift before and after the mask comes off, marking the threshold between suppression and eruption.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"未來發展掛鉤","en":"Future Hooks","pairs":[{"cn":"綾女與霜月澄（雪女）構成情緒型的對照組：綾女是爆發的情緒，澄是冰封的情緒。","en":"Ayame and Shimotsuki Sumi (yuki-onna) form the Emotion archetype's contrasting pair: Ayame is emotion erupting, Sumi is emotion frozen.","proposal":true},{"cn":"作為全書第一位抵達金寂者，她的案例可作為未來集數回溯「金寂如何被證明可能」的關鍵範例。","en":"As the first character to reach Golden Stillness, her case could serve as the key reference point in future episodes revisiting how Golden Stillness was first proven possible.","proposal":true},{"cn":"那位曾稱她為妖怪的男人若在後續集數中重新出現，可延伸探討「怨」在金寂之後是否真正消散。","en":"Should the man who once called her a monster resurface in future episodes, it could extend the exploration of whether resentment truly dissolves after Golden Stillness.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"製作資產清單","en":"Production Asset Checklist","pairs":[{"cn":"概念設定圖：半副般若面具與素顏的並置設計，強調裂痕紋理。","en":"Concept art: juxtaposition of the half hannya mask and her bare face, emphasizing crack textures.","proposal":false},{"cn":"三視圖：白袍與散髮在靜止與情緒爆發兩種狀態下的輪廓差異。","en":"Character turnaround: silhouette differences of the white robe and loose hair between calm and emotional-outburst states.","proposal":false},{"cn":"表情表：面具下紅眼眶的微表情，從壓抑、顫抖到面具碎裂瞬間的完整序列。","en":"Expression sheet: full sequence of micro-expressions in the red-rimmed eyes beneath the mask, from suppression to trembling to the instant the mask shatters.","proposal":false},{"cn":"服裝道具表：白色長袍布料垂墜與半副般若面具的材質規格。","en":"Costume & prop sheet: drape specifications for the white robe fabric and material specs for the half hannya mask.","proposal":false},{"cn":"色彩指定：白、紫藤紫（淚焰）、金（金寂降臨）三階段配色。","en":"Color script: three-stage palette of white, wisteria violet (tear-flame), and gold (arrival of Golden Stillness).","proposal":false},{"cn":"動態參考：地面裂痕擴散與空氣扭曲的特效動態參考。","en":"Motion reference: effects reference for ground-crack propagation and air-warp distortion.","proposal":false},{"cn":"聲優試音方向：需能在極度壓抑與瞬間爆發間自由切換，並掌握「怒中帶脆」的聲線。","en":"VO casting direction: must switch fluidly between extreme restraint and sudden eruption, with a vocal quality that carries fragility inside the fury.","proposal":false},{"cn":"分集出場表：第八章為核心出場集，第十一章為金寂離場集。","en":"Episode appearance list: Chapter 8 is her centerpiece episode; Chapter 11 is her Golden Stillness departure episode.","proposal":false}]}]},{"id":"09","kanji":"白妙","romaji":"Shirotae","species_cn":"骨女","species_en":"Hone-onna","archetype_cn":"存在型","archetype_en":"Presence","archetypeKey":"presence","color":"#8f8672","color2":"#cdbfa6","priority":"T2","active":false,"roleline":"The violence of never being seen — Part Two","sections":[{"cn":"基本資料","en":"Basic Information","pairs":[{"cn":"名字：白妙（しろたえ）","en":"Name: Shirotae","proposal":false},{"cn":"妖怪種類：骨女（ほねおんな）","en":"Species: hone-onna (bone woman)","proposal":false},{"cn":"人物原型：存在型（見不見的暴力）","en":"Archetype: Presence (the violence of invisibility)","proposal":false},{"cn":"第一部初登場：無","en":"First Appearance in Part One: None","proposal":false},{"cn":"角色身份：保留至後續分集","en":"Status: Reserved for future episodes","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"名字由來","en":"Name Etymology","pairs":[{"cn":"白妙是古代對白色布料的雅稱。","en":"Shirotae is an archaic term for white cloth.","proposal":false},{"cn":"「妙」帶著若隱若現的含義——精妙卻難以名狀。","en":"The character \"tae\" carries a sense of subtle, barely perceptible—exquisite yet hard to name.","proposal":false},{"cn":"名字本身就是一種不存在：再精美的白布，也往往被人忽視。","en":"The name itself is a kind of non-existence: even the finest white cloth is easily overlooked.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"氣質與性格","en":"Temperament & Personality","pairs":[{"cn":"淡薄而存在感低，容易被忽視。","en":"Faint and low in presence; easily overlooked.","proposal":false},{"cn":"不是害羞，而是一種更根本的消失——彷彿世界天然就看不見她。","en":"Not shyness, but a more fundamental disappearance, as if the world is naturally blind to her.","proposal":false},{"cn":"她的沉默是被迫的，而非選擇的。","en":"Her silence is compelled, not chosen.","proposal":true},{"cn":"講話時常被打斷，已經習慣了無法完成一句話。","en":"Her speech is habitually interrupted; she has learned to leave sentences unfinished.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"外貌與視覺設計","en":"Appearance & Visual Design","pairs":[{"cn":"膚色如未漂白的布料，介於米白與灰白之間。","en":"Complexion like undyed cloth, between cream and ash-white.","proposal":true},{"cn":"衣著以白色和褪色的紫色為主，彷彿已被時間沖淡。","en":"Garments primarily white and faded lavender, as if bleached by time.","proposal":true},{"cn":"身形纖細而輪廓模糊，即使她站在你面前，視線也容易滑過她。","en":"Form slender and outline soft; even when present, eyes tend to slide away from her.","proposal":true},{"cn":"調色：未漂白的布料白、骨白、褪色紫。","en":"Palette: undyed cloth white, bone ivory, faded lavender.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"背景與象徵","en":"Background & Symbolism","pairs":[{"cn":"骨女是被遺忘的死者——不是著名的幽靈，只是消失在時間裡的普通人。","en":"The hone-onna is the forgotten dead—not a famous ghost, but an ordinary person dissolved into time.","proposal":false},{"cn":"在『金無垢』中，白妙代表一種相反的暴力：不是被過度命名，而是永遠不被命名。","en":"In Kinmuku, Shirotae represents an inverse violence: not over-naming, but eternal non-naming.","proposal":true},{"cn":"她的存在提出修行的根本問題：如果你從未被需要，你能如何「在不被需要時仍然存在」？","en":"Her existence poses a fundamental question of the Practice: if you were never needed, how can you \"remain when unneeded\"?","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"第一部故事線","en":"Part One Story Arc","pairs":[{"cn":"白妙不出現在第一部故事中。","en":"Shirotae does not appear in Part One.","proposal":false},{"cn":"保留至後續分集。","en":"Reserved for future episodes.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"人物關係","en":"Relationships","pairs":[{"cn":"與其他妖怪的對比：他人遭遇被過度定義；她則從未被定義。","en":"In contrast to other yokai: they suffer from over-definition; she from never being defined at all.","proposal":true},{"cn":"可能與赤座玄鬼產生共鳴——但從完全相反的傷口出發。","en":"May resonate with Akaza Genki, but from the opposite wound.","proposal":true},{"cn":"與黑縁的潛在連結：都是被遺棄者，但以不同的方式。","en":"Potential connection with Kuroberi: both abandoned, but in different ways.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"關鍵台詞","en":"Key Lines","pairs":[{"cn":"白妙在第一部無台詞。","en":"Shirotae has no canonical lines in Part One.","proposal":false},{"cn":"「我……在嗎？」","en":"\"Do I… exist?\"","proposal":true},{"cn":"「被遺忘的感覺，比痛更空。」","en":"\"Being forgotten feels emptier than pain.\"","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"聲音與表演備註","en":"Voice & Performance Notes","pairs":[{"cn":"嗓音柔和，常被其他聲音淹沒，需要努力才能聽清。","en":"Voice soft; often submerged beneath other sounds, requiring effort to hear.","proposal":true},{"cn":"說話時有停頓，彷彿隨時準備被打斷。","en":"Speech marked by pauses, as if always ready to be interrupted.","proposal":true},{"cn":"很少主動開口，但當她終於發言時，帶著一種被壓抑許久的脆弱。","en":"Rarely initiates speech, but when she does, it carries long-suppressed fragility.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"未來發展掛鉤","en":"Future Hooks","pairs":[{"cn":"第二部的某一集：隱形作為它自己的暴力——無法被看見的恐懼。","en":"A future episode: invisibility as its own violence—the fear of never being seen.","proposal":true},{"cn":"她測試修行的前提：如果你從未被需要，「指名」對你來說是救贖還是詛咒？","en":"She tests the Naming's premise: if you were never needed, is being named salvation or curse?","proposal":true},{"cn":"可能成為後續故事裡，被遺忘者的聲音。","en":"May become, in future episodes, the voice of the forgotten.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"製作資產清單","en":"Production Asset Checklist","pairs":[{"cn":"概念設定圖","en":"Concept art","proposal":false},{"cn":"三視圖","en":"Character turnaround","proposal":false},{"cn":"表情表","en":"Expression sheet","proposal":false},{"cn":"服裝道具表","en":"Costume & prop sheet","proposal":false},{"cn":"色彩指定","en":"Color script","proposal":false},{"cn":"動態參考","en":"Motion reference","proposal":false},{"cn":"聲優試音方向","en":"VO casting direction","proposal":false},{"cn":"分集出場表","en":"Episode appearance list","proposal":false}]}]},{"id":"10","kanji":"碧吉","romaji":"Aokichi","species_cn":"河童","species_en":"Kappa","archetype_cn":"游離型","archetype_en":"Drifting","archetypeKey":"drifting","color":"#3f8a6e","color2":"#5fb894","priority":"T0","active":true,"roleline":"The first follower; the city's licensed scapegoat","sections":[{"cn":"基本資料","en":"Basic Information","pairs":[{"cn":"全名：碧吉（あおきち），羅馬拼音 Aokichi。","en":"Full name: Aokichi (碧吉), romaji Aokichi.","proposal":false},{"cn":"種族：河童（Kappa）。","en":"Species: kappa.","proposal":false},{"cn":"原型分類：游離型。","en":"Archetype: Drifting.","proposal":false},{"cn":"角色定位：夜行的第一位追隨者。","en":"Role: the first follower of the Night Parade.","proposal":false},{"cn":"初登場：第一章｜停下來的瞬間。","en":"First appearance: Chapter 1 — The Moment He Stopped.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第一部結尾狀態：已獲得自由，不再受限於水；是否進入金寂之光未在書中明確呈現，屬於劇情曖昧留白。","en":"Status at the end of Part One: freed, no longer bound to the water; whether he passes into the golden light is not shown on the page — canon-ambiguous.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"名字由來","en":"Name Etymology","pairs":[{"cn":"名字帶有半開玩笑、親切隨和的意味，意近「幸運的藍綠色」。","en":"The name carries a half-joking, approachable tone, roughly meaning \"lucky blue-green.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"這種輕巧的命名方式，正好對映他「輕浮卻善良」的性格底色。","en":"This light, easygoing naming style directly mirrors his underlying temperament — flippant but kind.","proposal":false},{"cn":"相較於玄鬼、白蓮等莊重的姓名系統，「碧吉」的通俗感標誌他在夜行位階中親民、非王族的定位。","en":"Compared to the solemn naming conventions of figures like Genki or Byakuren, \"Aokichi's\" folksy simplicity marks his approachable, non-royal place in the Parade's hierarchy.","proposal":true},{"cn":"這個名字也暗示他長年被城市當作「熟悉的笑話」看待，而非被真正尊重的存在。","en":"The name also hints at how the city has long treated him as a familiar joke rather than a being to be truly respected.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"氣質與性格","en":"Temperament & Personality","pairs":[{"cn":"性格核心：輕浮卻善良。","en":"Core temperament: flippant but kind.","proposal":false},{"cn":"他習慣用玩笑掩飾恐懼，笑話總是比他的害怕慢半拍出現。","en":"He habitually masks his fear with jokes, the humor always landing half a beat after the fear itself.","proposal":false},{"cn":"他清楚自己是城市裡「被默許存在的笑話」，卻仍選擇善良行事，即使善良為他招來更多責難。","en":"He knows he is the city's licensed joke, tolerated rather than respected — yet he still chooses to act kindly, even when kindness brings him more blame.","proposal":false},{"cn":"他的善良伴隨自我懷疑：「我是不是……犯規了？」正是這種矛盾的體現。","en":"His kindness comes bundled with self-doubt: \"Did I… break the rules?\" captures this contradiction exactly.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"外貌與視覺設計","en":"Appearance & Visual Design","pairs":[{"cn":"濕漉漉的頭部從河水中浮出，像一顆晃動的藍綠色石頭。","en":"A wet head surfaces from the river like a bobbing bluestone.","proposal":false},{"cn":"頭頂有皿（水皿），這是他生存機制的核心。","en":"A dish (皿) rests atop his crown — the core mechanism of his survival.","proposal":false},{"cn":"皿裡的水在他害怕時會晃動，若離水過久則會逐漸乾涸。","en":"The water in the dish sloshes when he is frightened, and slowly dries out if he stays away from the river too long.","proposal":false},{"cn":"移動時會帶起一道濕潤的綠色殘影。","en":"A wet green shadow trails him when he moves.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"背景與象徵","en":"Background & Symbolism","pairs":[{"cn":"河童在城中的角色，是被官方默許、掛牌的笑柄，長年被當作溺水事件的代罪對象。","en":"The kappa's role in the city is that of a licensed, tolerated joke — perpetually blamed for drownings.","proposal":false},{"cn":"他曾將一名溺水的孩子推上岸救活，隔天全城卻傳「是碧吉拉人下水」。","en":"He once pushed a drowning child ashore, saving her — the next day, the whole city said instead that \"Aokichi drags people under.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"他有時會偷瓜，因為扮演眾人預期的角色，比對抗這個角色更容易。","en":"He sometimes steals melons, because playing the role people expect of him is easier than fighting it.","proposal":false},{"cn":"他留下的理由被玄鬼道破：「你留下來，是因為你厭倦被定義。」","en":"Genki names the reason he stays: \"You stay because you are weary of being defined.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"離水太久，皿裡的水會慢慢乾涸——這是他為「留下」所付出的第一個具體代價。","en":"If he stays from the river too long, the water in his dish slowly dries out — the first concrete cost of staying.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"第一部故事線","en":"Part One Story Arc","pairs":[{"cn":"第一至二章：他顫抖著靠近玄鬼，說：「覺得你很像……被丟下了。」","en":"Chapters 1–2: he approaches Genki trembling, saying: \"Felt like you were… kind of left behind.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"第四章：他的身世揭露——被城市當作笑柄與代罪羊，玄鬼站在他與人群之間，未曾出手，只是讓人們看見自己的恐懼。","en":"Chapter 4: his backstory is revealed — the city's licensed joke and scapegoat; Genki stands between him and the mob without attacking, simply letting people see their own fear.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第五章：他違規救下一名陷入火場的孩子，卻遭毆打，被「指名」的陰影蜂擁而至；玄鬼將陰影自他身上撕下。","en":"Chapter 5: he breaks the rule to save a child from a fire, only to be beaten as the shadows of the Naming swarm him; Genki tears the shadows off him.","proposal":false},{"cn":"他問：「我是不是……犯規了？」玄鬼答：「不是。」這是玄鬼第一次將手放在他的肩上，作為支持而非命令。","en":"He asks: \"Did I… break the rules?\" Genki answers: \"No.\" This is the first time Genki lays a hand on his shoulder — an act of support, not command.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第十一至十二章：他留在玄鬼身邊，直至最後。","en":"Chapters 11–12: he stays at Genki's side to the very end.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第十三章：他某天醒來，已不再需要躲入水中；他為玄鬼的孤獨落淚，說：「你會很孤單。」","en":"Chapter 13: he wakes one day no longer needing to hide in water; he weeps for Genki's solitude, saying: \"You'll be so alone.\"","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"人物關係","en":"Relationships","pairs":[{"cn":"玄鬼：第一個真正把手放在他肩上、給予支持而非命令的存在。","en":"Genki: the first being who ever laid a hand on his shoulder in support, not command.","proposal":false},{"cn":"黒縁：彼此鬥嘴，卻是「共同被拋下者」之間真實的溫暖。","en":"Kuroberi: bickering siblings-in-abandonment, with real warmth beneath the teasing.","proposal":false},{"cn":"那名先被他救起、後又被他無意間傷害名聲的孩子：他心中最深的傷口。","en":"The child he once saved from drowning, whose rescue later became the source of his ruined reputation: his deepest wound.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"關鍵台詞","en":"Key Lines","pairs":[{"cn":"「覺得你很像……被丟下了。」","en":"\"Felt like you were… kind of left behind.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「你留下來，是因為你厭倦被定義。」","en":"\"You stay because you are weary of being defined.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「我是不是……犯規了？」","en":"\"Did I… break the rules?\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「你說，我還要不要繼續做好事？」","en":"\"So tell me — should I even keep doing good things?\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「你會很孤單。」","en":"\"You'll be so alone.\"","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"聲音與表演備註","en":"Voice & Performance Notes","pairs":[{"cn":"語速偏快，帶自嘲口吻。","en":"A quick speaking pace, carrying a self-deprecating tone.","proposal":true},{"cn":"笑話的節奏永遠比恐懼慢半拍出現，形成他招牌的喜劇時機。","en":"His jokes always land half a beat after his fear — his signature comic timing.","proposal":true},{"cn":"在莊重或危險場景中，可用突兀的輕鬆語調製造反差張力。","en":"In solemn or dangerous scenes, an incongruously light tone can create contrast and tension.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"未來發展掛鉤","en":"Future Hooks","pairs":[{"cn":"他離水而不需躲藏的轉變，可作為未來集數「河童離開河流意味著什麼」的延伸主題。","en":"His transformation into no longer needing to hide from water could seed a future episode on what it means for a kappa to leave the river behind.","proposal":true},{"cn":"他是否最終走入金寂之光，屬於書中刻意留白的懸念，可作為續集揭曉的關鍵伏筆。","en":"Whether he ultimately enters the golden light is a deliberate narrative gap in the text, and could serve as a key hook to resolve in a sequel.","proposal":true},{"cn":"與黒縁的鬥嘴情誼，可延伸為「被拋下者互相扶持」的支線故事。","en":"His bickering bond with Kuroberi could be expanded into a side story about those who were abandoned supporting one another.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"製作資產清單","en":"Production Asset Checklist","pairs":[{"cn":"概念設定圖：頭頂水皿的結構設計與濕潤河童皮膚質感。","en":"Concept art: structural design of the head-dish and the texture of his wet kappa skin.","proposal":false},{"cn":"三視圖：從河中浮出到完全上岸兩種狀態的體態差異。","en":"Character turnaround: posture differences between surfacing from the river and standing fully on land.","proposal":false},{"cn":"表情表：從自嘲玩笑到恐懼、再到落淚的完整表情序列，強調笑與怕的半拍時差。","en":"Expression sheet: full sequence from self-deprecating jokes to fear to tears, emphasizing the half-beat delay between humor and fear.","proposal":false},{"cn":"服裝道具表：水皿的材質與晃動機關設計規格。","en":"Costume & prop sheet: material and sloshing-mechanism specifications for the head-dish.","proposal":false},{"cn":"色彩指定：河流綠、泥褐、皿水銀灰三色為主軸。","en":"Color script: primary palette of river green, mud brown, and dish-water silver.","proposal":false},{"cn":"動態參考：皿中水晃動與離水乾涸的特效動態參考。","en":"Motion reference: the sloshing water in the head-dish and the drying-out effect once he is out of water.","proposal":false}]}]},{"id":"11","kanji":"黒縁","romaji":"Kuroberi","species_cn":"貓又","species_en":"Nekomata","archetype_cn":"記憶型","archetype_en":"Memory","archetypeKey":"memory","color":"#5a5560","color2":"#c19240","priority":"T0","active":true,"roleline":"The second to stay; memory and conscience with claws","sections":[{"cn":"基本資料","en":"Basic Information","pairs":[{"cn":"全名：黒縁（くろべり），羅馬拼音 Kuroberi。","en":"Full name: Kuroberi (黒縁), romaji Kuroberi.","proposal":false},{"cn":"種族：貓又（Nekomata）。","en":"Species: nekomata.","proposal":false},{"cn":"原型分類：記憶型。","en":"Archetype: Memory.","proposal":false},{"cn":"角色定位：全書的記憶與帶爪良心。","en":"Role: the story's memory and conscience-with-claws.","proposal":false},{"cn":"初登場：第二章｜被留下的夜。","en":"First appearance: Chapter 2 — The Night Left Behind.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第一部結尾狀態：已離開，進入金寂。","en":"Status at the end of Part One: departed, into Golden Stillness.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"名字由來","en":"Name Etymology","pairs":[{"cn":"「黒縁」意為「黑色的邊緣／輪廓」，象徵陰影的邊界。","en":"\"Kuroberi\" means \"black rim/edge,\" symbolizing the border of a shadow.","proposal":false},{"cn":"這個名字暗示她始終站在事件的邊緣觀察，卻從未真正置身事外。","en":"The name implies she always stands at the edge of events, observing — yet is never truly detached from them.","proposal":false},{"cn":"「邊緣」也呼應貓又傳說中「介於家貓與妖物之間」的身分模糊性。","en":"\"Rim/edge\" also echoes the nekomata legend's inherent ambiguity — a creature caught between housecat and yokai.","proposal":true},{"cn":"她視覺設計中的白色滾邊，可視為這個名字最直接的美術轉譯。","en":"The white rim detail in her visual design can be read as the most direct art-direction translation of her name.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"氣質與性格","en":"Temperament & Personality","pairs":[{"cn":"性格核心：冷嘲、記憶強。","en":"Core temperament: sardonic; never forgets.","proposal":false},{"cn":"她以冷嘲作為保護色，真誠只在代價高昂時才顯露。","en":"She uses sardonic wit as camouflage; sincerity surfaces only when it costs her something.","proposal":false},{"cn":"她是留下的第二人，動機並非理念，而是共鳴：「你以為不回應，就不會被拋棄嗎？」","en":"She is the second to stay, moved not by ideals but by resonance: \"Do you think staying silent means you won't be abandoned?\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"她對玄鬼說：「我知道那種感覺。你為人付出，為人承擔，最後人卻說——這本來就是你的樣子。」道出她自身也曾被辜負。","en":"She tells Genki: \"I know that feeling. You give yourself to people, you bear their weight for them, and in the end they say — that's just what you are.\" This reveals she too was once betrayed.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"外貌與視覺設計","en":"Appearance & Visual Design","pairs":[{"cn":"一雙細長的眼睛在黑暗中睜開。","en":"Long, narrow eyes opening in the darkness.","proposal":false},{"cn":"分叉的尾巴掃過屋瓦，動作柔軟而冷冽。","en":"Her forked tail sweeps across roof tiles, the motion soft and cold.","proposal":false},{"cn":"落地時不發出任何聲響。","en":"She lands without a sound.","proposal":false},{"cn":"當夜行有所變動時，她的毛會豎起。","en":"Her fur bristles whenever the Parade shifts.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"背景與象徵","en":"Background & Symbolism","pairs":[{"cn":"她所記得的，是曾經付出卻被人們拋棄的滋味——這份記憶構成她的核心創傷。","en":"What she remembers is the taste of giving herself to people and then being discarded — this memory forms the core of her wound.","proposal":false},{"cn":"她問玄鬼：「鬼大人。被留下的滋味……很不好受吧？」既是提問，也是自身經歷的投射。","en":"She asks Genki: \"Lord Oni. The taste of being left behind… it isn't a good one, is it?\" — at once a question and a projection of her own experience.","proposal":false},{"cn":"作為記憶型角色，她的功能是替全書「記得」——記得誰被拋棄、記得誰的痛被輕描淡寫。","en":"As the story's Memory archetype, her function is to remember for the whole cast — who was abandoned, whose pain was waved away.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"第一部故事線","en":"Part One Story Arc","pairs":[{"cn":"第二章：她是繼碧吉之後第二位留下的角色，出於共鳴而非理念。","en":"Chapter 2: she becomes the second character to stay, after Aokichi — moved by resonance, not ideals.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第八章：她準確讀出綾女的處境，說：「她不是在失控。她是在證明自己存在。」","en":"Chapter 8: she reads Ayame's situation with precision, saying: \"She is not losing control. She is proving she exists.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"第八章：她對修行下了評語：「這比打架難多了。」","en":"Chapter 8: she offers her verdict on the Practice: \"This is a lot harder than fighting.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"第十一章：面對即將發生的離散，她低聲說：「真的會消失。」","en":"Chapter 11: facing the coming departures, she says quietly: \"It really will disappear.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"第十三章：某個清晨，她靜靜化作光。","en":"Chapter 13: one quiet morning, she becomes light.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"人物關係","en":"Relationships","pairs":[{"cn":"玄鬼：她替他說出他自己不願說出口的傷。","en":"Genki: she says aloud the wounds he refuses to voice himself.","proposal":false},{"cn":"碧吉：彼此鬥嘴，卻懷有真實的溫暖。","en":"Aokichi: mutual teasing, with real warmth underneath.","proposal":false},{"cn":"那些曾拋棄她的人類：她始終記得的傷痕來源。","en":"The humans who once discarded her: the source of the wound she keeps as memory.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"關鍵台詞","en":"Key Lines","pairs":[{"cn":"「你以為不回應，就不會被拋棄嗎？」","en":"\"Do you think staying silent means you won't be abandoned?\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「我知道那種感覺。你為人付出，為人承擔，最後人卻說——這本來就是你的樣子。」","en":"\"I know that feeling. You give yourself to people, you bear their weight for them, and in the end they say — that's just what you are.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「這比打架難多了。」","en":"\"This is a lot harder than fighting.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「真的會消失。」","en":"\"It really will disappear.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"「鬼大人。被留下的滋味……很不好受吧？」","en":"\"Lord Oni. The taste of being left behind… it isn't a good one, is it?\"","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"聲音與表演備註","en":"Voice & Performance Notes","pairs":[{"cn":"聲音基調：乾燥、帶著貓科的呼嚕式諷刺感。","en":"Vocal baseline: dry, with a purring, feline irony.","proposal":true},{"cn":"真誠只在代價高昂時才會顯露，聲線需在冷嘲與突然的坦率之間切換。","en":"Sincerity should surface only when it costs her; the voice needs to shift between sardonic wit and sudden candor.","proposal":true},{"cn":"表演上建議以極簡的音量變化傳達情緒重量，避免誇張的情緒外顯。","en":"Performance should convey emotional weight through minimal volume shifts, avoiding overt emotional display.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"未來發展掛鉤","en":"Future Hooks","pairs":[{"cn":"她「記憶型」的定位，可作為未來集數回顧全書事件的敘事錨點角色。","en":"Her Memory-archetype role could serve as a narrative anchor for future episodes that revisit events across the whole story.","proposal":true},{"cn":"她口中「曾拋棄她的人類」的具體事件尚未展開，可作為她的獨立支線或前傳素材。","en":"The specific incident behind \"the humans who once discarded her\" has not yet been depicted and could become material for her own side story or prequel.","proposal":true},{"cn":"與碧吉的鬥嘴情誼，可延伸為「被拋下者互相扶持」的支線故事。","en":"Her bickering bond with Aokichi could be expanded into a side story about those who were abandoned supporting one another.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"製作資產清單","en":"Production Asset Checklist","pairs":[{"cn":"概念設定圖：細長雙眼與分叉尾巴的核心設計圖。","en":"Concept art: core design study of her long narrow eyes and forked tail.","proposal":false},{"cn":"三視圖：屋瓦間無聲落地姿態與靜止站姿的三視圖。","en":"Character turnaround: silent roof-landing pose versus standing-still pose from three angles.","proposal":false},{"cn":"表情表：從冷嘲到毛髮豎起、再到罕見坦率瞬間的表情序列。","en":"Expression sheet: sequence from sardonic composure to bristling fur to rare moments of candor.","proposal":false},{"cn":"服裝道具表：毛色與「黑色邊緣」白色滾邊細節的規格表。","en":"Costume & prop sheet: specifications for her fur coloring and the white \"rim\" edge detail.","proposal":false},{"cn":"色彩指定：煤黑、燈籠琥珀（眼睛）、一線白邊為主軸。","en":"Color script: primary palette of soot black, lantern amber (eyes), and a single white rim line.","proposal":false},{"cn":"動態參考：無聲落地與尾巴掃過屋瓦的動態參考。","en":"Motion reference: reference for silent landings and the tail sweeping across roof tiles.","proposal":false},{"cn":"聲優試音方向：需具備乾燥諷刺的聲線基底，並能在單句台詞中轉出真誠的裂縫。","en":"VO casting direction: needs a baseline of dry, sardonic delivery, capable of cracking into sincerity within a single line.","proposal":false},{"cn":"分集出場表：第二章初登場，第八章為核心洞察集，第十一至十三章為結局告別集。","en":"Episode appearance list: first appears in Chapter 2; Chapter 8 is her core insight episode; Chapters 11–13 are her farewell episodes.","proposal":false}]}]},{"id":"12","kanji":"紅緒","romaji":"Benio","species_cn":"妖狐","species_en":"Yōko","archetype_cn":"游離型","archetype_en":"Drifting","archetypeKey":"drifting","color":"#3f8a6e","color2":"#5fb894","priority":"T2","active":false,"roleline":"Vanity's trickster — reserved for Part Two","sections":[{"cn":"基本資料","en":"Basic Information","pairs":[{"cn":"名字：紅緒（べんお）","en":"Name: Benio","proposal":false},{"cn":"妖怪種類：妖狐（ようこ）","en":"Species: yōko (wild fox)","proposal":false},{"cn":"人物原型：游離型（無定所的輕巧）","en":"Archetype: Drifting (unattached lightness)","proposal":false},{"cn":"第一部初登場：無","en":"First Appearance in Part One: None","proposal":false},{"cn":"角色身份：保留至後續分集","en":"Status: Reserved for future episodes","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"名字由來","en":"Name Etymology","pairs":[{"cn":"紅緒是「紅色的線」之意——象徵牽引與連結。","en":"Benio means \"red cord,\" symbolizing connection and binding threads.","proposal":false},{"cn":"對應九條白蓮的高貴：紅緒是野性的、街頭的、來自底層的。","en":"In contrast to Kujō Byakuren's nobility: Benio is wild, street-level, from below.","proposal":false},{"cn":"紅色也象徵她的輕浮與狡詐——既誘人又危險。","en":"Red also embodies her levity and cunning—both alluring and perilous.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"氣質與性格","en":"Temperament & Personality","pairs":[{"cn":"游離、輕巧，不執著於任何事物或任何人。","en":"Drifting and light-footed, unattached to anything or anyone.","proposal":false},{"cn":"與九條白蓮相比：白蓮是宮廷的理性型狐；紅緒是街道的野性狐。","en":"In contrast to Byakuren: Byakuren is the courtly rational fox; Benio is the street's wild fox.","proposal":false},{"cn":"表面嘻嘻哈哈，實則精於觀察與操弄。","en":"Superficially flippant, yet keenly observant and subtly manipulative.","proposal":true},{"cn":"修行第一條對她是反面戰場：她天生善於「為證明自己而動」。","en":"The First Precept is her inverse battlefield: she is naturally prone to \"acting to prove herself.\"","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"外貌與視覺設計","en":"Appearance & Visual Design","pairs":[{"cn":"膚色溫暖的蜜色或淡金色。","en":"Warm honey or pale golden complexion.","proposal":true},{"cn":"眼睛琥珀色，帶著狡黠的光芒；尾巴細長有力，顏色若隱若現。","en":"Amber eyes glinting with cunning; tail slender and strong, appearing and vanishing.","proposal":true},{"cn":"衣著輕薄、活動自由，主要色彩為紅色與暖橙。","en":"Light, unrestricted garments in red and warm orange tones.","proposal":true},{"cn":"調色：紅色絲線、狐狸琥珀、暮光玫瑰。","en":"Palette: vermilion cord red, fox amber, dusk rose.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"背景與象徵","en":"Background & Symbolism","pairs":[{"cn":"妖狐（野狐）在傳說中是狡猾與變化的象徵，不似九尾狐的高遠與威嚴。","en":"The yōko (wild fox) in legend embodies cunning and transformation, unlike the nine-tailed fox's nobility and majesty.","proposal":false},{"cn":"在『金無垢』中，紅緒代表那些在官方敘事之外的妖怪——邊緣、取巧、求生。","en":"In Kinmuku, Benio represents those yokai outside the official narrative—marginal, clever, surviving.","proposal":true},{"cn":"她可能是已被命名妖怪與未來世界之間的使者。","en":"She may be a messenger between the named yokai and whatever comes after.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"第一部故事線","en":"Part One Story Arc","pairs":[{"cn":"紅緒不出現在第一部故事中。","en":"Benio does not appear in Part One.","proposal":false},{"cn":"保留至後續分集。","en":"Reserved for future episodes.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"人物關係","en":"Relationships","pairs":[{"cn":"與九條白蓮的微妙對立：同為狐，卻代表階級與價值觀的分裂。","en":"Subtle opposition with Byakuren: both foxes, yet representing a rift in hierarchy and values.","proposal":true},{"cn":"可能成為後續故事的樞紐角色——她對所有人都有所知，卻不對任何人完全效忠。","en":"May become a pivot character in future episodes—knowing something of everyone yet wholly loyal to none.","proposal":true},{"cn":"與赤座玄鬼的潛在互動：她代表那些修行之外的選擇。","en":"Potential interaction with Akaza Genki: she represents choices outside the Practice.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"關鍵台詞","en":"Key Lines","pairs":[{"cn":"紅緒在第一部無台詞。","en":"Benio has no canonical lines in Part One.","proposal":false},{"cn":"「我為什麼要證明什麼？我活著，就夠了。」","en":"\"Why should I prove anything? That I live is enough.\"","proposal":true},{"cn":"「證明自己？太累了。我更喜歡讓別人猜。」","en":"\"Prove myself? Too exhausting. I prefer to let them guess.\"","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"聲音與表演備註","en":"Voice & Performance Notes","pairs":[{"cn":"嗓音輕快、歌唱般，帶著轉音的靈巧感。","en":"Voice light and melodic, nimble with inflection.","proposal":true},{"cn":"說話速度快，常用轉折避免直答。","en":"Speech quick; often deflects rather than answers directly.","proposal":true},{"cn":"笑聲頻繁，但笑聲往往掩蓋了她真實的意圖。","en":"Laughter frequent, but often masks her true intent.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"未來發展掛鉤","en":"Future Hooks","pairs":[{"cn":"第二部的某一集：狡詐作為一種生存方式——不是惡，只是另一條路。","en":"A future episode: cunning as a survival strategy—not evil, just another path.","proposal":true},{"cn":"她測試修行第一條的反面：如果一切都是為了存活，「證明」本身是虛幻的。","en":"She tests the inverse of the First Precept: if all is for survival, \"proof\" itself is illusion.","proposal":true},{"cn":"可能成為已離去妖怪與人世之間的信使。","en":"May become a messenger between the departed yokai and the human world.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"製作資產清單","en":"Production Asset Checklist","pairs":[{"cn":"概念設定圖","en":"Concept art","proposal":false},{"cn":"三視圖","en":"Character turnaround","proposal":false},{"cn":"表情表","en":"Expression sheet","proposal":false},{"cn":"服裝道具表","en":"Costume & prop sheet","proposal":false},{"cn":"色彩指定","en":"Color script","proposal":false},{"cn":"動態參考","en":"Motion reference","proposal":false},{"cn":"聲優試音方向","en":"VO casting direction","proposal":false},{"cn":"分集出場表","en":"Episode appearance list","proposal":false}]}]},{"id":"13","kanji":"玉藻静香","romaji":"Tamamo Shizuka","species_cn":"玉藻前","species_en":"Tamamo-no-Mae","archetype_cn":"理性型","archetype_en":"Reason","archetypeKey":"reason","color":"#4f7398","color2":"#9cc0e0","priority":"T2","active":false,"roleline":"Byakuren's buried failure — referenced, prequel key","sections":[{"cn":"基本資料","en":"Basic Information","pairs":[{"cn":"名字：玉藻静香（たまもしずか）","en":"Name: Tamamo Shizuka","proposal":false},{"cn":"妖怪種類：玉藻前（たまものまえ）","en":"Species: Tamamo-no-Mae","proposal":false},{"cn":"人物原型：理性型（被安排的棋子）","en":"Archetype: Reason (the arranged pawn)","proposal":false},{"cn":"第一部初登場：第一章提及（非舞台出場）","en":"First Appearance in Part One: Referenced in Chapter 1 (not on stage)","proposal":false},{"cn":"角色身份：保留至後續分集","en":"Status: Reserved for future episodes","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"名字由來","en":"Name Etymology","pairs":[{"cn":"玉藻（たまも）是古典傳說中的狐妖之名，象徵華麗與誘惑。","en":"Tamamo is the name of the legendary fox spirit, symbolizing beauty and seduction.","proposal":false},{"cn":"静香（しずか）意為「靜謐的香氣」，帶著優雅卻淡漠的氣質。","en":"Shizuka means \"quiet fragrance,\" bearing elegance yet indifference.","proposal":false},{"cn":"名字本身就是一場安排——華美的外殼包著虛空。","en":"The name itself is an arrangement—gorgeous exterior containing emptiness.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"氣質與性格","en":"Temperament & Personality","pairs":[{"cn":"她不是以自己的意志行動，而是以被設計的身份存在。","en":"She does not act by her own will but exists as a designed identity.","proposal":false},{"cn":"理性型的扭曲——理性被用來為他人的計劃服務，而非自我抉擇。","en":"A twisted Reason archetype—rationality deployed to serve others' plans, not self-determination.","proposal":true},{"cn":"她的沉寂不是內斂，而是一種被禁止的狀態。","en":"Her quietness is not restraint but a state of enforced silence.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"外貌與視覺設計","en":"Appearance & Visual Design","pairs":[{"cn":"雍容華貴的古典妝扮，彷彿永遠停留在某個儀式的時刻。","en":"Dignified classical appearance, as if frozen in a ceremonial moment.","proposal":true},{"cn":"配色華麗而冷調，以金色與紫色為主。","en":"Sumptuous yet cool palette, dominated by gold and purple.","proposal":true},{"cn":"眼神空洞，彷彿靈魂早已離去。","en":"Eyes hollow, as if the soul departed long ago.","proposal":true},{"cn":"調色：華麗的金色、深紫、淡金色調。","en":"Palette: sumptuous gold, deep purple, pale aureate tone.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"背景與象徵","en":"Background & Symbolism","pairs":[{"cn":"玉藻前是日本古傳說中的狐妖，據說因其美貌與魅惑被皇帝所寵愛，最後卻被發現為妖怪而遭到驅逐。","en":"Tamamo-no-Mae is a fox spirit from classical Japanese legend, said to have been the emperor's beloved for her beauty and seduction, only to be discovered and driven out.","proposal":false},{"cn":"在『金無垢』的故事前史中，她是九條白蓮古老計劃的失敗者——「把罪推到一個人身上，這樣所有人都可以假裝無辜」。","en":"In Kinmuku's prehistory, she is the failure of Byakuren's ancient scheme—\"push sin onto one name so everyone may keep pretending innocence.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"她代表制度化的暴力——被設計、被利用、被拋棄的妖怪。","en":"She represents systemic violence—the designed, used, discarded yokai.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"第一部故事線","en":"Part One Story Arc","pairs":[{"cn":"玉藻静香在第一部故事的第一章中被提及，但未出場。","en":"Tamamo Shizuka is referenced in Chapter 1 of Part One but does not appear on stage.","proposal":false},{"cn":"九條白蓮在回憶中說出她的失敗——當年的計劃試圖以玉藻为代罪羊，卻導致了反效果。","en":"Byakuren recalls her failure in memory—the old plan attempted to make Tamamo a scapegoat, only to backfire catastrophically.","proposal":false},{"cn":"保留至後續分集（前傳故事）。","en":"Reserved for future episodes (prequel narrative).","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"人物關係","en":"Relationships","pairs":[{"cn":"與九條白蓮：過去的受害者與加害者之間的沈默關係。","en":"With Byakuren: the unspoken relationship between past victim and perpetrator.","proposal":false},{"cn":"她的存在可能是後續故事中白蓮須要面對的鬼魂。","en":"Her existence may be the ghost Byakuren must confront in future episodes.","proposal":true},{"cn":"與赤座玄鬼的潛在聯繫：都是被命名與使用的容器。","en":"Potential connection with Akaza Genki: both vessels named and used.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"關鍵台詞","en":"Key Lines","pairs":[{"cn":"玉藻静香在第一部無直接台詞。","en":"Tamamo Shizuka has no direct lines in Part One.","proposal":false},{"cn":"「我是被選中的……或者說，我是被創造出來的。」","en":"\"I was chosen… or rather, I was created.\"","proposal":true},{"cn":"「罪不是我的。但我成了它的容器。」","en":"\"The sin was not mine. Yet I became its vessel.\"","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"聲音與表演備註","en":"Voice & Performance Notes","pairs":[{"cn":"嗓音高雅優美，卻帶著一種機械般的冷淡。","en":"Voice elegant and refined, yet tinged with mechanical coldness.","proposal":true},{"cn":"言辭華麗但無感情——彷彿根據劇本而非本心說話。","en":"Speech ornate but affectless, as if recited rather than felt.","proposal":true},{"cn":"長時間沉默是她的特徵；當她開口時，往往已是訣別之言。","en":"Prolonged silence characterizes her; when she speaks, it is often a farewell.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"未來發展掛鉤","en":"Future Hooks","pairs":[{"cn":"前傳故事：玉藻与九條白蓮——過去的安排是如何造成現在的悖論。","en":"Prequel episode: Tamamo and Byakuren—how the past arrangement created today's paradox.","proposal":true},{"cn":"她是否真正「消失」，還是存在於某處？這是『金無垢』宇宙的開放謎題。","en":"Did she truly \"disappear,\" or does she exist somewhere? This is an open mystery of the Kinmuku cosmos.","proposal":true},{"cn":"她的故事可能揭示修行本身的局限——即使修行也無法救贖被制度化犧牲的人。","en":"Her story may reveal the limits of the Practice itself—even the Practice cannot redeem those sacrificed by the system.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"製作資產清單","en":"Production Asset Checklist","pairs":[{"cn":"概念設定圖","en":"Concept art","proposal":false},{"cn":"三視圖","en":"Character turnaround","proposal":false},{"cn":"表情表","en":"Expression sheet","proposal":false},{"cn":"服裝道具表","en":"Costume & prop sheet","proposal":false},{"cn":"色彩指定","en":"Color script","proposal":false},{"cn":"動態參考","en":"Motion reference","proposal":false},{"cn":"聲優試音方向","en":"VO casting direction","proposal":false},{"cn":"分集出場表","en":"Episode appearance list","proposal":false}]}]},{"id":"14","kanji":"峰","romaji":"Mine","species_cn":"山姥","species_en":"Yamanba","archetype_cn":"母性型","archetype_en":"Maternal","archetypeKey":"maternal","color":"#a97b3c","color2":"#d6ab63","priority":"T3","active":false,"roleline":"Devouring-as-protecting — reserved for Part Two","sections":[{"cn":"基本資料","en":"Basic Information","pairs":[{"cn":"名字：峰（みね）","en":"Name: Mine","proposal":false},{"cn":"妖怪種類：山姥（やまんば）","en":"Species: yamanba (mountain witch)","proposal":false},{"cn":"人物原型：母性型（吞噬即保護）","en":"Archetype: Maternal (devouring as protection)","proposal":false},{"cn":"第一部初登場：無","en":"First Appearance in Part One: None","proposal":false},{"cn":"角色身份：保留至後續分集","en":"Status: Reserved for future episodes","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"名字由來","en":"Name Etymology","pairs":[{"cn":"峰（みね）意為「山峰」——簡潔而直率，毫無修飾。","en":"Mine means \"peak\"—plain and direct, unadorned.","proposal":false},{"cn":"名字帶著山野的氣息，不屬於都市的妖怪。","en":"The name carries the breath of mountains, belonging to no city yokai.","proposal":false},{"cn":"簡潔的名字反映了她的本質——大地、直率、母性。","en":"The simple name reflects her nature—earth, directness, motherhood.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"氣質與性格","en":"Temperament & Personality","pairs":[{"cn":"強勢的母性——既保護，也吞噬。","en":"Forceful maternity—both protective and devouring.","proposal":false},{"cn":"不同於都市中的精巧與算計，峰代表原始的、本能的力量。","en":"Unlike urban sophistication and scheming, Mine embodies primal, instinctive force.","proposal":false},{"cn":"她的關懷是壓倒性的——會為了保護你而吞噬你。","en":"Her care is overwhelming—she will devour you to protect you.","proposal":true},{"cn":"沒有優雅與迂迴，只有直接而沈重的存在。","en":"No grace, no circumlocution—only direct and weighty presence.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"外貌與視覺設計","en":"Appearance & Visual Design","pairs":[{"cn":"身形魁梧而肌肉發達，彷彿大地本身長出了形體。","en":"Robust and muscular form, as if the earth itself took shape.","proposal":true},{"cn":"皮膚呈現大地的褐色，帶著泥土與火焰的紋理。","en":"Skin in earthy brown, bearing the texture of soil and flame.","proposal":true},{"cn":"長髮粗獷而蓬亂，編織著樹枝與植物。","en":"Hair wild and unkempt, woven with twigs and foliage.","proposal":true},{"cn":"眼睛炯炯有神，帶著母獸般的溫暖與危險。","en":"Eyes bright with a mother beast's warmth and peril.","proposal":true},{"cn":"調色：大地赭色、森林暗色、爐火溫暖。","en":"Palette: earth ochre, forest dark, hearth fire.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"背景與象徵","en":"Background & Symbolism","pairs":[{"cn":"山姥在日本傳說中既是保護者也是獵食者——撫養英雄的母親，同時吞食迷路的旅人。","en":"The yamanba in Japanese legend is both protector and predator—the mother who raises heroes, simultaneously devouring lost travelers.","proposal":false},{"cn":"在『金無垢』中，峰代表都市之外的恐懼——山野中的害怕是另一種形態。","en":"In Kinmuku, Mine represents fear beyond the city—terror in the wilderness wears a different mask.","proposal":true},{"cn":"她的存在提出一個問題：母性與掠食何時重疊？愛與佔有如何界分？","en":"Her existence poses a question: when do motherhood and predation overlap? How to distinguish love from possession?","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"第一部故事線","en":"Part One Story Arc","pairs":[{"cn":"峰不出現在第一部故事中。","en":"Mine does not appear in Part One.","proposal":false},{"cn":"保留至後續分集。","en":"Reserved for future episodes.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"人物關係","en":"Relationships","pairs":[{"cn":"與赤座玄鬼的可能對照：他承擔都市的恐懼，她統治山野的恐懼。","en":"Possible contrast with Akaza Genki: he bears urban fear, she rules the fear of wilderness.","proposal":true},{"cn":"與其他妖怪的斷裂——她來自完全不同的世界，夜行從未進入山野。","en":"A break from other yokai—she comes from an entirely different world, the Night Parade never entered the mountains.","proposal":true},{"cn":"可能與農村的人類有著複雜的共生關係。","en":"May have a complex symbiotic relationship with rural humans.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"關鍵台詞","en":"Key Lines","pairs":[{"cn":"峰在第一部無台詞。","en":"Mine has no canonical lines in Part One.","proposal":false},{"cn":"「我吃的不是你。我吃的是你的執念。」","en":"\"I do not eat you. I eat your obsession.\"","proposal":true},{"cn":"「保護，有時就是吞噬。你明白嗎？」","en":"\"Protection sometimes means devouring. Do you understand?\"","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"聲音與表演備註","en":"Voice & Performance Notes","pairs":[{"cn":"嗓音粗嘎而有力，帶著山風的蕭瑟感。","en":"Voice rough and powerful, carrying the desolation of mountain wind.","proposal":true},{"cn":"說話大聲而直率，不留迴旋空間。","en":"Speech loud and forthright, leaving no room for subtlety.","proposal":true},{"cn":"笑聲是深沈的、令人生畏的，卻又帶著真實的溫暖。","en":"Laughter deep and awe-inspiring, yet carrying genuine warmth.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"未來發展掛鉤","en":"Future Hooks","pairs":[{"cn":"第二部的某一集：山村的故事——恐懼在都市之外的池塘裡沈澱。","en":"A future episode: the mountain village story—fear pooled in waters the Parade never reached.","proposal":true},{"cn":"她測試母性本身的界限——保護與佔有、愛與吞噬何時變成同一件事。","en":"She tests the limits of motherhood itself—when protection becomes possession, love becomes devouring.","proposal":true},{"cn":"可能是後續故事裡，失落世界與人類世界的橋樑。","en":"May become, in future episodes, the bridge between the lost world and the human one.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"製作資產清單","en":"Production Asset Checklist","pairs":[{"cn":"概念設定圖","en":"Concept art","proposal":false},{"cn":"三視圖","en":"Character turnaround","proposal":false},{"cn":"表情表","en":"Expression sheet","proposal":false},{"cn":"服裝道具表","en":"Costume & prop sheet","proposal":false},{"cn":"色彩指定","en":"Color script","proposal":false},{"cn":"動態參考","en":"Motion reference","proposal":false},{"cn":"聲優試音方向","en":"VO casting direction","proposal":false},{"cn":"分集出場表","en":"Episode appearance list","proposal":false}]}]},{"id":"15","kanji":"黒潮","romaji":"Kuroshio","species_cn":"海坊主","species_en":"Umibōzu","archetype_cn":"重力型","archetype_en":"Gravity","archetypeKey":"gravity","color":"#8b2f28","color2":"#c0453b","priority":"T3","active":false,"roleline":"The sea's silent pressure — reserved for Part Two","sections":[{"cn":"基本資料","en":"Basic Information","pairs":[{"cn":"名字：黒潮（くろしお）","en":"Name: Kuroshio","proposal":false},{"cn":"妖怪種類：海坊主（うみぼうず）","en":"Species: umibōzu (sea monk)","proposal":false},{"cn":"人物原型：重力型（無法抵抗的沈重）","en":"Archetype: Gravity (inescapable weight)","proposal":false},{"cn":"第一部初登場：無","en":"First Appearance in Part One: None","proposal":false},{"cn":"角色身份：保留至後續分集","en":"Status: Reserved for future episodes","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"名字由來","en":"Name Etymology","pairs":[{"cn":"黒潮是日本南部的一股溫暖海流，帶著強大的洋流力量。","en":"Kuroshio is the warm ocean current off Japan's southern coast, bearing tremendous force.","proposal":false},{"cn":"「潮」代表不可逆的、循環的力量——漲潮與退潮永不停歇。","en":"\"Shio\" (tide) represents irreversible, cyclical force—tides that never cease.","proposal":false},{"cn":"名字本身就是自然的沈重——你無法改變洋流，只能被它改變。","en":"The name itself embodies natural weight—you cannot change the current, only be changed by it.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"氣質與性格","en":"Temperament & Personality","pairs":[{"cn":"沉默而有壓迫感，幾乎不發聲。","en":"Silent and oppressive, scarcely speaking at all.","proposal":false},{"cn":"重力型的最極致表現——存在本身就是壓力。","en":"The Gravity archetype in its purest form—mere presence is pressure.","proposal":false},{"cn":"不像赤座玄鬼的沈重來自内在掙扎，黒潮的沈重是外在的、不可抗的。","en":"Unlike Genki's weight born of inner struggle, Kuroshio's weight is external and irresistible.","proposal":true},{"cn":"他代表那些無法被言語改變、只能被時間或力量改變的東西。","en":"He represents what cannot be changed by words, only by time or force.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"外貌與視覺設計","en":"Appearance & Visual Design","pairs":[{"cn":"身形龐大而幽暗，彷彿海本身穿上了人的外衣。","en":"Enormous and shadowed form, as if the sea itself wore a human shape.","proposal":true},{"cn":"膚色深海的黑藍色，帶著不透光的質感。","en":"Deep-sea black-blue skin with opaque texture.","proposal":true},{"cn":"眼睛如深淵般空洞，卻含著某種絕對的觀察。","en":"Eyes hollow as the abyss, yet containing absolute observation.","proposal":true},{"cn":"衣著簡樸，如海水浸透後的布料。","en":"Simple garments like cloth soaked through with seawater.","proposal":true},{"cn":"調色：深海黑藍、泡沫白、無月的灰。","en":"Palette: deep sea black-blue, foam white, moonless grey.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"背景與象徵","en":"Background & Symbolism","pairs":[{"cn":"海坊主在傳說中是海上的恐怖化身——無形、無聲、無可逃脫。","en":"The umibōzu in legend is the terror of the sea—formless, silent, inescapable.","proposal":false},{"cn":"在『金無垢』中，黒潮代表都市之外的另一種恐懼——開放海洋的恐怖。","en":"In Kinmuku, Kuroshio represents a different fear beyond the city—the terror of open sea.","proposal":true},{"cn":"漁村的恐懼與江戶城的恐懼是兩個獨立的世界，夜行從未進入過。","en":"The fear of fishing villages and Edo Castle are two separate worlds the Parade never entered.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"第一部故事線","en":"Part One Story Arc","pairs":[{"cn":"黒潮不出現在第一部故事中。","en":"Kuroshio does not appear in Part One.","proposal":false},{"cn":"保留至後續分集。","en":"Reserved for future episodes.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"人物關係","en":"Relationships","pairs":[{"cn":"與赤座玄鬼的隔絕對照：他是都市的承擔者，黒潮是海洋的孤獨者。","en":"Inverted contrast with Akaza Genki: Genki bears the city's burden; Kuroshio dwells in the sea's solitude.","proposal":false},{"cn":"與其他妖怪完全分離——他可能是夜行從未觸及的存在。","en":"Utterly separated from all other yokai—he may be a being the Night Parade never touched.","proposal":true},{"cn":"可能與漁民形成某種無言的共生關係。","en":"May share an unspoken symbiotic relationship with fishers.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"關鍵台詞","en":"Key Lines","pairs":[{"cn":"黒潮在第一部無台詞。","en":"Kuroshio has no canonical lines in Part One.","proposal":false},{"cn":"「……」","en":"\"…\"","proposal":true},{"cn":"「潮，會改變。人，不改變。」","en":"\"Tide changes. People do not.\"","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"聲音與表演備註","en":"Voice & Performance Notes","pairs":[{"cn":"幾乎沒有嗓音——呼吸聲、水流聲才是他的「語言」。","en":"Scarcely any voice—breath and water are his \"language.\"","proposal":true},{"cn":"偶爾發聲時，音色深沈而遙遠，彷彿從海底傳來。","en":"When he rarely speaks, tone is deep and remote, as if from the seabed.","proposal":true},{"cn":"長時間無言是他的特徵——沈默就是他的在場。","en":"Prolonged silence defines him—silence is his presence.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"未來發展掛鉤","en":"Future Hooks","pairs":[{"cn":"第二部的某一集：漁村的故事——一個夜行從未進入的地方。","en":"A future episode: the fishing village story—a place the Parade never entered.","proposal":true},{"cn":"他提出一個根本的問題：如果修行是為了「在不被需要時仍然存在」，那麼從未被夜行接納過的妖怪呢？","en":"He poses a fundamental question: if the Practice teaches \"existence when unneeded,\" what of those the Parade never claimed?","proposal":true},{"cn":"他的金寂是什麼？沉入深海，還是其他？","en":"What is his Golden Stillness? Descent into the abyss, or something else?","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"製作資產清單","en":"Production Asset Checklist","pairs":[{"cn":"概念設定圖","en":"Concept art","proposal":false},{"cn":"三視圖","en":"Character turnaround","proposal":false},{"cn":"表情表","en":"Expression sheet","proposal":false},{"cn":"服裝道具表","en":"Costume & prop sheet","proposal":false},{"cn":"色彩指定","en":"Color script","proposal":false},{"cn":"動態參考","en":"Motion reference","proposal":false},{"cn":"聲優試音方向","en":"VO casting direction","proposal":false},{"cn":"分集出場表","en":"Episode appearance list","proposal":false}]}]}],"precepts":[{"n":1,"cn":"不為證明而動／不為他們證明自己","en":"Do not act to prove yourself."},{"n":2,"cn":"承受質疑，而不反擊","en":"Bear doubt without striking back."},{"n":3,"cn":"不為他人背負","en":"Do not carry what belongs to others."},{"n":4,"cn":"即使失敗，也不後悔","en":"Even in failure, no regret."},{"n":5,"cn":"面對忠誠，不摧毀","en":"Faced with loyalty, do not destroy it."},{"n":6,"cn":"承認情緒，而不被情緒定義","en":"Acknowledge emotion; do not be defined by it."},{"n":7,"cn":"不否認過去","en":"Do not deny the past."},{"n":8,"cn":"不怨","en":"Do not resent."}],"terms":[{"cn":"赤座玄鬼","en":"Akaza Genki (\"Genki\" in running text)","note":"the oni; male lead"},{"cn":"九條白蓮","en":"Kujō Byakuren (\"Byakuren\")","note":"nine-tailed fox (kyūbi no kitsune); female lead"},{"cn":"大江炎馬","en":"Ōe Enma (\"Enma\")","note":"Shuten-dōji"},{"cn":"茨木義牙","en":"Ibaraki Giga (\"Giga\")","note":"Ibaraki-dōji"},{"cn":"鞍馬烏嶽","en":"Kurama Ugaku (\"Ugaku\")","note":"tengu"},{"cn":"鞍馬白嶺","en":"Kurama Hakurei (\"Hakurei\")","note":"daitengu"},{"cn":"霜月澄","en":"Shimotsuki Sumi (\"Sumi\")","note":"yuki-onna"},{"cn":"綾女","en":"Ayame","note":"hannya"},{"cn":"白妙","en":"Shirotae","note":"hone-onna"},{"cn":"碧吉","en":"Aokichi","note":"kappa"},{"cn":"黒縁／黑縁","en":"Kuroberi","note":"nekomata"},{"cn":"紅緒","en":"Benio","note":"yōko (wild fox)"},{"cn":"玉藻静香","en":"Tamamo Shizuka","note":"Tamamo-no-Mae"},{"cn":"峰","en":"Mine","note":"yamanba"},{"cn":"黒潮","en":"Kuroshio","note":"umibōzu"},{"cn":"新之助","en":"Shinnosuke","note":"human; young woodblock carver"},{"cn":"炎馬大人","en":"Lord Enma","note":"honorific 大人 → \"Lord ___\""},{"cn":"鬼大人","en":"Lord Oni","note":""},{"cn":"百鬼夜行","en":"the Night Parade","note":"First mention per chapter may gloss: \"the Night Parade of a Hundred Demons (Hyakki Yagyō)\". Thereafter: \"the Night Parade\" or \"the Parade\"."},{"cn":"夜行","en":"the Parade / the Night Parade","note":""},{"cn":"妖怪","en":"yokai","note":"lowercase, no italics"},{"cn":"鬼","en":"oni","note":"lowercase generic; the character = Genki"},{"cn":"無垢界","en":"the Immaculate Realm","note":"may gloss once: \"(Mukukai)\""},{"cn":"金寂","en":"Golden Stillness","note":"may gloss once: \"(Kinjaku)\". Chapter 13 title: \"Golden Stillness\"."},{"cn":"指名","en":"Naming / to name","note":"capital-N when the concept: \"the Naming\""},{"cn":"回收","en":"to reclaim / reclamation","note":"fear is \"reclaimed\" by the Parade"},{"cn":"承擔","en":"to bear / bearing","note":"never \"shoulder\" — keep \"bear\""},{"cn":"容器","en":"vessel","note":""},{"cn":"出口","en":"outlet","note":"\"people need an outlet\""},{"cn":"偏見","en":"prejudice","note":""},{"cn":"修行","en":"the Practice","note":"capital P"},{"cn":"修行第N條","en":"the Nth Precept","note":"e.g. 修行第一條 → \"The First Precept.\""},{"cn":"皿","en":"dish","note":"the water dish on a kappa's crown: \"his dish\""},{"cn":"陰陽師","en":"onmyōji","note":""},{"cn":"百物語","en":"hyakumonogatari","note":"ghost-story gatherings"},{"cn":"河童","en":"kappa","note":""},{"cn":"貓又","en":"nekomata","note":""},{"cn":"般若","en":"hannya","note":"the mask: \"hannya mask\""},{"cn":"戌時","en":"the hour of the Dog","note":"c. 8 p.m."}],"chapterTitles":[{"cn":"序章｜夜行之常","en":"Prologue — The Way of the Night Parade"},{"cn":"第一章｜停下來的瞬間","en":"Chapter 1 — The Moment He Stopped"},{"cn":"第二章｜被留下的夜","en":"Chapter 2 — The Night Left Behind"},{"cn":"第三章｜觀察者的條件","en":"Chapter 3 — The Observer's Terms"},{"cn":"第四章｜留下的理由","en":"Chapter 4 — Reasons to Stay"},{"cn":"第五章｜不回應的代價","en":"Chapter 5 — The Price of Not Answering"},{"cn":"第六章｜王的視線","en":"Chapter 6 — The King's Gaze"},{"cn":"第七章｜忠誠的牙","en":"Chapter 7 — The Fang of Loyalty"},{"cn":"第八章｜怨的形狀","en":"Chapter 8 — The Shape of Resentment"},{"cn":"第九章｜秩序的壓力","en":"Chapter 9 — The Weight of Order"},{"cn":"第十章｜夜行的意識","en":"Chapter 10 — The Parade's Mind"},{"cn":"第十一章｜有人必須留下","en":"Chapter 11 — Someone Must Remain"},{"cn":"第十二章｜最後的承擔","en":"Chapter 12 — The Last Bearing"},{"cn":"第十三章｜金寂","en":"Chapter 13 — Golden Stillness"}],"world":[{"cn":"作品概要","en":"IP Overview","pairs":[{"cn":"《金無垢》是一部江戶時代妖怪題材的故事IP：當人類把心中不肯承認的惡「指名」給妖怪承擔，百鬼夜行便夜夜搬運這座城的恐懼。","en":"Kinmuku is an Edo-period yokai IP: when humans \"name\" the evil they refuse to admit onto yokai, the Night Parade carries the city's fear away, night after night.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第一部《百鬼夜行》講述走在夜行最前端的鬼——赤座玄鬼——第一次停下腳步之後，整個秩序開始瓦解與昇華的過程。","en":"Part One, \"The Night Parade,\" follows what happens after the oni at its head — Akaza Genki — stops for the first time, and the whole order begins to crack, and to transcend.","proposal":false},{"cn":"核心一句話：惡不在鬼身上，惡在人心裡；當沒有人再需要被怪罪，妖怪便能放下重量，走入無垢界。","en":"In one line: evil is not in the oni but in the human heart; when no one needs to be blamed anymore, the yokai can lay down their weight and cross into the Immaculate Realm.","proposal":false},{"cn":"標題含義：「金無垢」即純金無瑕——抵達無垢界時的狀態稱為「金寂」，如純金般穩定的沉靜。","en":"The title means \"pure, untainted gold\" — the state of arrival in the Immaculate Realm is called Golden Stillness (Kinjaku), a quiet as stable as pure gold.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"時代與舞台","en":"Era & Setting","pairs":[{"cn":"時間定錨：江戶中後期，約1780–1830年。","en":"Time anchor: mid-to-late Edo period, c. 1780–1830.","proposal":false},{"cn":"選擇理由（源自設定文件）：城市化成熟、人口爆炸使恐懼自然累積；百物語與妖怪繪卷盛行；印刷術發達，偏見得以被「量產」。","en":"Rationale (from the source design doc): mature urbanization and population explosion let fear accumulate naturally; hyakumonogatari gatherings and yokai scrolls flourish; printing lets prejudice be \"mass-produced.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"社會表面穩定，底層壓抑極深——最適合「偏見製造鬼」的土壤。","en":"Society is stable on the surface and deeply repressed underneath — the perfect soil for prejudice to manufacture oni.","proposal":false},{"cn":"主要場景：深川河邊、日本橋商家街、石橋（玄鬼的定點）、屋脊與瓦頂（白蓮的領域）、新之助的版畫鋪。","en":"Key locations: the Fukagawa riverside, the Nihonbashi merchant streets, the stone bridge (Genki's fixed point), the roof ridges (Byakuren's domain), Shinnosuke's print shop.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"世界規則","en":"World Rules","pairs":[{"cn":"百鬼夜行不是妖怪的遊行，而是「人心積下來的東西」——太多、太滿、太久不肯承認，最後在夜裡自己走出來。","en":"The Night Parade is not a procession of yokai but \"what the human heart has stored up\" — too much, too full, unacknowledged too long, until it walks out on its own at night.","proposal":false},{"cn":"夜行並非每晚出現；出現條件：恐懼累積到閾值、流言傳播失控、或集體偏見被強化。","en":"The Parade does not appear every night; its conditions: fear accumulating past a threshold, rumor spreading out of control, or collective prejudice being reinforced.","proposal":false},{"cn":"夜行的本質是「社會壓力釋放機制」：它來「回收」被壓下的恐懼與惡意，不是來害人。","en":"The Parade is in essence a social pressure-release mechanism: it comes to reclaim suppressed fear and malice, not to do harm.","proposal":false},{"cn":"可見性規則：只有心中真正恐懼的人才能看見夜行；恐懼是門檻。","en":"Visibility rule: only those who truly fear can see the Parade; fear is the threshold.","proposal":false},{"cn":"指名規則：人只要把某個存在叫做「惡」，那存在就會被迫擁有惡的形狀——夜行裡最先被指名的，永遠是鬼。","en":"The Naming rule: call any being \"evil,\" and it is forced to take on evil's shape — and in the Parade, the first to be named is always the oni.","proposal":false},{"cn":"重量規則：恐懼越多，夜行越重；夜行越重，承擔者的肩越沉。","en":"The weight rule: the more fear, the heavier the Parade; the heavier the Parade, the heavier its bearer's shoulders.","proposal":false},{"cn":"滯留規則：恐懼若不被回收，會像油一樣黏在城上，自行凝聚成形，長出「偏見的牙」，尋找可怪罪的容器。","en":"The lingering rule: unreclaimed fear clings to the city like oil, congeals into form on its own, grows \"prejudice's teeth,\" and hunts for a vessel to blame.","proposal":false},{"cn":"減量規則：每一次有人承認恐懼來自自己，夜行就輕一分；當承認多於指名，夜行終將不再被需要。","en":"The diminishing rule: each time someone admits the fear is their own, the Parade grows lighter; when acknowledgment outweighs Naming, the Parade is no longer needed.","proposal":false},{"cn":"終局規則：妖怪褪去被指名的重量後，會進入「金寂」，離開此世，前往無垢界；總量減少不可逆。","en":"The endgame rule: a yokai that sheds its named weight enters Golden Stillness and departs this world for the Immaculate Realm; the diminishing is irreversible.","proposal":false},{"cn":"夜行本身具有集合意識（第十章）：它是「結果」，是人類選擇的形狀——它不是神，也不是敵人，而是妥協的總和。","en":"The Parade itself has a collective mind (Ch. 10): it is \"the result,\" the shape of human choices — not a god, not an enemy, but the sum of a compromise.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"核心主題","en":"Core Themes","pairs":[{"cn":"恐懼不是天生的，是被教出來的——孩子的眼睛能看見大人看不見的疲憊。","en":"Fear is not innate; it is taught — a child's eyes can see the weariness adults cannot.","proposal":false},{"cn":"偏見不是一個詞，是一種習慣：人們用它來避免思考。","en":"Prejudice is not a word but a habit — the one people use to avoid thinking.","proposal":false},{"cn":"承擔與阻止的分界：吞下惡讓鬼更重；讓惡失去形狀讓人更慌——後者才是修行。","en":"The line between bearing and preventing: swallowing evil makes the oni heavier; unforming evil makes people uneasy — the latter is the Practice.","proposal":false},{"cn":"停止回應不是解脫，是開始；人找不到出口時，才會開始懷疑問題出在自己身上。","en":"To stop answering is not release but a beginning; only when people lose their outlet do they begin to suspect the problem is their own.","proposal":false},{"cn":"「世界需要鬼」的真相：世界需要一個能承擔「惡」的容器——而本作要問的是：如果容器拒絕了呢？","en":"The truth of \"the world needs an oni\": the world needs a vessel to bear \"evil\" — and this work asks: what if the vessel refuses?","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"修行八條","en":"The Eight Precepts","pairs":[{"cn":"第一條：不為證明而動。（第三章）","en":"The First Precept: Do not act to prove yourself. (Ch. 3)","proposal":false},{"cn":"第二條：承受質疑，而不反擊。（第三章）","en":"The Second Precept: Bear doubt without striking back. (Ch. 3)","proposal":false},{"cn":"第三條：不為他人背負。（第四章）","en":"The Third Precept: Do not carry what belongs to others. (Ch. 4)","proposal":false},{"cn":"第四條：即使失敗，也不後悔。（第五章）","en":"The Fourth Precept: Even in failure, no regret. (Ch. 5)","proposal":false},{"cn":"第五條：面對忠誠，不摧毀。（第七章）","en":"The Fifth Precept: Faced with loyalty, do not destroy it. (Ch. 7)","proposal":false},{"cn":"第六條：承認情緒，而不被情緒定義。（第八章）","en":"The Sixth Precept: Acknowledge emotion; do not be defined by it. (Ch. 8)","proposal":false},{"cn":"第七條：不否認過去。（第十章）","en":"The Seventh Precept: Do not deny the past. (Ch. 10)","proposal":false},{"cn":"第八條：不怨。（第十二章）","en":"The Eighth Precept: Do not resent. (Ch. 12)","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"核心名詞","en":"Key Terms","pairs":[{"cn":"百鬼夜行——恐懼的搬運機制；社會壓力的釋放閥。","en":"The Night Parade (Hyakki Yagyō) — the mechanism that carries fear; society's pressure-release valve.","proposal":false},{"cn":"指名——把某個存在叫做「惡」的行為；一種古老而陰暗的力量。","en":"The Naming — the act of calling a being \"evil\"; an old and dark power.","proposal":false},{"cn":"回收——夜行吞下滯留恐懼的流程。","en":"Reclamation — the Parade's procedure of swallowing lingering fear.","proposal":false},{"cn":"修行——讓自己在不被需要的時候，仍然存在（白蓮的定義，第三章）。","en":"The Practice — to remain in existence even when unneeded (Byakuren's definition, Ch. 3).","proposal":false},{"cn":"無垢界——不需要任何存在被定義為惡的地方；彼岸，但彼岸不在遠方。","en":"The Immaculate Realm (Mukukai) — a place where no being need be defined as evil; the far shore, though the far shore is not far away.","proposal":false},{"cn":"金寂——抵達無垢界時的狀態：不是刺眼的光，而是純金般穩定的沉靜。","en":"Golden Stillness (Kinjaku) — the state of arrival: not blinding light, but a quiet as stable as pure gold.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"陣營與關係","en":"Factions & Relationships","pairs":[{"cn":"留下者（裂縫方）：玄鬼（錯誤的起點）、碧吉（第一個跟隨者）、黑縁（第二個，因共鳴）、綾女（第三個，因被承認）、白蓮（觀察者與規則命名者）。","en":"Those who stayed (the crack): Genki (origin of the error), Aokichi (first follower), Kuroberi (second, out of resonance), Ayame (third, because she was acknowledged), Byakuren (observer and namer of rules).","proposal":false},{"cn":"秩序方（夜行的王）：炎馬（最古老的重量、疲憊的王）、義牙（忠誠的牙）、烏嶽（審判與監視）、白嶺（秩序的承重者、最後的裁決）。","en":"The order (kings of the Parade): Enma (its oldest weight, the weary king), Giga (the fang of loyalty), Ugaku (judgment and watch), Hakurei (order's load-bearer, the final arbiter).","proposal":false},{"cn":"人類側：日本橋的孩子（第一道不含恐懼的目光）、新之助（製造鬼臉的版刻師）、賣夜蕎麥的老人（第一個「看見」的人）。","en":"The human side: the child of Nihonbashi (the first gaze without fear), Shinnosuke (the carver who manufactures oni faces), the night-soba seller (the first to \"see\").","proposal":false},{"cn":"保留角色（第一部未登場）：霜月澄、白妙、紅緒、玉藻静香（第一章被提及）、峰、黒潮。","en":"Reserved characters (absent from Part One): Shimotsuki Sumi, Shirotae, Benio, Tamamo Shizuka (referenced in Ch. 1), Mine, Kuroshio.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"人類配角","en":"Human Side Characters","pairs":[{"cn":"日本橋的孩子：全作的引信。他不含恐懼的疑問——「你一定要這樣嗎？」——刺穿了玄鬼的麻木。","en":"The child of Nihonbashi: the fuse of the whole work. His fearless question — \"Do you have to be this way?\" — pierces Genki's numbness.","proposal":false},{"cn":"新之助：年輕版刻師，靠刻「越醜越好」的鬼臉維生；某夜明白恐懼不是因為看見鬼，而是因為他正在製造鬼。","en":"Shinnosuke: a young woodblock carver who lives by carving oni faces \"the uglier the better\"; one night he understands the fear is not from seeing an oni, but from making one.","proposal":false},{"cn":"賣夜蕎麥的老人：序章的視點；一半祈求、一半指名的普通人。","en":"The night-soba seller: the prologue's viewpoint; an ordinary man, half praying, half naming.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"章節摘要","en":"Chapter Summaries","pairs":[{"cn":"序章｜夜行之常——夜行照常搬運恐懼；孩子的目光讓玄鬼慢了半拍；白蓮認出「錯誤」，說出無垢界與金寂之名。","en":"Prologue — The Way of the Night Parade: the Parade carries fear as always; a child's gaze slows Genki half a beat; Byakuren recognizes \"the error\" and names the Immaculate Realm and Golden Stillness.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第一章｜停下來的瞬間——抬手是本能，收回是選擇；隊伍不等他；碧吉上岸，說出「你很像被丟下了」。","en":"Chapter 1 — The Moment He Stopped: lifting the hand is instinct, drawing it back is choice; the column does not wait; Aokichi comes ashore — \"you look… left behind.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"第二章｜被留下的夜——滯留的恐懼自行凝形；玄鬼不吞而拆；黑縁現身，帶著被拋棄者的共鳴留下。","en":"Chapter 2 — The Night Left Behind: lingering fear takes form on its own; Genki unforms it rather than swallow it; Kuroberi appears and stays, out of an abandoned one's resonance.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第三章｜觀察者的條件——白蓮定義修行：「在不被需要的時候，仍然存在」；烏嶽降臨審判：「那就證明」。","en":"Chapter 3 — The Observer's Terms: Byakuren defines the Practice — \"to remain when unneeded\"; Ugaku descends in judgment: \"Then prove it.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"第四章｜留下的理由——碧吉的過去（救人反被指名）；玄鬼白日擋在橋前，讓人看見自己的怕；第三條修行。","en":"Chapter 4 — Reasons to Stay: Aokichi's past (he saved a child and was named for it); Genki stands before the bridge by day and lets people see their own fear; the Third Precept.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第五章｜不回應的代價——火災之夜，碧吉為救孩子犯規被打；指名撲向他；玄鬼將黑影從他身上撕開——比吞下更痛。","en":"Chapter 5 — The Price of Not Answering: on the night of the fire Aokichi breaks the rule to save a child and is beaten; the Naming swarms him; Genki tears the shadows off him — more painful than swallowing.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第六章｜王的視線——炎馬親自吞下恐懼證明「夜行不需要你」；玄鬼看見王吞噬時的空洞：規律內部本身已有倦意。","en":"Chapter 6 — The King's Gaze: Enma swallows the fear himself to prove \"the Parade does not need you\"; Genki sees the hollowness in the act — the order is weary from within.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第七章｜忠誠的牙——義牙以拳試探；憤怒底下是恐懼：若鬼可以拒絕，忠誠可能是一場漫長的誤解；「你可以選擇」讓他停手。","en":"Chapter 7 — The Fang of Loyalty: Giga tests with his fists; under the fury is fear — if the oni may refuse, loyalty may have been a long misunderstanding; \"You can choose\" stops him.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第八章｜怨的形狀——般若綾女：被愛人背叛、以憤怒證明存在；玄鬼給出「承認而不定義」；面具碎裂，她留下。","en":"Chapter 8 — The Shape of Resentment: Ayame the hannya — betrayed by her lover, proving her existence through rage; Genki offers acknowledgment without definition; the mask shatters, and she stays.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第九章｜秩序的壓力——白嶺攤牌：秩序是承重；若修行成功，夜行消失，大半妖怪失去存在理由；玄鬼：「那我會最後一個。」","en":"Chapter 9 — The Weight of Order: Hakurei lays it bare — order is load-bearing; if the Practice succeeds most yokai lose their reason to exist; Genki: \"Then I will be the last.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"第十章｜夜行的意識——夜行以集合意識直接對話；玄鬼不否認過去：「你是結果，但不是唯一的結果。」","en":"Chapter 10 — The Parade's Mind: the Parade speaks as a collective mind; Genki does not deny the past — \"You are the result. But not the only result.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"第十一章｜有人必須留下——夜行全力壓境對照「沒有容器人會崩」；白蓮之聲提醒全城「承認，不是爆發」；綾女第一個抵達金寂。","en":"Chapter 11 — Someone Must Remain: the Parade presses with full weight to prove people collapse without a vessel; Byakuren's voice reminds the city \"acknowledgment, not eruption\"; Ayame is the first to reach Golden Stillness.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第十二章｜最後的承擔——王們立約：「不阻止，也不幫」；最後的指名集中於玄鬼；他站進火裡，不吞不推，只是承認。","en":"Chapter 12 — The Last Bearing: the kings set terms — \"we will not stop you, and we will not help\"; the last Naming converges on Genki; he stands into the fire, neither swallowing nor pushing back — only acknowledging.","proposal":false},{"cn":"第十三章｜金寂——角淡了，紅褪了；歲月流過，眾妖一一化光離去；玄鬼守橋至最後，終於走入純金無瑕的光。","en":"Chapter 13 — Golden Stillness: the horns fade, the red recedes; years pass, and one by one the yokai become light and leave; Genki keeps the bridge to the very end, then walks into the flawless light of pure gold.","proposal":false}]}],"episodes":[{"cn":"總覽","en":"Season Overview","pairs":[{"cn":"第一部共14個章節（序章＋13章），建議切為8集：每集一個明確的情緒重心與一位「本集妖怪」，章節對應如下。","en":"Part One's 14 chapters (prologue + 13) map to 8 episodes: each with one clear emotional center and one \"yokai of the week,\" per the mapping below.","proposal":true},{"cn":"節奏設計：前3集建立世界與同伴（裂縫形成），中3集是三場「王的試煉」與一場情緒風暴，後2集收束為體制對決與昇華終章。","en":"Pacing: episodes 1–3 build the world and companions (the crack forms); 4–6 are the kings' trials and one emotional storm; 7–8 resolve into the confrontation with the system and the transcendent finale.","proposal":true},{"cn":"每集片尾固定卡：本集對應的修行條目（金底黑字），作為系列的儀式感記號。","en":"Fixed end-card per episode: the Precept earned that episode (black on gold), as the series' ritual signature.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"第1集","en":"Episode 1","pairs":[{"cn":"第1集《停下的半拍》——涵蓋：序章＋第一章。","en":"Episode 1, \"The Half Beat\" — covers: Prologue + Chapter 1.","proposal":false},{"cn":"一句話：走在百鬼夜行最前端的鬼，因為一個孩子不含恐懼的目光，第一次收回了手。","en":"Logline: the oni at the head of the Night Parade draws back his hand for the first time, because of a child's gaze that holds no fear.","proposal":false},{"cn":"關鍵場面：夜行開場（聲音先行）；紙門縫的對視；半拍的遲疑；隊伍不等他；碧吉上岸——「你很像……被丟下了。」","en":"Key scenes: the Parade's opening (sound before image); the gaze through the paper-door gap; the half-beat hesitation; the column moving on without him; Aokichi coming ashore — \"you look… left behind.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"登場角色：玄鬼、白蓮、碧吉、孩子一家、賣夜蕎麥的老人。","en":"Featured: Genki, Byakuren, Aokichi, the child's family, the night-soba seller.","proposal":false},{"cn":"集尾鉤子：滯留的恐懼在街角凝成無臉的影——「要找一個可以怪罪的東西。」","en":"Out: the lingering fear congeals into a faceless shadow at the corner — \"seeking something to blame.\"","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"第2集","en":"Episode 2","pairs":[{"cn":"第2集《被留下的》——涵蓋：第二章＋第三章。","en":"Episode 2, \"The Left-Behind\" — covers: Chapters 2 + 3.","proposal":false},{"cn":"一句話：不吞、只拆——玄鬼拒絕成為出口；留下來的第二個是記憶太好的貓。","en":"Logline: not swallowing, only unforming — Genki refuses to be the outlet; the second to stay is a cat who remembers too well.","proposal":false},{"cn":"關鍵場面：新之助刻鬼臉的手第一次停下；玄鬼拆散無形之惡；黑縁的刺與共鳴；白蓮定義修行；烏嶽降臨——「那就證明。」","en":"Key scenes: Shinnosuke's carving hand stops for the first time; Genki unforms the formless; Kuroberi's barbs and resonance; Byakuren defines the Practice; Ugaku descends — \"Then prove it.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"登場角色：玄鬼、碧吉、黑縁、白蓮、新之助、烏嶽（白嶺剪影）。","en":"Featured: Genki, Aokichi, Kuroberi, Byakuren, Shinnosuke, Ugaku (Hakurei in silhouette).","proposal":false},{"cn":"本集修行：第一條、第二條。","en":"Precepts earned: the First and the Second.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"第3集","en":"Episode 3","pairs":[{"cn":"第3集《留下的理由》——涵蓋：第四章＋第五章。","en":"Episode 3, \"Reasons to Stay\" — covers: Chapters 4 + 5.","proposal":false},{"cn":"一句話：救過人反而被指名的河童，再一次選擇救人；玄鬼把指名從他身上撕開。","en":"Logline: the kappa once named for the very act of saving a life chooses to save again; Genki tears the Naming off him.","proposal":false},{"cn":"關鍵場面：碧吉的皿在白日乾涸；橋前對峙（存在即阻擋）；火災之夜；棍棒落下；撕開黑影——比吞下更痛。","en":"Key scenes: Aokichi's dish drying in daylight; the standoff at the bridge (presence as defense); the night of the fire; the club falling; tearing the shadows away — more painful than swallowing.","proposal":false},{"cn":"登場角色：玄鬼、碧吉、黑縁、白蓮、人群（暴徒化）。","en":"Featured: Genki, Aokichi, Kuroberi, Byakuren, the crowd (turning mob).","proposal":false},{"cn":"本集修行：第三條、第四條。","en":"Precepts earned: the Third and the Fourth.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"第4集","en":"Episode 4","pairs":[{"cn":"第4集《王的視線》——涵蓋：第六章＋第七章。","en":"Episode 4, \"The King's Gaze\" — covers: Chapters 6 + 7.","proposal":false},{"cn":"一句話：最古老的王親自吞下恐懼證明「夜行不需要你」，而他的眼裡沒有喜悅；忠誠的牙隨後咬來。","en":"Logline: the oldest king swallows the fear himself to prove \"the Parade does not need you\" — and there is no joy in his eyes; then loyalty's fang strikes.","proposal":false},{"cn":"關鍵場面：炎馬讓空氣讓開；暗紅球體入喉、眼神空洞；義牙的拳與石橋裂縫；「你可以選擇」；「我會看著你。」","en":"Key scenes: the air stepping aside for Enma; the dark-red sphere swallowed, the empty gaze; Giga's fists and the cracking bridge; \"You can choose\"; \"I will be watching you.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"登場角色：玄鬼、炎馬、義牙、碧吉、黑縁、白蓮。","en":"Featured: Genki, Enma, Giga, Aokichi, Kuroberi, Byakuren.","proposal":false},{"cn":"本集修行：第五條。","en":"Precept earned: the Fifth.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"第5集","en":"Episode 5","pairs":[{"cn":"第5集《怨的形狀》——涵蓋：第八章（單章成集）。","en":"Episode 5, \"The Shape of Resentment\" — covers: Chapter 8 (standalone).","proposal":false},{"cn":"一句話：被愛人當眾稱作怪物的般若，以憤怒證明自己存在——直到有人不因她的怨而後退。","en":"Logline: called a monster in public by the man who loved her, the hannya proves she exists through rage — until someone does not step back from it.","proposal":false},{"cn":"關鍵場面：巷中的燈；半張面具下通紅的眼；情緒具象化（牆滲水、地裂紋、紫焰淚）；「你的怨，不是錯」；面具全碎。","en":"Key scenes: the lamp in the alley; red-rimmed eyes beneath half a mask; emotion made physical (weeping walls, cracking ground, violet-flame tears); \"Your resentment is not wrong\"; the mask shattering entirely.","proposal":false},{"cn":"登場角色：綾女、玄鬼、黑縁（讀懂她的人）、碧吉、白蓮。","en":"Featured: Ayame, Genki, Kuroberi (the one who reads her truly), Aokichi, Byakuren.","proposal":false},{"cn":"本集修行：第六條。","en":"Precept earned: the Sixth.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"第6集","en":"Episode 6","pairs":[{"cn":"第6集《秩序與意識》——涵蓋：第九章＋第十章。","en":"Episode 6, \"Order and the Mind\" — covers: Chapters 9 + 10.","proposal":false},{"cn":"一句話：大天狗攤開真正的賭注——若你成功，我們大半將失去存在理由；而夜行本身，第一次開口對話。","en":"Logline: the daitengu lays out the true stakes — if you succeed, most of us lose our reason to exist; and the Parade itself speaks for the first time.","proposal":false},{"cn":"關鍵場面：白嶺降臨、空氣變得乾淨；「秩序是承重」；水面浮現過去與可能的未來；陰影包裹玄鬼；「你是結果，但不是唯一的結果。」","en":"Key scenes: Hakurei's descent, the air going unnaturally clean; \"order is load-bearing\"; pasts and possible futures surfacing on the water; the shadow enveloping Genki; \"You are the result. But not the only result.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"登場角色：白嶺、玄鬼、白蓮、碧吉、黑縁、綾女、夜行意識（聲音演出）。","en":"Featured: Hakurei, Genki, Byakuren, Aokichi, Kuroberi, Ayame, the Parade's mind (voice performance).","proposal":false},{"cn":"本集修行：第七條。","en":"Precept earned: the Seventh.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"第7集","en":"Episode 7","pairs":[{"cn":"第7集《第一道光》——涵蓋：第十一章。","en":"Episode 7, \"The First Light\" — covers: Chapter 11.","proposal":false},{"cn":"一句話：夜行全力壓境要證明「沒有容器，人會崩」；而第一個抵達金寂的，是不再需要證明的般若。","en":"Logline: the Parade presses with all its weight to prove people collapse without a vessel; and the first to reach Golden Stillness is the hannya who no longer needs to prove anything.","proposal":false},{"cn":"關鍵場面：全城同時想起自己推給鬼的事；白蓮之聲穿過千戶——「承認，不是爆發」；綾女褪去重量、金光升起、「謝謝」。","en":"Key scenes: the whole city remembering at once what it pushed onto the oni; Byakuren's voice threading a thousand homes — \"acknowledgment, not eruption\"; Ayame shedding her weight, gold light rising, \"Thank you.\"","proposal":false},{"cn":"登場角色：全體留下者、炎馬、白嶺、義牙、烏嶽、城民群像。","en":"Featured: all who stayed, Enma, Hakurei, Giga, Ugaku, the city as ensemble.","proposal":false},{"cn":"集尾鉤子：夜行「重新計算」；炎馬仰望天空——「原來如此。」","en":"Out: the Parade \"recalculating\"; Enma looking up at the sky — \"So that's how it is.\"","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"第8集","en":"Episode 8","pairs":[{"cn":"第8集《金寂》——涵蓋：第十二章＋第十三章（終章，可考慮加長版）。","en":"Episode 8, \"Golden Stillness\" — covers: Chapters 12 + 13 (finale; extended cut worth considering).","proposal":false},{"cn":"一句話：王們立約退場，最後的指名如潮水湧向獨自站立的鬼；然後——歲月、告別、與純金無瑕的光。","en":"Logline: the kings set their terms and step back; the last Naming floods toward the oni standing alone; then — the years, the farewells, and the flawless light of pure gold.","proposal":false},{"cn":"關鍵場面：「你不是王，卻選擇了王的結局」；火把之夜、不吞不推的承擔；「夜行，停」；角淡紅褪；眾妖依序化光；橋上最後的鬼；空橋與風。","en":"Key scenes: \"You are not a king, yet you chose a king's ending\"; the night of torches, bearing without swallowing or pushing back; \"Night Parade — halt\"; horns fading, red receding; the yokai becoming light one by one; the last oni on the bridge; the empty bridge, and wind.","proposal":false},{"cn":"登場角色：全員（含依序退場：炎馬、義牙、烏嶽、白嶺、黑縁、白蓮，最後玄鬼）。","en":"Featured: the full cast (departures in order: Enma, Giga, Ugaku, Hakurei, Kuroberi, Byakuren, and last, Genki).","proposal":false},{"cn":"本集修行：第八條——不怨。","en":"Precept earned: the Eighth — Do not resent.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"未來掛鉤","en":"Future Hooks","pairs":[{"cn":"前傳特別篇：白蓮×玉藻静香——「把罪推給一個名字」的失敗如何生出無垢界的願望（第一章已埋線）。","en":"Prequel special: Byakuren × Tamamo Shizuka — how the failure of \"pushing sin onto one name\" gave birth to the wish for the Immaculate Realm (seeded in Ch. 1).","proposal":true},{"cn":"第二部候選單元：霜月澄（凍結的情緒）、白妙（從未被看見的暴力）、紅緒（虛榮側的第一條修行）、峰（城外的恐懼形態）、黒潮（夜行從未行經的海）。","en":"Part Two candidate units: Shimotsuki Sumi (emotion frozen), Shirotae (the violence of never being seen), Benio (the First Precept from vanity's side), Mine (fear's shape beyond the city), Kuroshio (the sea the Parade never walked).","proposal":true},{"cn":"開放疑問（IP級懸念）：玉藻静香「退場」去了哪裡？無垢界裡是否仍有「先行者」在等待？","en":"Open questions (IP-level mysteries): where did Tamamo Shizuka \"exit\" to? Do earlier arrivals wait within the Immaculate Realm?","proposal":true}]}],"pipeline":[{"cn":"流程總覽","en":"Pipeline Overview","pairs":[{"cn":"每位角色走同一條六階段生產線：①角色基礎 → ②背景與故事線 → ③視覺設計 → ④資產製作 → ⑤聲音 → ⑥分集整合。","en":"Every character moves down the same six-stage line: 1) Character Base → 2) Background & Arc → 3) Visual Design → 4) Asset Production → 5) Voice → 6) Episode Integration.","proposal":true},{"cn":"規則：任何階段引用設定時，一律以《角色檔案》與《翻譯聖經》為準；凡標示的內容須經創作決策後才轉為正式設定。","en":"Rule: at every stage, the Character Profile and Translation Bible are the source of truth; anything marked [PROPOSAL] becomes canon only after a creative sign-off.","proposal":true},{"cn":"雙語規則：所有對白先鎖定繁中版，再依聖經產出英文版；字幕與配音稿共用同一份雙語對照表。","en":"Bilingual rule: lock the Traditional Chinese line first, then derive the English per the bible; subtitles and dub scripts share the same side-by-side table.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"階段一：角色基礎","en":"Stage 1: Character Base","pairs":[{"cn":"產出：基本資料表（名、種、類型、定位）、名字由來、氣質關鍵詞三個、一句話定位。","en":"Deliverables: basic info sheet (name, species, archetype, role), etymology, three temperament keywords, one-line positioning.","proposal":false},{"cn":"驗收標準：與角色檔案第1–3節完全一致；一句話定位能讓新進成員在30秒內理解角色。","en":"Acceptance: matches Profile sections 1–3 exactly; the one-liner lets a new team member grasp the character in 30 seconds.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"階段二：背景與故事線","en":"Stage 2: Background & Arc","pairs":[{"cn":"產出：背景故事摘要、第一部逐章出場表、關係網、關鍵台詞表（雙語）。","en":"Deliverables: background summary, chapter-by-chapter Part One appearance table, relationship web, key-line table (bilingual).","proposal":false},{"cn":"驗收標準：每一條背景都能對應到章節出處或PDF設定；內容明確標示。","en":"Acceptance: every background item traces to a chapter or the PDF; [PROPOSAL] content clearly flagged.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"階段三：視覺設計","en":"Stage 3: Visual Design","pairs":[{"cn":"產出：概念設定圖 → 三視圖 → 表情表 → 服裝道具表 → 色彩指定。","en":"Deliverables: concept art → turnaround → expression sheet → costume & props → color script.","proposal":false},{"cn":"驗收標準：故事中的既定外貌細節（如玄鬼的角如影、碧吉的皿、綾女的半面具）必須全部呈現；色彩不得偏離角色檔案的色板超出一次修訂。","en":"Acceptance: all canon appearance details (Genki's shadow-like horns, Aokichi's dish, Ayame's half mask) must appear; palettes stay within one revision of the profile's [PROPOSAL] palette.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"階段四：資產製作","en":"Stage 4: Asset Production","pairs":[{"cn":"產出：模型／作畫素材、動態參考、特效素材（恐懼黑影、金寂之光為全劇共用資產）。","en":"Deliverables: model/animation assets, motion reference, VFX elements (the fear-shadows and Golden Stillness light are series-wide shared assets).","proposal":false},{"cn":"共用特效優先級：恐懼黑影（每集）＞金寂金光（第7、8集高規格）＞情緒具象化（第5集綾女專屬）。","en":"Shared VFX priority: fear-shadows (every episode) > Golden Stillness light (hero-quality for EP7–8) > emotion-made-physical (EP5, Ayame-specific).","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"階段五：聲音","en":"Stage 5: Voice","pairs":[{"cn":"產出：聲優試音方向、台詞樣本（雙語各三句）、呼吸與停頓規範（本作大量留白，停頓即表演）。","en":"Deliverables: VO casting direction, sample lines (three per language), breath-and-pause spec (this work lives on silence — the pause is the performance).","proposal":false},{"cn":"選角基調：玄鬼＝低而慢；白蓮＝輕而準；炎馬＝宏亮而疲憊；綾女＝瓷面裂紋；碧吉＝快而自嘲；黑縁＝乾冷嘲弄。","en":"Casting keynote: Genki = low and slow; Byakuren = light and precise; Enma = booming yet weary; Ayame = porcelain with cracks; Aokichi = quick and self-mocking; Kuroberi = dry, purring irony.","proposal":true}]},{"cn":"階段六：分集整合","en":"Stage 6: Episode Integration","pairs":[{"cn":"產出：各集分鏡引用表、角色每集情緒曲線、片尾修行卡（金底黑字）素材。","en":"Deliverables: per-episode storyboard reference table, per-episode emotion curve per character, end-card Precept assets (black on gold).","proposal":false},{"cn":"驗收標準：每集「本集妖怪」的關鍵場面與分集規劃一致；跨集連續性（傷、皿的水量、面具裂痕進度）有專人核對。","en":"Acceptance: each episode's \"yokai of the week\" scenes match the Episode Breakdown; cross-episode continuity (wounds, the dish's water level, mask-crack progression) has a named owner.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"角色資料夾標準結構","en":"Standard Character Folder Structure","pairs":[{"cn":"每個角色資料夾固定五個子目錄：01_角色基礎、02_背景故事、03_視覺設計、04_台詞語音、05_分集出場。","en":"Every character folder carries five fixed subfolders: 01_Character_Base, 02_Background, 03_Visual_Design, 04_Lines_Voice, 05_Episode_Appearances.","proposal":false},{"cn":"《角色檔案》雙語文件放在資料夾根層，是該角色唯一的正典入口。","en":"The bilingual Character Profile sits at the folder root as the character's single canonical entry point.","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"角色狀態總表","en":"Character Status Board","pairs":[{"cn":"01 赤座玄鬼（鬼｜重力型）——第一部主角；優先級T0；資料完備，可直接進入視覺設計。","en":"01 Akaza Genki (oni | Gravity) — Part One lead; priority T0; canon complete, ready for visual design.","proposal":false},{"cn":"02 九條白蓮（九尾狐｜理性型）——第一部女主；優先級T0；資料完備。","en":"02 Kujō Byakuren (nine-tailed fox | Reason) — Part One female lead; T0; canon complete.","proposal":false},{"cn":"03 大江炎馬（酒吞童子｜野性型）——第4集起主要；優先級T1。","en":"03 Ōe Enma (Shuten-dōji | Feral) — major from EP4; T1.","proposal":false},{"cn":"04 茨木義牙（茨木童子｜野性型）——第4集起；優先級T1。","en":"04 Ibaraki Giga (Ibaraki-dōji | Feral) — from EP4; T1.","proposal":false},{"cn":"05 鞍馬烏嶽（天狗｜理性型）——第2集起；優先級T1。","en":"05 Kurama Ugaku (tengu | Reason) — from EP2; T1.","proposal":false},{"cn":"06 鞍馬白嶺（大天狗｜重力型）——第2集剪影、第6集主場；優先級T1。","en":"06 Kurama Hakurei (daitengu | Gravity) — silhouette EP2, centerpiece EP6; T1.","proposal":false},{"cn":"07 霜月澄（雪女｜情緒型）——第一部未登場；優先級T2（第二部候選）。","en":"07 Shimotsuki Sumi (yuki-onna | Emotion) — absent from Part One; T2 (Part Two candidate).","proposal":false},{"cn":"08 綾女（般若｜情緒型）——第5集主場、第7集金寂第一人；優先級T1。","en":"08 Ayame (hannya | Emotion) — centerpiece EP5, first Golden Stillness EP7; T1.","proposal":false},{"cn":"09 白妙（骨女｜存在型）——第一部未登場；優先級T2。","en":"09 Shirotae (hone-onna | Presence) — absent from Part One; T2.","proposal":false},{"cn":"10 碧吉（河童｜游離型）——第1集起全程；優先級T0。","en":"10 Aokichi (kappa | Drifting) — throughout from EP1; T0.","proposal":false},{"cn":"11 黒縁（貓又｜記憶型）——第2集起全程；優先級T0。","en":"11 Kuroberi (nekomata | Memory) — throughout from EP2; T0.","proposal":false},{"cn":"12 紅緒（妖狐｜游離型）——第一部未登場；優先級T2。","en":"12 Benio (yōko | Drifting) — absent from Part One; T2.","proposal":false},{"cn":"13 玉藻静香（玉藻前｜理性型）——第一部僅被提及（第一章）；優先級T2（前傳關鍵）。","en":"13 Tamamo Shizuka (Tamamo-no-Mae | Reason) — referenced only (Ch. 1); T2 (prequel key).","proposal":false},{"cn":"14 峰（山姥｜母性型）——第一部未登場；優先級T3。","en":"14 Mine (yamanba | Maternal) — absent from Part One; T3.","proposal":false},{"cn":"15 黒潮（海坊主｜重力型）——第一部未登場；優先級T3。","en":"15 Kuroshio (umibōzu | Gravity) — absent from Part One; T3.","proposal":false},{"cn":"人類側資產：日本橋的孩子（T0——第1集情感核心）、新之助（T1）、蕎麥老人（T1）、群眾模組（T0，每集必用）。","en":"Human-side assets: the child of Nihonbashi (T0 — EP1's emotional core), Shinnosuke (T1), the soba seller (T1), crowd modules (T0, used every episode).","proposal":false}]},{"cn":"雙語工作流","en":"Bilingual Workflow","pairs":[{"cn":"所有正典文本以「中文左欄、英文右欄」逐行對照維護；行對行對齊是字幕與配音的基礎。","en":"All canon text is maintained line-by-line, Chinese left column, English right; line alignment is the foundation for subtitles and dubbing.","proposal":false},{"cn":"名詞與人名一律以《翻譯聖經》為準；聖經未收錄的新名詞須先入聖經、再入劇本。","en":"Names and terms follow the Translation Bible without exception; new terms enter the bible first, scripts second.","proposal":false},{"cn":"本地化順序：繁中原文 → 英文 →（未來）日文；日文版人名讀音已在聖經內建（如あかざ げんき）。","en":"Localization order: Traditional Chinese original → English → (future) Japanese; Japanese readings are already built into the bible (e.g., Akaza Genki あかざ げんき).","proposal":true}]}],"story":[{"id":"ch00","n":0,"title_cn":"序章｜夜行之常","title_en":"Prologue — The Way of the Night Parade","lines":[{"cn":"江戶的夜，本該只有兩種聲音：","en":"The Edo night was supposed to hold only two kinds of sound:"},{"cn":"一種是人活著的聲音——木屐踩過石板、夜鶯在庭樹上鳴、遠處浪頭拍打堤岸；","en":"the sound of people living — wooden clogs on flagstones, a nightingale in a garden tree, waves striking the embankment far away;"},{"cn":"另一種是人假裝自己活著的聲音——門閂落下的輕響、紙門拉合的摩擦、被子裡壓住的呼吸。","en":"and the sound of people pretending to live — the soft drop of a door bolt, the rasp of paper doors sliding shut, breath pressed down beneath the quilts."},{"cn":"但這一夜，江戶多了一種聲音。","en":"But on this night, Edo held one sound more."},{"cn":"那不是誰說話，也不是誰哭。","en":"It was no one speaking, and no one weeping."},{"cn":"那是一種很慢、很齊、像潮水一樣的步伐，從城外低處往上推過來——不急不躁，卻絕對不會停。腳步踩過青石，像是把整座城的陰影都推動了。","en":"It was a tread — slow, even, tidelike — pushing up from the low ground beyond the city, unhurried, and absolutely unwilling to stop. Footsteps crossed the bluestone as if pushing the shadow of the whole city along with them."},{"cn":"在深川的河邊，賣夜蕎麥的老人把鍋蓋按得更緊。","en":"By the river at Fukagawa, the old man who sold night soba pressed the lid of his pot down tighter."},{"cn":"他本不該看見什麼，按理說他一生見過的怪事已夠多，眼睛早學會把不該看的忽略掉。可他的手抖得像被風抓住，指節泛白，汗卻冷得像水。","en":"He should not have seen anything. By rights he had seen enough strangeness for one lifetime; his eyes had long since learned to pass over what should not be seen. Yet his hands shook as if seized by wind, knuckles white, and his sweat ran cold as water."},{"cn":"他看見了。","en":"He saw."},{"cn":"不是用眼睛看——而像是恐懼從胸口爬出來，替他睜開了另一雙眼。","en":"Not with his eyes — it was as if fear had crawled out of his chest and opened a second pair for him."},{"cn":"那雙眼看見街角的影子變得更黑，黑得像墨汁往外滲；看見屋瓦下有一線白霧凝成帶子，在空中慢慢飄；看見沒有風，卻有無數紙燈籠的火苗同時朝一個方向偏斜，像在敬畏什麼。","en":"Those eyes saw the shadows at the street corner turn blacker, black as ink seeping outward; saw a thread of white mist gather into a ribbon beneath the roof tiles, drifting slowly through the air; saw no wind at all, and yet the flames of countless paper lanterns leaning together in one direction, as if in awe of something."},{"cn":"江戶的人說，百鬼夜行從來不是妖怪的遊行。","en":"The people of Edo said the Night Parade of a Hundred Demons (Hyakki Yagyō) was never a procession of yokai."},{"cn":"它是「人心積下來的東西」，太多、太滿、太久不肯承認，最後只好在夜裡走出來。","en":"It was what the human heart had stored up — too much, too full, unacknowledged too long — until at last it had no choice but to walk out into the night."},{"cn":"也因此，並非人人都能看見。","en":"And so, not everyone could see it."},{"cn":"能看見的人，多半不願承認自己看見。","en":"Those who could see mostly refused to admit they had."},{"cn":"他們會說自己只是夜裡眼花，或是喝了酒，或是聽了太多怪談。","en":"They would say their eyes had played tricks in the dark, or that they had been drinking, or had heard too many ghost stories."},{"cn":"因為承認看見，就等於承認——","en":"Because to admit seeing was to admit —"},{"cn":"自己心裡有一塊地方正在怕。","en":"that some place inside them was afraid."},{"cn":"老人把蕎麥湯勺放下，退進陰影裡，嘴唇顫抖地念著從寺裡聽來的詞。","en":"The old man set down his soba ladle, backed into the shadows, and with trembling lips recited words he had heard at the temple."},{"cn":"他念得不完整，因為他一半的心在祈求，一半的心在指名。","en":"He recited them imperfectly, for half his heart was praying, and half his heart was naming."},{"cn":"指名是一種更古老、更陰暗的力量。","en":"Naming is an older, darker power."},{"cn":"人只要把某個存在叫做「惡」，那存在就會被迫擁有惡的形狀。","en":"A person need only call some being \"evil,\" and that being is forced to take on evil's shape."},{"cn":"而在百鬼夜行裡，最先被指名的那一個——永遠是鬼。","en":"And in the Night Parade, the first to be named — is always the oni."},{"cn":"赤座玄鬼走在夜行的前端。","en":"Akaza Genki walked at the head of the Parade."},{"cn":"他身形高大得像一扇門，肩寬，背直，步伐沉。","en":"He stood tall as a gate, broad-shouldered, straight-backed, heavy of stride."},{"cn":"不是武士的挺拔，而像石像的筆直——久站在某個位置，早已忘了「想動」是什麼感覺。","en":"Not the uprightness of a samurai — more the straightness of a stone statue: something that had stood in one place so long it had forgotten what wanting to move felt like."},{"cn":"他的角不張揚，像兩道在額上生出的陰影。皮膚帶著暗紅的底色，像是被火燒過又冷卻下來的鐵。","en":"His horns did not flaunt themselves; they were like two shadows grown from his brow. His skin carried a dark red undertone, like iron burned and then cooled."},{"cn":"他沒穿鎧甲，卻比鎧甲更讓人不敢靠近。衣襟是深色布，沾著看不清的塵，像走過很多人不願回想的地方。","en":"He wore no armor, yet he was harder to approach than armor. His robe was dark cloth, dusted with something indistinct, as if he had walked through many places people preferred not to remember."},{"cn":"玄鬼不記得自己從何時開始走在這裡。","en":"Genki did not remember when he had begun walking here."},{"cn":"他只記得每一次夜行開始之前，江戶會先安靜下來。","en":"He remembered only that before each Parade began, Edo would first fall silent."},{"cn":"安靜像一層灰落在城上，落在每個人的喉嚨裡，讓人說不出話。","en":"The silence settled over the city like a layer of ash, settled in every throat, so that no one could speak."},{"cn":"那不是善良的安靜，而是「不能說」的安靜——不能說怨，不能說恨，不能說窮，不能說怕。","en":"It was not a kindly silence but the silence of must-not-say — must not speak resentment, must not speak hatred, must not speak poverty, must not speak fear."},{"cn":"那些不能說的，便會在夜裡自己走出來。","en":"What could not be spoken would walk out on its own, at night."},{"cn":"夜行的隊伍在他身後延展，像一條看不見盡頭的河。","en":"The Parade's column stretched out behind him like a river without visible end."},{"cn":"有飄著紙燈籠的影子，有拖著破布的白帶，有像樹根一樣扭曲的手臂，有在屋瓦之間跳躍的單腳伞影。","en":"There were shadows trailing paper lanterns, white ribbons dragging torn cloth, arms twisted like tree roots, the shade of a one-legged umbrella leaping between roof tiles."},{"cn":"它們不是每一個都有清楚的形體，因為它們不全是妖怪。","en":"Not every one of them had a clear form, for not all of them were yokai."},{"cn":"其中有些只是人心的碎片，借著妖怪的樣子暫時站起來。","en":"Some were only fragments of the human heart, standing upright for a while in a yokai's borrowed shape."},{"cn":"玄鬼知道自己要做什麼。","en":"Genki knew what he was to do."},{"cn":"百鬼夜行不是來「害人」。","en":"The Night Parade did not come to do harm."},{"cn":"它是來回收。","en":"It came to reclaim."},{"cn":"回收人們擠在一起不肯承認的恐懼；回收那些被壓下去的惡意；回收「我明明什麼都沒做卻被你恨」的委屈；回收「我被你看不起所以我也要你不好過」的陰影。","en":"To reclaim the fear people huddled together refusing to admit; to reclaim the malice pressed down out of sight; to reclaim the grievance of I did nothing, and still you hate me; to reclaim the shadow of you looked down on me, so I will see you suffer too."},{"cn":"恐懼越多，夜行越重。","en":"The more fear, the heavier the Parade."},{"cn":"夜行越重，玄鬼的肩就越沉。","en":"The heavier the Parade, the heavier Genki's shoulders."},{"cn":"他走得越慢。","en":"The slower he walked."},{"cn":"而這座城的人，只會說：看吧，鬼又來了。","en":"And the people of this city would only say: look, the oni has come again."},{"cn":"他們不會說「我們的恐懼太多」。","en":"They would not say, \"our fear has grown too great.\""},{"cn":"他們只會說「鬼很可怕」。","en":"They would only say, \"the oni is terrifying.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼有時候想笑。","en":"Sometimes Genki wanted to laugh."},{"cn":"但他忘了怎麼笑。","en":"But he had forgotten how."},{"cn":"在日本橋附近，一戶商家熄了燈，紙門背後縮著一家人。","en":"Near Nihonbashi, a merchant house put out its lights, and a family huddled behind the paper door."},{"cn":"屋裡的母親把孩子摟得死緊，指尖陷入孩子肩膀。","en":"Inside, the mother clutched her child so hard her fingertips sank into his shoulders."},{"cn":"她在孩子耳邊說：「別出聲，鬼會聽見。」","en":"She whispered at his ear: \"Not a sound. The oni will hear.\""},{"cn":"孩子點頭，眼睛卻亮得不合時宜，像想把恐懼看清楚。","en":"The child nodded, but his eyes were bright at the wrong moment, as if he wanted to see fear clearly."},{"cn":"父親額頭都是汗，卻仍硬撐著說：「別怕，不過是妖怪。」","en":"The father's forehead ran with sweat, yet he forced himself to say: \"Don't be afraid. It's only a yokai.\""},{"cn":"他說得像在教訓孩子，其實是在教訓自己。","en":"He said it as if scolding the child; in truth he was scolding himself."},{"cn":"他們看見外面有黑影走過。","en":"They saw a dark shape pass outside."},{"cn":"只有那個孩子看見得更清楚一些——","en":"Only the child saw a little more clearly —"},{"cn":"他看見黑影的腳步不是要靠近他們的門，而是按著某種固定的路線走過街口，像巡夜的役人。","en":"He saw that the dark shape's steps were not turning toward their door, but following some fixed route past the street corner, like a watchman on his rounds."},{"cn":"他看見黑影走過時，屋外的風反而變小了，像那影子把風都壓住了。","en":"He saw that as the shape passed, the wind outside grew smaller, as if the shadow were holding even the wind down."},{"cn":"孩子的心忽然冒出一個荒謬的念頭：","en":"An absurd thought rose suddenly in the child's heart:"},{"cn":"如果那是鬼，為什麼走得那麼穩？","en":"If that is an oni, why does it walk so steadily?"},{"cn":"為什麼看起來……那麼累？","en":"Why does it look… so tired?"},{"cn":"孩子還太小，不懂什麼叫「偏見」。","en":"The child was too young to know the word \"prejudice.\""},{"cn":"偏見不是一個詞，是一種習慣——人們用它來避免思考。","en":"Prejudice is not a word but a habit — the one people use to avoid thinking."},{"cn":"他只知道，自己不想跟著大人一起害怕。","en":"He knew only that he did not want to be afraid along with the grown-ups."},{"cn":"他想知道答案。","en":"He wanted to know the answer."},{"cn":"於是他在母親的臂彎裡，微微抬起頭。","en":"So, in the crook of his mother's arm, he lifted his head a little."},{"cn":"紙門縫隙透進來一線月光，他把眼睛貼上去。","en":"A thread of moonlight came through the gap in the paper door, and he pressed his eye to it."},{"cn":"那一瞬間，他與玄鬼的視線撞在一起。","en":"In that instant, his gaze and Genki's collided."},{"cn":"沒有尖叫。","en":"No scream."},{"cn":"沒有咒罵。","en":"No curse."},{"cn":"沒有石頭。","en":"No stone."},{"cn":"孩子只是睜大眼睛。","en":"The child only opened his eyes wide."},{"cn":"而玄鬼，第一次在夜行的固定步伐裡，感到胸口某個地方被輕輕撞了一下。","en":"And Genki, for the first time within the Parade's fixed tread, felt something knock softly against a place in his chest."},{"cn":"那不是痛。","en":"It was not pain."},{"cn":"不是憐憫。","en":"Not pity."},{"cn":"更不是勇氣。","en":"Still less courage."},{"cn":"那是一個極單純、極乾淨的疑問：","en":"It was a question, utterly simple, utterly clean:"},{"cn":"——你一定要這樣嗎？","en":"— Do you have to be this way?"},{"cn":"疑問像一根針，刺穿了他長久以來的麻木。","en":"The question was a needle, and it pierced through his long numbness."},{"cn":"玄鬼抬手的動作慢了半拍。","en":"Genki's hand rose half a beat slow."},{"cn":"只是半拍而已。","en":"Half a beat, nothing more."},{"cn":"在刀光劍影裡，半拍不算什麼。","en":"Amid flashing blades, half a beat counts for nothing."},{"cn":"可在百鬼夜行裡，半拍足以讓整個隊伍的節奏變形。","en":"But in the Night Parade, half a beat is enough to warp the rhythm of the entire column."},{"cn":"他聽見身後那些非人之物的躁動。","en":"He heard the stirring of the inhuman things behind him."},{"cn":"不是吼叫，而像無數腳步同時變重，像潮水突然被石頭堵住。","en":"Not a roar — more like countless footsteps growing heavy at once, like a tide suddenly dammed by stone."},{"cn":"恐懼沒有被回收。","en":"The fear was not reclaimed."},{"cn":"恐懼仍滯留在街上，像一層看不見的油，黏在人的皮膚上，讓人喘不過氣。","en":"It lingered in the streets like an invisible film of oil, clinging to people's skin, stealing their breath."},{"cn":"玄鬼知道這意味著什麼。","en":"Genki knew what that meant."},{"cn":"當恐懼滯留，人會開始找出口。","en":"When fear lingers, people begin looking for an outlet."},{"cn":"而人最擅長的出口，就是找一個「可以怪罪」的存在。","en":"And the outlet people are best at finding is a being that can be blamed."},{"cn":"他們會把夜行說得更可怕。","en":"They would make the Parade out to be more terrifying."},{"cn":"會把妖怪畫得更醜。","en":"Would paint the yokai uglier."},{"cn":"會把鬼說得更殘忍。","en":"Would speak of the oni as crueler still."},{"cn":"只要那樣，他們就不用承認——恐懼來自自己。","en":"So long as they did, they would never have to admit — the fear came from themselves."},{"cn":"玄鬼的手指微微收緊。","en":"Genki's fingers tightened slightly."},{"cn":"他能繼續「完成」流程。","en":"He could go on and \"complete\" the procedure."},{"cn":"他能把這半拍消除，讓夜行回到應有的速度，讓恐懼被吞下去，讓江戶明日依舊像什麼都沒發生。","en":"He could erase that half beat, return the Parade to its proper pace, let the fear be swallowed, let Edo wake tomorrow as if nothing had happened."},{"cn":"他也能——停下來。","en":"Or he could — stop."},{"cn":"停下來意味著他要承受後果。","en":"Stopping meant bearing the consequences."},{"cn":"因為在這個世界裡，停下來的鬼，仍然會被叫做鬼。","en":"Because in this world, an oni that stops is still called an oni."},{"cn":"可停下來的人，未必會被叫做人。","en":"But one who stops is not always called human."},{"cn":"玄鬼的喉嚨像被灰堵住。","en":"Genki's throat felt stopped with ash."},{"cn":"他想說什麼，卻發現自己根本沒有語言能說。","en":"He wanted to say something, and found he had no language to say it in."},{"cn":"他只能——把那一步收回。","en":"All he could do was — draw that one step back."},{"cn":"那一步收回的瞬間，夜色深處傳來一聲極輕的笑。","en":"The instant the step was drawn back, a very soft laugh came from deep in the night."},{"cn":"像狐狸尾巴掃過雪。","en":"Like a fox's tail sweeping over snow."},{"cn":"白蓮站在屋脊的陰影裡，衣袖不動，長髮卻像墨色的水流下來。","en":"Byakuren stood in the shadow of a roof ridge, sleeves unmoving, her long hair flowing down like water of ink."},{"cn":"月光不敢落在她身上，像知道自己一旦照亮她，便會被她看透。","en":"The moonlight dared not fall on her, as if it knew that to light her was to be seen through by her."},{"cn":"她看見了整個過程：","en":"She had seen the whole of it:"},{"cn":"鬼的手抬起、停頓、收回。","en":"the oni's hand rising, pausing, drawing back."},{"cn":"孩子的眼神。","en":"The child's eyes."},{"cn":"恐懼的滯留。","en":"The fear left lingering."},{"cn":"她不急著靠近。","en":"She was in no hurry to approach."},{"cn":"不急著說話。","en":"In no hurry to speak."},{"cn":"白蓮的眼睛像兩片薄冰，冷而清，映著江戶城裡千百年都不變的規則：","en":"Byakuren's eyes were like two slivers of thin ice, cold and clear, reflecting the rule of Edo that a thousand years had never changed:"},{"cn":"世界需要鬼。","en":"The world needs an oni."},{"cn":"因為世界需要一個能承擔「惡」的容器。","en":"Because the world needs a vessel that can bear \"evil.\""},{"cn":"但如果鬼不再承擔呢？","en":"But what if the oni stopped bearing it?"},{"cn":"她的心裡浮出一個很久以前就存在的詞。","en":"A word rose in her heart, one that had existed there a very long time."},{"cn":"那不是佛寺裡的口誦，也不是陰陽師的符文。","en":"Not a chant from the temples, not an onmyōji's script."},{"cn":"那只是某種更古老的願望，被她記住了太久太久。","en":"Only some older wish, remembered too long, far too long."},{"cn":"——無垢界。","en":"— The Immaculate Realm (Mukukai)."},{"cn":"一個不需要任何存在被定義為惡的地方。","en":"A place where no being need be defined as evil."},{"cn":"一個不需要鬼來承擔人類偏見的地方。","en":"A place where no oni need bear human prejudice."},{"cn":"一個……會讓很多人失去「怪罪出口」的地方。","en":"A place that… would cost a great many people their outlet for blame."},{"cn":"白蓮本該嘲笑這樣的地方。","en":"Byakuren should have laughed at such a place."},{"cn":"她活得夠久，早知道人並不想要無垢。","en":"She had lived long enough to know that people do not want immaculacy."},{"cn":"人只想要「看起來無垢」。","en":"People only want to \"appear immaculate.\""},{"cn":"但她仍記得另一個詞。","en":"Yet she remembered another word."},{"cn":"那是抵達無垢界時的狀態——","en":"The state of one who arrives in the Immaculate Realm —"},{"cn":"不是光芒刺眼，不是奇蹟降臨。","en":"Not blinding light, not miracle descending."},{"cn":"而是一種純金般穩定的沉靜：","en":"But a stillness steady as pure gold:"},{"cn":"——金寂。","en":"— Golden Stillness (Kinjaku)."},{"cn":"她在屋脊上微微俯身，像在行禮，又像在觀察獵物。","en":"On the roof ridge she bowed forward slightly, as if in courtesy, or as if studying prey."},{"cn":"「原來如此。」她輕聲說，像怕驚動夜色本身。","en":"\"So that's how it is,\" she said softly, as if afraid of startling the night itself."},{"cn":"「錯誤，出現了。」","en":"\"The error has appeared.\""},{"cn":"而玄鬼站在街口，聽見夜行遠處的步伐仍在前進——","en":"And Genki stood at the street corner, hearing the Parade's tread continue in the distance —"},{"cn":"隊伍並沒有等他。","en":"The column had not waited for him."},{"cn":"它像一條不需要他也能流動的河，繼續把恐懼往更深的黑暗裡帶走。","en":"Like a river that could flow without him, it went on carrying the fear away into deeper darkness."},{"cn":"留下他一個人，站在江戶城的陰影中，第一次感到自己像被丟在岸上。","en":"Leaving him alone, standing in the shadow of Edo, feeling for the first time like something left on the shore."},{"cn":"孩子仍看著他。","en":"The child was still watching him."},{"cn":"那雙眼睛沒有恐懼，只有困惑與一點點擔心。","en":"There was no fear in those eyes, only puzzlement and a small measure of worry."},{"cn":"像是他不是怪物，而是一個迷路的人。","en":"As if he were not a monster, but someone who had lost his way."},{"cn":"玄鬼低頭，看著自己的手。","en":"Genki lowered his head and looked at his own hand."},{"cn":"那隻手曾經替無數恐懼完成儀式，替無數偏見長出牙。","en":"That hand had completed the rite for countless fears, had grown teeth for countless prejudices."},{"cn":"如今，它停在半空，像忽然不知道該往哪裡落。","en":"Now it hung in midair, as if suddenly unsure where to fall."},{"cn":"他忽然明白了一件事：","en":"He suddenly understood one thing:"},{"cn":"如果他停止回應人的惡，","en":"If he stopped answering human evil,"},{"cn":"人會更用力地把惡塞進他身上。","en":"people would only stuff their evil into him harder."},{"cn":"因為那樣，人就不用承認——惡本來就在他們心裡。","en":"Because then they would never have to admit — the evil had been in their hearts all along."},{"cn":"玄鬼慢慢吐出一口氣。","en":"Genki let out a slow breath."},{"cn":"那口氣在冷夜裡成霧，又很快散掉。","en":"It turned to mist in the cold night, and quickly scattered."},{"cn":"像他本該消失卻還被迫存在的命運。","en":"Like his own fate: meant to vanish, forced to remain."},{"cn":"遠處的夜行聲越來越淡。","en":"The sound of the Parade grew fainter in the distance."},{"cn":"江戶的街道卻沒有因此變亮。","en":"The streets of Edo grew no brighter for it."},{"cn":"恐懼滯留著，像一條無形的蛇，鑽進每一戶人的門縫。","en":"The fear lingered, an unseen snake slipping through the crack of every door."},{"cn":"屋裡的父親會更用力地教訓孩子，母親會更用力地摟緊，老人會更用力地祈求。","en":"Inside, fathers would scold their children harder, mothers would clutch them tighter, old men would pray with more force."},{"cn":"他們會更確定：鬼更可怕了。","en":"They would be more certain than ever: the oni has grown more terrible."},{"cn":"玄鬼站在那裡，忽然感到胸口有一種陌生的疼。","en":"Standing there, Genki felt an unfamiliar ache in his chest."},{"cn":"那不是刀傷，不是火燒。","en":"Not a sword wound, not a burn."},{"cn":"那是一種更慢、更深的——","en":"Something slower, deeper —"},{"cn":"被留下來的疼。","en":"the ache of being left behind."},{"cn":"而白蓮在高處看著他，眼神仍冷，卻第一次有了一絲幾乎不可察的動搖。","en":"And Byakuren watched him from above, her gaze still cold, yet holding, for the first time, a wavering almost too faint to see."},{"cn":"她心想：","en":"She thought:"},{"cn":"如果這個鬼真的不再回應，","en":"If this oni truly stops answering,"},{"cn":"那他最後會被留下來的——不只是一個夜晚。","en":"then what he is left holding, in the end — will not be a single night."},{"cn":"也許會是一整個世界。","en":"It may be an entire world."},{"cn":"⸻","en":"⸻"},{"cn":"（序章完）","en":"(End of Prologue)"},{"cn":"⸻","en":"⸻"},{"cn":"第一部｜百鬼夜行","en":"Part One — The Night Parade"}]},{"id":"ch01","n":1,"title_cn":"第一章｜停下來的瞬間","title_en":"Chapter 1 — The Moment He Stopped","lines":[{"cn":"夜行遠去之後，江戶並沒有立刻變回一座城市。","en":"After the Night Parade had gone far off, Edo did not at once turn back into a city."},{"cn":"燈火仍在，門仍緊閉，風仍從河面吹來，可街道像被某種看不見的東西浸泡過——空氣裡多了一層黏稠的冷，像油，又像汗。","en":"The lamps still burned, the doors still stood shut, the wind still blew off the river, but the streets seemed steeped in something unseen — the air carried an extra layer of clinging cold, like oil, or like sweat."},{"cn":"它附在皮膚上，讓人覺得自己被盯著；附在喉嚨裡，讓人吞嚥時微微發痛。","en":"It clung to the skin, so that people felt watched; it clung inside the throat, so that swallowing brought a faint ache."},{"cn":"那是恐懼的殘留。","en":"That was the residue of fear."},{"cn":"以往，百鬼夜行會把它帶走，像潮水把岸邊的垃圾捲回海裡。","en":"In the past, the Night Parade would have carried it away, the way the tide drags the litter on the shore back into the sea."},{"cn":"今夜卻不一樣。今夜的潮水走了，岸上留下了濕漉漉的痕跡與腥味。","en":"Tonight was different. Tonight the tide had gone, and left on the shore a damp trace, and a smell like raw flesh."},{"cn":"赤座玄鬼站在街口，聽見自己心跳的聲音。","en":"Akaza Genki stood at the street corner, and heard the sound of his own heartbeat."},{"cn":"他早已忘了自己也有心跳。","en":"He had long since forgotten that he too had a heartbeat."},{"cn":"在那些被指名、被咒罵、被恐懼塑形的漫長年月裡，他以為自己只剩一副會動的殼——走在最前面，做該做的事，背負人們不肯背負的那部分。","en":"Through those long years of being named, being cursed, being shaped by fear, he had come to think of himself as nothing more than a shell that moved — walking at the head, doing what needed doing, bearing the part that people would not bear."},{"cn":"但剛才那一瞬間，他聽見了。","en":"But in that instant just past, he had heard it."},{"cn":"咚。","en":"Thud."},{"cn":"咚。","en":"Thud."},{"cn":"像兩下沉悶的鼓點，在胸腔裡慢慢敲。","en":"Like two dull drumbeats, striking slowly inside his chest."},{"cn":"他抬起手，掌心朝外，指節粗大，掌紋深得像裂谷。","en":"He raised his hand, palm turned outward, the knuckles thick, the lines of his palm cut deep as ravines."},{"cn":"那隻手曾經不止一次覆上人的頭顱——不是撫摸，而是完成一個「被需要的殘忍」。","en":"That hand had more than once come down over a human head — not a caress, but the completion of a cruelty that was needed."},{"cn":"他只要把手落下去，今夜就會回到正軌：恐懼被回收，夜行順利離去，人類明日照常開市，照常笑，照常把惡藏進袖子裡。","en":"He had only to let the hand fall, and tonight would return to its proper course: the fear reclaimed, the Parade passing on without incident, humankind opening their shops again tomorrow, laughing again, hiding their malice in their sleeves again."},{"cn":"他的手卻停在半空。","en":"His hand stopped, in midair."},{"cn":"停得不久。","en":"It did not stop for long."},{"cn":"也不短。","en":"Nor was it brief."},{"cn":"正好足夠讓他感到那一瞬的遲疑，像骨頭裡突然生出一根刺。","en":"Just long enough for him to feel that instant of hesitation, like a thorn suddenly grown inside a bone."},{"cn":"身後傳來隊伍的躁動。","en":"Behind him came the stirring of the column."},{"cn":"不是聲音——至少不是凡人能聽懂的聲音。","en":"Not a sound — not one a mortal could understand as sound."},{"cn":"那更像無數腳步同時在黑暗裡加重，像一整片影子開始不耐煩地扭動。","en":"It was more like countless footsteps all at once growing heavier in the dark, like a whole sheet of shadow beginning to writhe with impatience."},{"cn":"夜行從來不等任何個體。它是過程，是機制，是城市裡那些被壓抑到發臭的東西的自動排泄。","en":"The Night Parade never waited for any single one of its own. It was process, it was mechanism, it was the automatic purge of all that the city had suppressed until it festered."},{"cn":"玄鬼知道自己如果再遲疑，隊伍會繼續往前推。","en":"Genki knew that if he hesitated longer, the column would keep pressing forward."},{"cn":"他會被推著走，像往常一樣。","en":"He would be swept along with it, as always."},{"cn":"他也知道，如果他收回那一步——","en":"He knew this too: if he drew that step back —"},{"cn":"夜行不會為他停。","en":"the Parade would not stop for him."},{"cn":"恐懼不會因此消失。","en":"The fear would not, for that, vanish."},{"cn":"城市不會因為他做了「善」就變得更善。","en":"The city would not, for that, become more good because he had done a \"good\" thing."},{"cn":"他把手慢慢收回。","en":"He drew his hand back, slowly."},{"cn":"像收回一把刀。","en":"Like sheathing a blade."},{"cn":"這個動作比抬手更難。","en":"This motion was harder than raising the hand had been."},{"cn":"抬手是本能；收回是選擇。","en":"Raising the hand was instinct; drawing it back was choice."},{"cn":"他聽見背後的潮水開始遠離。","en":"He heard the tide behind him begin to withdraw."},{"cn":"百鬼夜行的步伐沒有停頓，反而像被誰輕輕推了一把，走得更快、更齊。","en":"The Night Parade's tread did not falter — if anything it seemed pushed gently onward by someone, walking faster, more in step."},{"cn":"玄鬼幾乎能感覺到那股力量擦過他的背，帶走了他身上某部分熟悉的重量——不是卸下，而是被抽走。","en":"Genki could almost feel that force brush past his back, taking with it some familiar weight from his body — not laid down, but drawn out of him."},{"cn":"像一個人忽然發現：自己不再是隊伍必需的齒輪。","en":"Like a man who suddenly discovers he is no longer a gear the column requires."},{"cn":"那感覺不是解脫。","en":"That feeling was not release."},{"cn":"是空。","en":"It was emptiness."},{"cn":"屋內的孩子仍看著他。","en":"The child in the house was still watching him."},{"cn":"那雙眼睛貼在紙門縫隙後，亮得像兩顆尚未被煙灰沾染的露珠。","en":"Those eyes were pressed to the gap in the paper door, bright as two dewdrops not yet touched by soot."},{"cn":"孩子的母親低聲念著佛號，手指抖得像在數命；父親把手按在刀柄上，卻不敢拉門——因為拉開門意味著承認自己「看見」。","en":"The child's mother murmured a Buddhist invocation under her breath, her fingers trembling as though counting out a life; the father set his hand on the hilt of his sword, yet dared not slide the door — because to open it would mean admitting he had \"seen.\""},{"cn":"孩子卻看見了。","en":"But the child had seen."},{"cn":"他看見玄鬼的手收回去時，指尖微微顫了一下。","en":"He saw that as Genki's hand drew back, the fingertips trembled, faintly."},{"cn":"不是憤怒的顫，而像疲憊的人終於放下重物時，手臂仍殘留的震動。","en":"Not the tremble of anger, but the shiver still left in an arm after a weary man finally sets down something heavy."},{"cn":"孩子的困惑變得更深。","en":"The child's puzzlement deepened."},{"cn":"他想問——你是不是很累？","en":"He wanted to ask — are you not very tired?"},{"cn":"他不知道這句話怎麼出口，因為大人們只教過他：鬼是可怕的，不能問。","en":"He did not know how to make the words come out, for the grown-ups had only ever taught him: the oni is terrible, and must not be questioned."},{"cn":"于是他只是把眼睛睜得更大一些。","en":"So he only opened his eyes a little wider."},{"cn":"像想把答案看清楚。","en":"As though trying to see the answer clearly."},{"cn":"玄鬼與他對視。","en":"Genki met his gaze."},{"cn":"那一瞬間，玄鬼突然明白：","en":"In that instant, Genki suddenly understood:"},{"cn":"恐懼不是天生的。","en":"fear is not born in a person."},{"cn":"恐懼是被教出來的。","en":"Fear is taught."},{"cn":"孩子還沒學會教條，所以他還能看見「鬼」以外的東西。","en":"The child had not yet learned the doctrine, and so he could still see something beyond \"the oni.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼喉嚨裡湧上一股陌生的酸。","en":"A strange sourness rose in Genki's throat."},{"cn":"那不是感動，也不是慈悲。","en":"It was not being moved, and it was not mercy."},{"cn":"更像某種突如其來的羞愧——","en":"It was more like a sudden shame —"},{"cn":"羞愧於自己竟然也渴望被如此看見。","en":"shame that he himself should long to be seen this way."},{"cn":"他轉開視線。","en":"He turned his gaze aside."},{"cn":"那是他第一次逃避一雙人類的眼睛。","en":"It was the first time he had fled from a pair of human eyes."},{"cn":"屋脊之上，九條白蓮靜靜俯視。","en":"Above, on the roof ridge, Kujō Byakuren looked quietly down."},{"cn":"她沒有像陰陽師那樣掐訣，也沒有像狐妖那樣放出狐火。","en":"She did not form seals like an onmyōji, nor did she release fox-fire like a common fox spirit."},{"cn":"她只是站著，衣袖垂落，像一朵不屬於人世的白花，扎根在瓦片的縫隙裡。","en":"She only stood, sleeves hanging still, like a white flower that did not belong to the human world, rooted in the gap between the tiles."},{"cn":"她看見玄鬼收回手的瞬間，江戶的恐懼沒有被回收——而是像失去出口的煙，回流進每一戶人的屋內。","en":"She had seen the whole of it — the instant Genki's hand drew back, Edo's fear was not reclaimed, but flowed back like smoke that had lost its outlet, back into every house."},{"cn":"她甚至看見更細微的事：","en":"She saw something even finer than that:"},{"cn":"恐懼不是散的，而是聚的。","en":"fear was not scattering, but gathering."},{"cn":"它在夜行離去後變得黏稠、集中，像一團看不見的墨，附在最脆弱的人身上。","en":"After the Parade withdrew, it thickened and concentrated, like an invisible ink clinging to the most fragile among the people."},{"cn":"白蓮的嘴角幾乎要翹起，又被她壓下。","en":"The corner of Byakuren's mouth nearly lifted, then she pressed it back down."},{"cn":"她想起很多年前自己曾犯過的錯：","en":"She remembered a mistake she herself had made, many years before:"},{"cn":"她曾以為只要把恐懼導向某個方向，世界就會穩。","en":"she had once believed that if fear were only steered in one direction, the world would hold steady."},{"cn":"她曾以為只要把人心的惡安排在可控的容器裡，世道就能保持表面的平靜。","en":"She had once believed that if the evil in human hearts were only arranged into a controllable vessel, the age could keep the appearance of peace."},{"cn":"玉藻前就是那種「安排」最失敗的例子。","en":"Tamamo-no-Mae was the very worst example of such an \"arrangement.\""},{"cn":"——把罪推給一個名字，讓所有人都能繼續假裝自己無辜。","en":"— Push the guilt onto one name, and let everyone go on pretending innocence."},{"cn":"白蓮早該知道，人類不需要真相。","en":"Byakuren should have known long ago that humankind has no need of truth."},{"cn":"人類需要出口。","en":"Humankind needs an outlet."},{"cn":"出口最好是某個「不是自己」的存在。","en":"The outlet is best when it is something \"not themselves.\""},{"cn":"而鬼，就是那個最方便的存在。","en":"And the oni — the oni is the most convenient such thing there is."},{"cn":"白蓮低聲念了一句像是自言自語的話：","en":"Byakuren murmured something, as if to herself:"},{"cn":"「如果你不再承擔，他們會更用力把它塞給你。」","en":"\"If you no longer bear it, they will only press it into you harder.\""},{"cn":"她不是在警告玄鬼。","en":"She was not warning Genki."},{"cn":"她是在確認規律。","en":"She was confirming a law."},{"cn":"她活得夠久，知道規律才是世界真正的神。","en":"She had lived long enough to know that law was the only true god of this world."},{"cn":"街角，河水輕響。","en":"At the street corner, the river gave a soft sound."},{"cn":"一個濕漉漉的頭從河裡冒出來，像一顆浮起的青石。","en":"A dripping head rose up out of the water, like a round stone surfacing."},{"cn":"碧吉把手按在岸邊，半個身子爬上來，皿裡的水晃得很危險。","en":"Aokichi set his hands on the bank and hauled half his body up; the water in his dish sloshed dangerously."},{"cn":"他原本不該出來。","en":"He should not have come out at all."},{"cn":"百鬼夜行的時候，碧吉最懂得躲。","en":"During the Night Parade, Aokichi knew better than anyone how to hide."},{"cn":"他懂得人類恐懼最重時，最容易拿他這種「半玩笑的妖怪」開刀——","en":"He knew that when human fear ran heaviest, it was easiest for them to turn on a yokai like him — one that was half a joke —"},{"cn":"被抓住時，笑話就會變成刑罰。","en":"for once caught, the joke would turn to punishment."},{"cn":"可他今晚忍不住。","en":"But tonight he could not help himself."},{"cn":"也許是因為夜行的節奏變了。","en":"Perhaps it was because the rhythm of the Parade had changed."},{"cn":"也許是因為他看見玄鬼竟然停下來。","en":"Perhaps it was because he had seen Genki actually stop."},{"cn":"又或許，是因為他忽然想起自己也曾有過一個念頭：","en":"Or perhaps, because he suddenly remembered a thought he too had once had:"},{"cn":"如果我不再做大家期待我做的事，我還剩下什麼？","en":"if I no longer do what everyone expects of me, what is left of me?"},{"cn":"碧吉清了清喉嚨，試圖讓自己看起來像平常一樣不正經。","en":"Aokichi cleared his throat, trying to look as flippant as usual."},{"cn":"「欸……那個……」他笑得有點乾，「夜行走掉了？你怎麼還在？」","en":"\"Er… so…\" he laughed, a little dry, \"the Parade's gone on, hasn't it? Why are you still here?\""},{"cn":"玄鬼沒有立刻回答。","en":"Genki did not answer at once."},{"cn":"他看著碧吉，像看一個不合規則的漏水點。","en":"He looked at Aokichi the way one looks at a leak that should not exist."},{"cn":"百鬼夜行不會留下任何妖怪。","en":"The Night Parade left no yokai behind."},{"cn":"留下的不是妖怪，是被排除的碎屑。","en":"What was left behind was not a yokai, but discarded debris."},{"cn":"碧吉被那眼神盯得縮了縮脖子，皿裡的水又晃了一下。","en":"Pinned by that gaze, Aokichi drew his neck in, and the water in his dish sloshed again."},{"cn":"「我、我不是來找麻煩的。」碧吉急忙說，「我只是……覺得……」","en":"\"I — I'm not here to make trouble,\" Aokichi said quickly. \"I just… felt…\""},{"cn":"他找不到詞，最後只說了最誠實也最不堪的一句：","en":"He could not find the word, and in the end said the most honest, and most unbecoming, thing he could:"},{"cn":"「覺得你很像……被丟下了。」","en":"\"Felt like you looked… left behind.\""},{"cn":"這句話落下來，空氣更冷了一點。","en":"The words fell, and the air went a shade colder."},{"cn":"玄鬼的指尖動了動。","en":"Genki's fingers twitched."},{"cn":"他本能地想把這句話掐斷——像掐斷一個太接近自己的真相。","en":"His instinct was to cut the words off — the way one cuts off a truth that has come too close."},{"cn":"但他沒有。","en":"But he did not."},{"cn":"他只是把目光移開，像怕自己一旦承認，就再也回不到以前那種麻木的安全。","en":"He only looked away, as though afraid that if he once admitted it, he could never return to that old, numb safety."},{"cn":"白蓮在高處看著這一幕，眼睛微微眯起。","en":"Above, Byakuren watched this unfold, her eyes narrowing slightly."},{"cn":"第一個跟隨者出現了。","en":"The first follower had appeared."},{"cn":"不是因為玄鬼偉大。","en":"Not because Genki was great."},{"cn":"而是因為有人太孤單，孤單到寧可跟著一個被恐懼指名的鬼。","en":"But because someone was lonely enough — lonely enough to follow even an oni named by fear."},{"cn":"白蓮心裡的某個計算開始轉動。","en":"Some calculation in Byakuren's mind began turning."},{"cn":"如果要讓「錯誤」擴散，必須有人留下來。","en":"If the \"error\" was to spread, someone had to remain."},{"cn":"如果要讓留下來變成修行，必須有人願意承擔留下的代價。","en":"If remaining was to become the Practice, someone had to be willing to bear the cost of remaining."},{"cn":"如果要讓承擔變成可能，必須有人——不再把鬼當作工具。","en":"If bearing was to become possible, someone had to — stop treating the oni as a tool."},{"cn":"她在心裡再次默念那個名詞：無垢界。","en":"In her heart she recited the term again: the Immaculate Realm."},{"cn":"又默念那個狀態：金寂。","en":"And recited the state again: Golden Stillness."},{"cn":"那不是安慰。","en":"That was not comfort."},{"cn":"那是目標。","en":"That was a goal."},{"cn":"而目標之所以值得追求，往往是因為它幾乎不可能。","en":"And a goal is worth pursuing precisely because it is nearly impossible."},{"cn":"這時，遠處傳來一聲破裂的響。","en":"Just then, a cracking sound came from somewhere far off."},{"cn":"像木頭被擰斷，又像紙被撕開。","en":"Like wood wrenched apart, or paper torn."},{"cn":"玄鬼與白蓮同時抬頭。","en":"Genki and Byakuren looked up at the same instant."},{"cn":"那不是人類聽得見的聲音。","en":"It was not a sound humans could hear."},{"cn":"那是「規律」在自我修正時發出的聲音。","en":"It was the sound \"law\" made when correcting itself."},{"cn":"夜行走遠了，本該把恐懼帶走。","en":"The Parade had gone far off, and should have carried the fear away with it."},{"cn":"可恐懼滯留。","en":"But the fear had stayed."},{"cn":"滯留的恐懼開始尋找新的形體。","en":"The fear that stayed had begun searching for a new shape."},{"cn":"江戶城內，有某個角落的影子，突然變得更深、更厚。","en":"Somewhere within Edo, a shadow in some corner had suddenly grown deeper, thicker."},{"cn":"像有人在墨裡再滴了一滴墨。","en":"As if someone had let one more drop of ink fall into ink."},{"cn":"那影子貼著牆，慢慢站起來——沒有臉，沒有口，只有一股強烈的指向性：","en":"That shadow pressed against the wall and slowly rose — no face, no mouth, only one strong intent:"},{"cn":"要找一個可以怪罪的東西。","en":"to find something it could blame."},{"cn":"碧吉打了個寒顫，突然明白自己為什麼不該出來。","en":"Aokichi shuddered, and suddenly understood why he should not have come out."},{"cn":"他往後退了一步，腳踩在濕石上，差點滑倒。","en":"He stepped back, his foot slipping on the wet stone, and nearly fell."},{"cn":"「那、那是什麼？」他小聲問。","en":"\"Wh-what is that?\" he asked in a small voice."},{"cn":"玄鬼沒有回答。","en":"Genki did not answer."},{"cn":"他只是向前踏了一步。","en":"He only stepped forward."},{"cn":"不是朝夜行，","en":"Not toward the Parade,"},{"cn":"而是朝那團逐漸凝成形的影子。","en":"but toward that shadow slowly gathering into shape."},{"cn":"他知道那是什麼。","en":"He knew what it was."},{"cn":"那不是妖怪。","en":"It was not a yokai."},{"cn":"那是人類的偏見找不到出口時，自己長出來的牙。","en":"It was the fang that human prejudice grows for itself, when it can find no outlet."},{"cn":"白蓮在屋脊上緩緩站直。","en":"On the roof ridge, Byakuren slowly straightened."},{"cn":"她第一次把手從袖中抽出一點點，像準備測試某個結果。","en":"For the first time she drew her hand a little way out of her sleeve, as if preparing to test some outcome."},{"cn":"而玄鬼站在街口，背影沉得像一座門。","en":"And Genki stood at the street corner, his back heavy as a gate."},{"cn":"他忽然明白：","en":"He suddenly understood:"},{"cn":"停止回應，並不會讓惡消失。","en":"to stop answering did not make evil vanish."},{"cn":"只會讓惡露出它原本的樣子。","en":"It only made evil show its true shape."},{"cn":"他回頭看了碧吉一眼。","en":"He glanced back once at Aokichi."},{"cn":"那一眼沒有命令，沒有威嚇。","en":"That glance carried no order, no threat."},{"cn":"只有一句無聲的訊息：","en":"Only one wordless message:"},{"cn":"如果你要留下，就準備承受。","en":"if you mean to stay, be ready to bear it."},{"cn":"碧吉咬緊牙，皿裡的水晃得更厲害了。","en":"Aokichi clenched his teeth, and the water in his dish sloshed harder still."},{"cn":"然後他點頭。","en":"Then he nodded."},{"cn":"夜色更深，江戶的恐懼在角落裡開始成形。","en":"The night grew deeper, and Edo's fear began, in its corner, to take shape."},{"cn":"而百鬼夜行遠處的步伐，仍像潮水——","en":"And the Night Parade's tread, off in the distance, still moved like the tide —"},{"cn":"不為任何個體回頭。","en":"turning back for no one."},{"cn":"（第一章完）","en":"(End of Chapter 1)"},{"cn":"⸻","en":"⸻"},{"cn":"第一部｜百鬼夜行","en":"Part One — The Night Parade"}]},{"id":"ch02","n":2,"title_cn":"第二章｜被留下的夜","title_en":"Chapter 2 — The Night Left Behind","lines":[{"cn":"夜行走遠之後，江戶並沒有睡著。","en":"After the Parade had gone far off, Edo did not fall asleep."},{"cn":"有些人翻身更頻繁。","en":"Some people turned over in bed more often than usual."},{"cn":"有些人做了夢，醒來卻不記得內容，只記得心口沉沉。","en":"Some dreamed, and woke remembering nothing of it, only a heaviness in the chest."},{"cn":"還有些人——看見了。","en":"And some — saw."},{"cn":"⸻","en":"⸻"},{"cn":"【人類視角】","en":"[The Human View]"},{"cn":"在日本橋東側，一間小小的印刷鋪子裡，燈仍亮著。","en":"On the east side of Nihonbashi, in a small print shop, a lamp still burned."},{"cn":"年輕的版刻師名叫新之助，正伏在木版前。","en":"The young woodblock carver was named Shinnosuke, bent over his block."},{"cn":"他本該睡了，可今晚的客人催得急——要一批新的怪談畫，說是最近「鬼氣」更重，越是可怕的畫越好賣。","en":"He should have been asleep by now, but tonight's customer had pressed him hard — a new batch of ghost-story prints wanted, since lately \"the air of the oni\" ran heavier, and the more terrible the picture, the better it sold."},{"cn":"他刻的是一張鬼的臉。","en":"He was carving an oni's face."},{"cn":"角誇張得像樹枝，眼珠凸出，牙齒尖利，口水滴落。","en":"The horns exaggerated like branches, the eyes bulging, the teeth sharp, drool dripping down."},{"cn":"他刻得很熟練，刀尖在木板上滑動時幾乎沒有猶豫。","en":"He carved it with practiced ease, the blade sliding over the wood almost without hesitation."},{"cn":"這種臉，他刻過太多次。","en":"He had carved this face too many times to count."},{"cn":"可今夜，他的手停了一下。","en":"But tonight, his hand stopped."},{"cn":"不是因為害怕。","en":"Not out of fear."},{"cn":"而是因為他忽然想不起——","en":"But because he suddenly could not remember —"},{"cn":"鬼真的長這樣嗎？","en":"did an oni really look like this?"},{"cn":"他小時候也曾聽母親說過鬼。","en":"As a boy he too had heard his mother speak of oni."},{"cn":"母親說，鬼是壞人死後變的，是懲罰，是報應。","en":"His mother said an oni was what a wicked person became after death, a punishment, a retribution."},{"cn":"可他從未親眼見過。","en":"But he had never once seen one with his own eyes."},{"cn":"「越醜越好。」客人說過。","en":"\"The uglier, the better,\" the customer had said."},{"cn":"「人看了才會怕，怕了才會買。」","en":"\"People are only afraid once they've looked, and only buy once they're afraid.\""},{"cn":"新之助抬頭，揉了揉酸痛的眼睛。","en":"Shinnosuke looked up and rubbed his aching eyes."},{"cn":"燈火晃了一下。","en":"The lamp flame wavered once."},{"cn":"就在那一晃之間，他看見牆角的影子比平常更深。","en":"In that single flicker, he saw the shadow in the corner grow deeper than usual."},{"cn":"不是燈影。","en":"It was not the lamp's shadow."},{"cn":"燈影會隨火動，那影子卻靜著。","en":"A lamp's shadow moves with the flame; this shadow held still."},{"cn":"他心口一緊。","en":"His chest tightened."},{"cn":"不是看見什麼形體，而是感到一股視線。","en":"He saw no shape — only felt a gaze."},{"cn":"像有人在盯著他刻的那張鬼臉。","en":"As though someone were staring at the oni's face he had carved."},{"cn":"新之助下意識地後退半步，椅腳刮地，發出刺耳的聲響。","en":"Shinnosuke drew back half a step without thinking, the chair leg scraping the floor with a harsh sound."},{"cn":"「……誰？」","en":"\"…Who's there?\""},{"cn":"沒有回應。","en":"No answer."},{"cn":"只有牆角那團濃重的黑，像慢慢貼著牆往上爬。","en":"Only that thick black mass in the corner, seeming to crawl slowly up the wall."},{"cn":"他突然明白了什麼。","en":"He suddenly understood something."},{"cn":"恐懼不是因為看見鬼。","en":"The fear was not from seeing an oni."},{"cn":"恐懼是因為——他正在製造鬼。","en":"The fear was because — he himself was making one."},{"cn":"他的刀，正在替某個模糊的存在刻出牙。","en":"His blade was carving fangs for some formless thing."},{"cn":"新之助猛地用布蓋住木版，心跳如鼓。","en":"Shinnosuke threw a cloth over the block, his heart pounding like a drum."},{"cn":"他不知道，在街的另一端，玄鬼也正在看著同一種黑暗。","en":"He did not know that, at the far end of the street, Genki was looking at that very same darkness."},{"cn":"⸻","en":"⸻"},{"cn":"【回到夜街】","en":"[Back on the Night Street]"},{"cn":"那團影子不是妖怪。","en":"That shadow was not a yokai."},{"cn":"它沒有名字，也沒有傳說。","en":"It had no name, and no legend."},{"cn":"它只是一種力量，從滯留的恐懼裡凝出來——沒有被夜行回收的部分，開始自行生長。","en":"It was only a force, condensed out of fear that had stayed too long — the part the Parade had failed to reclaim, now growing on its own."},{"cn":"玄鬼看著它，胸口的沉重更深。","en":"Genki watched it, and the weight in his chest grew deeper."},{"cn":"他曾見過這種形態。","en":"He had seen this shape before."},{"cn":"當人類長時間壓抑某種偏見，它就會自行尋找容器。","en":"When humans suppress some prejudice long enough, it goes looking for a vessel of its own."},{"cn":"如果沒有鬼承擔，它便會變成更扭曲的東西。","en":"If no oni bears it, it becomes something more twisted still."},{"cn":"碧吉站在他身後，聲音顫得不穩。","en":"Aokichi stood behind him, his voice unsteady."},{"cn":"「那、那不是我們的人吧……？」","en":"\"That — that's not one of ours, is it…?\""},{"cn":"玄鬼搖頭。","en":"Genki shook his head."},{"cn":"「不是。」","en":"\"No.\""},{"cn":"那東西動了。","en":"The thing moved."},{"cn":"不是走路，而像濃墨被風吹動，貼著地面滑行。","en":"Not walking — more like thick ink blown by wind, sliding along the ground."},{"cn":"它沒有眼睛，卻朝著最近的恐懼聚集之處移去——朝著新之助的印刷鋪。","en":"It had no eyes, yet it moved toward the nearest gathering of fear — toward Shinnosuke's print shop."},{"cn":"玄鬼向前一步。","en":"Genki stepped forward."},{"cn":"那不是出於責任。","en":"It was not out of duty."},{"cn":"也不是出於正義。","en":"Nor out of justice."},{"cn":"只是因為他知道，如果放任那東西成形，明天的怪談會更多，畫會更醜，恐懼會更重。","en":"Only because he knew that if that thing were allowed to take shape, tomorrow's ghost stories would multiply, the pictures would grow uglier, the fear heavier."},{"cn":"然後——夜行會更沉。","en":"And then — the Parade would grow heavier still."},{"cn":"他伸出手。","en":"He put out his hand."},{"cn":"這一次，他不是為了回收恐懼。","en":"This time, it was not to reclaim fear."},{"cn":"而是為了阻止恐懼變形。","en":"It was to stop fear from taking shape."},{"cn":"他的掌心貼上那團黑。","en":"His palm pressed against the black mass."},{"cn":"黑影像被燙到般扭曲，發出沒有聲音的尖叫。","en":"The shadow twisted as if scalded, and let out a soundless scream."},{"cn":"那不是痛，而是失去形體的不甘。","en":"It was not pain, but the resentment of a thing losing its form."},{"cn":"玄鬼閉上眼。","en":"Genki closed his eyes."},{"cn":"他感覺到那黑暗裡混著許多東西——","en":"He felt many things mixed within that darkness —"},{"cn":"嫉妒、怨恨、羞愧、被壓抑的憤怒、被利用的不甘。","en":"envy, resentment, shame, suppressed anger, the resentment of being used."},{"cn":"他聽見某個聲音在裡面反覆低語：","en":"He heard a voice within it, murmuring over and over:"},{"cn":"「給我一個名字。」","en":"\"Give me a name.\""},{"cn":"「給我一個可以怪罪的東西。」","en":"\"Give me something to blame.\""},{"cn":"「給我一個鬼。」","en":"\"Give me an oni.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼的手微微顫抖。","en":"Genki's hand trembled, faintly."},{"cn":"他知道，只要他順勢承認——","en":"He knew that if he only gave way and admitted it —"},{"cn":"只要他把那黑影吸納進自己身體裡，","en":"if he only drew that shadow into his own body,"},{"cn":"它就會安靜。","en":"it would grow quiet."},{"cn":"人類會睡得更好。","en":"Humankind would sleep better."},{"cn":"版刻師會刻出更可怕的鬼。","en":"The woodblock carver would carve an even more terrible oni."},{"cn":"世界會繼續穩定。","en":"The world would go on being stable."},{"cn":"他卻沒有那麼做。","en":"But he did not do it."},{"cn":"他把黑影往地面壓去。","en":"He pressed the shadow down into the ground."},{"cn":"不是吞下，而是讓它失去依附。","en":"Not swallowing it, but stripping it of anything to cling to."},{"cn":"黑影掙扎了一會兒，終於散成薄霧，像被拆解的謠言。","en":"The shadow struggled a while, and at last scattered into thin mist, like a rumor taken apart."},{"cn":"碧吉跌坐在地，大口喘氣。","en":"Aokichi sat down hard on the ground, gasping for breath."},{"cn":"「你、你剛才不是說不回應嗎？」他結巴地問。","en":"\"You — didn't you just say you weren't going to answer?\" he stammered."},{"cn":"玄鬼低聲說：","en":"Genki said quietly:"},{"cn":"「我沒有替他們承擔。」","en":"\"I did not bear it for them.\""},{"cn":"他只是沒有讓它成形。","en":"He had only kept it from taking shape."},{"cn":"碧吉一時分不清差別。","en":"Aokichi could not, for the moment, tell the difference."},{"cn":"在他眼裡，那兩者很像。","en":"To him, the two seemed nearly the same."},{"cn":"可在玄鬼心裡，卻有一道細得幾乎看不見的界線。","en":"But in Genki's heart, there was a line, fine almost past seeing."},{"cn":"承擔，是把惡吸進自己身上。","en":"To bear is to draw evil into oneself."},{"cn":"阻止，是讓惡失去形狀。","en":"To stop is to strip evil of its shape."},{"cn":"前者會讓鬼更重。","en":"The former makes the oni heavier."},{"cn":"後者會讓人更慌。","en":"The latter makes people more afraid."},{"cn":"屋脊上，白蓮的眼神變得更深。","en":"On the roof ridge, Byakuren's gaze deepened."},{"cn":"她看懂了。","en":"She understood."},{"cn":"玄鬼不是要做善。","en":"Genki was not trying to do good."},{"cn":"他只是拒絕成為「出口」。","en":"He was only refusing to be an \"outlet.\""},{"cn":"這比做善更危險。","en":"This was more dangerous than doing good."},{"cn":"因為當人找不到出口，他們會開始懷疑——","en":"Because when people can find no outlet, they begin to wonder —"},{"cn":"問題是否出在自己身上。","en":"whether the trouble lies in themselves."},{"cn":"白蓮的唇角微微動了一下。","en":"The corner of Byakuren's lips moved, faintly."},{"cn":"「很好。」她低聲說。","en":"\"Good,\" she said quietly."},{"cn":"「那我們試試看，你能承受多久。」","en":"\"Then let us see how long you can bear it.\""},{"cn":"巷子深處，黑暗再度晃動。","en":"Deep in the alley, the darkness stirred again."},{"cn":"這一次，不是無形之物。","en":"This time, it was not a formless thing."},{"cn":"一雙細長的眼睛在夜裡睜開。","en":"A pair of slender eyes opened in the night."},{"cn":"尾巴輕輕掃過瓦片，發出柔軟卻冰冷的聲響。","en":"A tail swept lightly over the roof tiles, making a sound soft yet cold."},{"cn":"黑縁。","en":"Kuroberi."},{"cn":"她一直在看。","en":"She had been watching all along."},{"cn":"她比碧吉更早出現，只是沒有露面。","en":"She had appeared even before Aokichi, only without showing herself."},{"cn":"她習慣躲在夜裡，看人如何遺忘，如何丟棄，如何把責任交給「怪物」。","en":"She liked to hide in the night, watching how people forgot, how they discarded, how they handed their guilt over to \"monsters.\""},{"cn":"她舔了舔爪子，語氣帶著若有若無的嘲諷。","en":"She licked her claw, her tone carrying a faint mockery."},{"cn":"「不回應……？」","en":"\"Not answering…?\""},{"cn":"她低聲笑。","en":"She laughed under her breath."},{"cn":"「你以為不回應，就不會被拋棄嗎？」","en":"\"Do you think that if you don't answer, you won't be abandoned?\""},{"cn":"她跳下屋簷，落地無聲。","en":"She dropped from the eaves, landing without a sound."},{"cn":"「鬼大人。」她聲音柔軟，卻帶刺。","en":"\"Lord Oni.\" Her voice was soft, but it carried a barb."},{"cn":"「被留下的滋味……很不好受吧？」","en":"\"The taste of being left behind… isn't pleasant, is it?\""},{"cn":"玄鬼沒有回頭。","en":"Genki did not turn."},{"cn":"黑縁慢慢走近，尾巴在地上拖出一道細影。","en":"Kuroberi walked slowly closer, her tail dragging a thin shadow along the ground."},{"cn":"「我知道那種感覺。」她說。","en":"\"I know that feeling,\" she said."},{"cn":"「你為人付出，為人承擔，最後人卻說——","en":"\"You give yourself for people, you bear things for people, and in the end people only say —"},{"cn":"這本來就是你的樣子。」","en":"this was your nature all along.\""},{"cn":"她停在玄鬼身側，眼睛半瞇。","en":"She stopped at Genki's side, her eyes half-lidded."},{"cn":"「你現在才開始嚐到而已。」","en":"\"You're only just beginning to taste it.\""},{"cn":"碧吉緊張地看著兩人，空氣像拉緊的弦。","en":"Aokichi watched the two of them nervously, the air taut as a drawn string."},{"cn":"白蓮在高處輕輕垂下目光。","en":"Above, Byakuren lowered her eyes slightly."},{"cn":"第二個留下來的出現了。","en":"The second one to remain had appeared."},{"cn":"不是因為理想。","en":"Not out of ideals."},{"cn":"而是因為共鳴。","en":"But out of resonance."},{"cn":"而留下來的人越多，夜行的規律就越容易出現裂縫。","en":"And the more who remained, the more easily the Parade's law would crack."},{"cn":"江戶的夜還沒有結束。","en":"Edo's night was not yet over."},{"cn":"恐懼仍在城中流動，尋找形體。","en":"Fear still moved through the city, searching for a shape."},{"cn":"玄鬼站在兩個妖怪之間，忽然明白一件事：","en":"Genki stood between the two yokai, and suddenly understood one thing:"},{"cn":"停止回應的第一夜，","en":"the first night of refusing to answer"},{"cn":"不是解脫。","en":"was not release."},{"cn":"是開始。","en":"It was a beginning."},{"cn":"（第二章完）","en":"(End of Chapter 2)"},{"cn":"第一部｜百鬼夜行","en":"Part One — The Night Parade"}]},{"id":"ch03","n":3,"title_cn":"第三章｜觀察者的條件","title_en":"Chapter 3 — The Observer's Terms","lines":[{"cn":"夜更深了。","en":"The night grew deeper."},{"cn":"江戶的屋瓦在月光下泛著冷色，像一片無聲的海。","en":"Edo's roof tiles gleamed cold under the moonlight, like a silent sea."},{"cn":"河水仍流，風仍動，可整座城像被壓低了一寸——不是重量，而是某種期待被打斷後的懸空。","en":"The river still flowed, the wind still moved, yet the whole city seemed pressed down an inch — not with weight, but with the suspension left after some expectation was broken."},{"cn":"玄鬼站在街口。","en":"Genki stood at the street corner."},{"cn":"黑縁坐在牆頭，尾巴垂下，輕輕左右晃動。","en":"Kuroberi sat on the wall, her tail hanging down, swaying gently side to side."},{"cn":"碧吉抱著膝蓋坐在石階上，皿裡的水終於平穩，卻仍時不時看向四周，像怕黑暗裡再長出什麼。","en":"Aokichi sat on the stone steps hugging his knees, the water in his dish finally calm, though he still glanced around now and again, as if afraid something else might grow out of the dark."},{"cn":"白蓮從屋脊上緩緩落下。","en":"Byakuren descended slowly from the roof ridge."},{"cn":"她沒有跳。","en":"She did not leap."},{"cn":"她只是往前一步，月光便替她鋪出一條看不見的階梯。","en":"She only stepped forward, and the moonlight laid out an unseen stair for her."},{"cn":"落地時，她的木屐沒有聲音。","en":"When she landed, her wooden sandals made no sound."},{"cn":"玄鬼看向她。","en":"Genki looked at her."},{"cn":"這是他們第一次在夜行之外的對視。","en":"This was their first time facing each other outside the Parade."},{"cn":"「你在觀察。」玄鬼說。","en":"\"You've been observing,\" Genki said."},{"cn":"白蓮輕輕一笑。","en":"Byakuren smiled faintly."},{"cn":"「觀察，是我唯一不會被奪走的權利。」","en":"\"Observing is the one right that cannot be taken from me.\""},{"cn":"她的聲音很輕，卻清晰得像寒夜裡的一口水。","en":"Her voice was soft, yet clear as a mouthful of water on a cold night."},{"cn":"不像碧吉那樣急，也不像黑縁那樣帶刺。","en":"Not urgent like Aokichi, nor barbed like Kuroberi."},{"cn":"她看著玄鬼，目光平穩。","en":"She looked at Genki, her gaze steady."},{"cn":"「你今晚做了兩件事。」她說。","en":"\"You did two things tonight,\" she said."},{"cn":"「第一，你停下來。」","en":"\"First, you stopped.\""},{"cn":"「第二，你拒絕承擔。」","en":"\"Second, you refused to bear it.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼沒有否認。","en":"Genki did not deny it."},{"cn":"白蓮繼續道：","en":"Byakuren went on:"},{"cn":"「你以為這是善嗎？」","en":"\"Do you think that was good?\""},{"cn":"玄鬼沉默了一會兒。","en":"Genki was silent a moment."},{"cn":"「不是。」","en":"\"No.\""},{"cn":"他從來沒有想過「善」。","en":"He had never once thought in terms of \"good.\""},{"cn":"他只是不想再做某件事。","en":"He had only not wanted to do a certain thing any longer."},{"cn":"白蓮點頭。","en":"Byakuren nodded."},{"cn":"「很好。」她說。","en":"\"Good,\" she said."},{"cn":"「如果你是為了善，這條路走不了多久。」","en":"\"If you were doing this for the sake of good, this road would not last you long.\""},{"cn":"黑縁輕哼一聲。","en":"Kuroberi gave a short snort."},{"cn":"「那他是為了什麼？為了清高？」","en":"\"Then what is he doing it for? To seem noble?\""},{"cn":"碧吉縮了縮脖子，覺得氣氛比剛才那團黑影還壓迫。","en":"Aokichi drew his neck in, feeling the air more oppressive now than it had been around that black shadow."},{"cn":"白蓮沒有理會黑縁的嘲諷。","en":"Byakuren paid Kuroberi's mockery no mind."},{"cn":"她往前走了一步，與玄鬼之間的距離縮短。","en":"She took a step forward, closing the distance to Genki."},{"cn":"「停止回應，並不是修行。」她說。","en":"\"To stop answering is not the Practice,\" she said."},{"cn":"「那只是拒絕。」","en":"\"That is only refusal.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼的眼神微微動了一下。","en":"Something shifted, faintly, in Genki's eyes."},{"cn":"「修行是什麼？」他問。","en":"\"What is the Practice?\" he asked."},{"cn":"這是他第一次主動問。","en":"It was the first time he had asked a question on his own."},{"cn":"白蓮沒有立即回答。","en":"Byakuren did not answer at once."},{"cn":"她抬頭看向夜空。","en":"She looked up at the night sky."},{"cn":"江戶上方的星星被薄雲遮住，只有幾點微光從縫隙裡漏出。","en":"Above Edo the stars were veiled in thin cloud, only a few points of dim light leaking through the gaps."},{"cn":"她指向那微光。","en":"She pointed toward that faint light."},{"cn":"「修行，是讓自己在不被需要的時候，仍然存在。」","en":"\"The Practice is to go on existing, even when you are not needed.\""},{"cn":"碧吉皺起眉。","en":"Aokichi frowned."},{"cn":"「什麼意思？」","en":"\"What does that mean?\""},{"cn":"白蓮轉向他。","en":"Byakuren turned to him."},{"cn":"「你存在，是因為人類把你當笑話。」","en":"\"You exist, because humans treat you as a joke.\""},{"cn":"「她存在，是因為人類記得被拋棄的痛。」她看了黑縁一眼。","en":"\"She exists, because humans remember the pain of being abandoned.\" She glanced at Kuroberi."},{"cn":"「而他存在——」","en":"\"And he —\""},{"cn":"她看向玄鬼。","en":"She looked toward Genki."},{"cn":"「是因為人類需要一個可以怪罪的容器。」","en":"\"He exists because humans need a vessel to blame.\""},{"cn":"她的聲音沒有情緒，卻準確得像刀。","en":"Her voice carried no emotion, yet it was as precise as a blade."},{"cn":"「如果明日開始，人類不再怪罪鬼，你還剩下什麼？」","en":"\"If, from tomorrow, humans no longer blamed the oni, what would be left of you?\""},{"cn":"空氣靜了。","en":"The air went still."},{"cn":"這個問題不只是問玄鬼。","en":"This question was not for Genki alone."},{"cn":"也是問在場的每一個。","en":"It was for everyone present."},{"cn":"黑縁的尾巴停住。","en":"Kuroberi's tail stopped moving."},{"cn":"碧吉下意識摸了摸自己的皿。","en":"Aokichi touched his own dish without thinking."},{"cn":"玄鬼的肩微微繃緊。","en":"Genki's shoulders tensed, faintly."},{"cn":"「我不知道。」玄鬼說。","en":"\"I don't know,\" Genki said."},{"cn":"這句話說出口時，他感到某種奇怪的輕。","en":"As the words left him, he felt a strange lightness."},{"cn":"他從未允許自己不知道。","en":"He had never once let himself not know."},{"cn":"白蓮點頭。","en":"Byakuren nodded."},{"cn":"「那就從這裡開始。」","en":"\"Then that is where we begin.\""},{"cn":"她轉身，走向街道中央。","en":"She turned and walked toward the center of the street."},{"cn":"「如果你只是停止，世界會自行修正。」","en":"\"If you only stop, the world will correct itself.\""},{"cn":"「它會創造新的怪物。」","en":"\"It will create new monsters.\""},{"cn":"「新的鬼。」","en":"\"New oni.\""},{"cn":"「新的更醜的臉。」","en":"\"New, uglier faces.\""},{"cn":"遠處，日本橋方向傳來一聲輕微的騷動。","en":"Far off, toward Nihonbashi, came the faint sound of a disturbance."},{"cn":"不是妖怪的聲音。","en":"It was not the sound of a yokai."},{"cn":"是人。","en":"It was human."},{"cn":"黑縁耳朵一動。","en":"Kuroberi's ear twitched."},{"cn":"「有人出來了。」","en":"\"Someone's come out.\""},{"cn":"白蓮沒有回頭。","en":"Byakuren did not turn."},{"cn":"「看吧。」她輕聲說。","en":"\"You see,\" she said softly."},{"cn":"街尾，幾個男人舉著燈籠走出屋門。","en":"At the end of the street, several men came out of their houses carrying lanterns."},{"cn":"他們原本只是因為睡不安穩。","en":"They had come out only because they could not sleep easy."},{"cn":"可當恐懼滯留，睡不安穩會變成行動。","en":"But once fear lingers, unease turns to action."},{"cn":"「剛才那是什麼？」","en":"\"What was that, just now?\""},{"cn":"「一定是鬼走過。」","en":"\"It must have been an oni passing.\""},{"cn":"「我說最近怪事多，都是因為那群妖怪！」","en":"\"I said there've been too many strange things lately — it's all because of those yokai!\""},{"cn":"新之助也在其中。","en":"Shinnosuke was among them."},{"cn":"他手裡提著燈，眼下發青。","en":"He carried a lantern in his hand, dark circles under his eyes."},{"cn":"牆角那團黑影雖已散去，可他的心仍懸著。","en":"The black shadow in the corner had already scattered, yet his heart still hung uneasy."},{"cn":"「我們不能等。」其中一人說。","en":"\"We can't just wait,\" one of them said."},{"cn":"「要找陰陽師，或是——」","en":"\"We should find an onmyōji, or —\""},{"cn":"他沒說完。","en":"He did not finish."},{"cn":"但眾人都知道那個未說出的詞。","en":"But everyone knew the word he had not said."},{"cn":"「把鬼趕走。」","en":"\"Drive the oni out.\""},{"cn":"他們的恐懼開始有方向。","en":"Their fear had begun to find a direction."},{"cn":"方向，需要目標。","en":"A direction needs a target."},{"cn":"白蓮看著這一幕，低聲道：","en":"Byakuren watched this unfold and said quietly:"},{"cn":"「修行的第一條。」","en":"\"The First Precept.\""},{"cn":"她轉向玄鬼。","en":"She turned to Genki."},{"cn":"「不為他們證明自己。」","en":"\"Do not act to prove yourself.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼看著那些提燈的人。","en":"Genki looked at the men with their lanterns."},{"cn":"他可以輕易讓他們跪下。","en":"He could easily bring them to their knees."},{"cn":"可以讓他們看見真正的恐怖，讓他們後悔今晚的念頭。","en":"He could show them true terror, make them regret tonight's thought."},{"cn":"可那樣只會讓怪談更多。","en":"But that would only breed more ghost stories."},{"cn":"他沒有動。","en":"He did not move."},{"cn":"黑縁瞇起眼。","en":"Kuroberi narrowed her eyes."},{"cn":"「你打算什麼都不做？」","en":"\"You mean to do nothing at all?\""},{"cn":"玄鬼沉聲說：","en":"Genki said in a low voice:"},{"cn":"「他們沒有看見我。」","en":"\"They have not seen me.\""},{"cn":"只有恐懼者能見夜行。","en":"Only those who feared could see the Parade."},{"cn":"而這些人現在還只是半信半疑。","en":"And these men were, for now, still only half convinced."},{"cn":"只要他不給形體，他們就只能怪彼此。","en":"So long as he gave it no shape, they could only blame each other."},{"cn":"白蓮的嘴角微不可察地動了一下。","en":"The corner of Byakuren's mouth moved, almost imperceptibly."},{"cn":"第一條，他過了。","en":"The first precept — he had passed it."},{"cn":"但修行從來不只一條。","en":"But the Practice was never only one precept."},{"cn":"忽然，一陣風從上方壓下。","en":"Suddenly, a gust of wind pressed down from above."},{"cn":"不是夜風。","en":"Not a night wind."},{"cn":"是帶著重量的氣流。","en":"A current of air carrying weight."},{"cn":"碧吉猛地抬頭。","en":"Aokichi's head jerked up."},{"cn":"屋瓦之上，兩道影子站立。","en":"Above the roof tiles, two shadows stood."},{"cn":"一高一矮。","en":"One tall, one short."},{"cn":"羽翼般的披風在夜色中展開，卻沒有真正的翅膀。","en":"Wing-like cloaks spread in the night air, though they were not true wings."},{"cn":"鞍馬烏嶽－天狗。","en":"Kurama Ugaku — the tengu."},{"cn":"他的眼神冷得像冬日的石階。","en":"His eyes were cold as a winter stone step."},{"cn":"他看向玄鬼時，不帶敵意，也不帶善意。","en":"When he looked at Genki, he carried neither hostility nor goodwill."},{"cn":"只有審視。","en":"Only scrutiny."},{"cn":"「夜行出現裂縫。」他開口。","en":"\"The Parade has developed a crack,\" he said."},{"cn":"聲音不大，卻清晰地落在每個人耳邊。","en":"His voice was not loud, yet it landed clearly on every ear."},{"cn":"「原因是你。」","en":"\"The cause is you.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼沒有辯解。","en":"Genki offered no defense."},{"cn":"烏嶽的目光掃過碧吉與黑縁。","en":"Ugaku's gaze swept over Aokichi and Kuroberi."},{"cn":"「你們選擇留下？」","en":"\"You two have chosen to remain?\""},{"cn":"黑縁冷笑。","en":"Kuroberi gave a cold laugh."},{"cn":"「誰規定不能？」","en":"\"Who says we can't?\""},{"cn":"烏嶽的目光轉向白蓮。","en":"Ugaku's gaze turned to Byakuren."},{"cn":"「這是你的安排？」","en":"\"Is this your arrangement?\""},{"cn":"白蓮輕輕搖頭。","en":"Byakuren shook her head lightly."},{"cn":"「只是觀察。」","en":"\"Only observation.\""},{"cn":"烏嶽沉默片刻。","en":"Ugaku was silent a moment."},{"cn":"然後他看向玄鬼。","en":"Then he looked to Genki."},{"cn":"「你停下來，並非為了更高的秩序。」","en":"\"You did not stop for the sake of some higher order.\""},{"cn":"「也非為了覺悟。」","en":"\"Nor for the sake of enlightenment.\""},{"cn":"「只是因為厭倦。」","en":"\"Only out of weariness.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼抬眼。","en":"Genki raised his eyes."},{"cn":"「是。」","en":"\"Yes.\""},{"cn":"這回答坦白得近乎無禮。","en":"The answer was blunt to the point of rudeness."},{"cn":"烏嶽眼神微動。","en":"Something moved, faintly, in Ugaku's eyes."},{"cn":"「厭倦，不足以支撐修行。」","en":"\"Weariness is not enough to sustain the Practice.\""},{"cn":"風壓更重了一點。","en":"The pressure of the wind grew heavier still."},{"cn":"碧吉覺得自己快要被壓扁。","en":"Aokichi felt he might be crushed flat."},{"cn":"黑縁的尾巴微微炸起。","en":"Kuroberi's tail bristled slightly."},{"cn":"烏嶽繼續道：","en":"Ugaku continued:"},{"cn":"「夜行不是你一個人的負擔。」","en":"\"The Parade is not your burden alone.\""},{"cn":"「你若不走在前面，便由他物填補。」","en":"\"If you do not walk at its head, something else will fill the place.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼低聲說：","en":"Genki said quietly:"},{"cn":"「那就讓它們填。」","en":"\"Then let it fill.\""},{"cn":"這句話落下，連白蓮都微微側目。","en":"At those words, even Byakuren glanced aside, faintly."},{"cn":"這不是叛逆。","en":"This was not defiance."},{"cn":"這是某種更深的決絕。","en":"It was some deeper resolve."},{"cn":"烏嶽的眼神第一次帶上明顯的鋒利。","en":"For the first time, a clear edge showed in Ugaku's eyes."},{"cn":"「你若不走，秩序會崩。」","en":"\"If you do not walk, the order will collapse.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼看著他。","en":"Genki looked at him."},{"cn":"「那就讓它崩。」","en":"\"Then let it collapse.\""},{"cn":"夜色在這句話之後沉了一瞬。","en":"The night seemed to sink for an instant, after those words."},{"cn":"烏嶽沒有立刻動手。","en":"Ugaku did not move to strike at once."},{"cn":"他只是長久地看著玄鬼。","en":"He only looked at Genki for a long while."},{"cn":"然後說了一句：","en":"Then he said one thing:"},{"cn":"「那就證明。」","en":"\"Then prove it.\""},{"cn":"說完，他轉身，身影如風般消失在屋瓦之上。","en":"With that, he turned, and his shape vanished over the tiles like wind."},{"cn":"壓迫感隨之散去。","en":"The pressure eased with him."},{"cn":"碧吉跌坐在地，大口喘氣。","en":"Aokichi sank to the ground, gasping for breath."},{"cn":"黑縁低聲說：","en":"Kuroberi said quietly:"},{"cn":"「他不會就此罷休。」","en":"\"He won't leave it at that.\""},{"cn":"白蓮輕聲道：","en":"Byakuren said softly:"},{"cn":"「很好。」","en":"\"Good.\""},{"cn":"她看向玄鬼。","en":"She looked to Genki."},{"cn":"「第二條修行。」","en":"\"The Second Precept.\""},{"cn":"「承受質疑，而不反擊。」","en":"\"Bear doubt without striking back.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼沒有說話。","en":"Genki said nothing."},{"cn":"他只是看著遠處提燈的人群逐漸散去，看著夜色慢慢回到表面的平靜。","en":"He only watched the men with their lanterns slowly disperse in the distance, watched the night settle slowly back into its surface calm."},{"cn":"可他知道——","en":"But he knew —"},{"cn":"裂縫已經存在。","en":"the crack already existed."},{"cn":"而裂縫一旦出現，就不會自己消失。","en":"And once a crack appears, it does not close on its own."},{"cn":"白蓮轉身，走向更深的夜。","en":"Byakuren turned and walked toward the deeper night."},{"cn":"「從今夜開始。」她說。","en":"\"From tonight,\" she said."},{"cn":"「這不是夜行。」","en":"\"This is not the Night Parade.\""},{"cn":"「這是修行。」","en":"\"This is the Practice.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼站在原地。","en":"Genki stood where he was."},{"cn":"他忽然意識到——","en":"He suddenly understood —"},{"cn":"真正的重，不是恐懼。","en":"the true weight was not fear."},{"cn":"而是選擇。","en":"It was choice."},{"cn":"（第三章完）","en":"(End of Chapter 3)"},{"cn":"第一部｜百鬼夜行","en":"Part One — The Night Parade"}]},{"id":"ch04","n":4,"title_cn":"第四章｜留下的理由","title_en":"Chapter 4 — Reasons to Stay","lines":[{"cn":"夜色褪去時，江戶看起來什麼都沒發生。","en":"When the night colors faded, Edo looked as though nothing had happened."},{"cn":"早市照常開張。","en":"The morning market opened as usual."},{"cn":"魚販的吆喝穿過巷口，蒸籠的熱氣在空氣裡浮起。","en":"Fishmongers' cries carried through the alley mouths, steam rising from the rice-steamers into the air."},{"cn":"孩子背著小木箱跑過橋，鞋底啪嗒作響。","en":"Children ran across the bridge with little wooden boxes on their backs, sandals clattering."},{"cn":"恐懼像被壓回地底。","en":"Fear had been pressed back beneath the ground."},{"cn":"表面恢復了秩序。","en":"The surface had returned to order."},{"cn":"但玄鬼知道，那只是暫時。","en":"But Genki knew it was only temporary."},{"cn":"他站在河邊，看著水面倒映的天空。","en":"He stood by the river, watching the sky reflected on the water's face."},{"cn":"白日裡，他比夜裡更顯得突兀——高大、沉重、不屬於人群。","en":"By day he stood out more than at night — tall, heavy, not belonging to the crowd."},{"cn":"只有真正恐懼的人，才能看見夜行。","en":"Only those who truly feared could see the Night Parade."},{"cn":"白日裡，恐懼被工作與日常壓住，玄鬼幾乎成了透明。","en":"By day, fear was pinned down by work and routine, and Genki became almost transparent."},{"cn":"碧吉卻沒有透明。","en":"Aokichi was not transparent."},{"cn":"他一整晚沒回河裡。","en":"He had not gone back to the river all night."},{"cn":"這是第一個代價。","en":"This was the first cost."},{"cn":"碧吉離水太久，皿裡的水會慢慢乾涸。","en":"When a kappa stays too long from water, the water in his dish slowly dries."},{"cn":"不是立刻死去，而是一種緩慢的失衡。","en":"Not sudden death, but a slow unbalancing."},{"cn":"碧吉蹲在橋下陰影裡，用手舀河水往皿裡補。","en":"Aokichi crouched in the shadow beneath the bridge, scooping river water with his hands to refill his dish."},{"cn":"「你不走嗎？」他問玄鬼。","en":"\"Aren't you leaving?\" he asked Genki."},{"cn":"玄鬼沒有回答。","en":"Genki did not answer."},{"cn":"碧吉苦笑了一下。","en":"Aokichi gave a bitter laugh."},{"cn":"「其實我也不知道為什麼留下來。」他說。","en":"\"Truth is, I don't know why I stayed either,\" he said."},{"cn":"「可能是……」","en":"\"Maybe…\""},{"cn":"他想了很久。","en":"He thought for a long while."},{"cn":"「可能是因為你停下來的樣子，很像我以前想做卻不敢做的事。」","en":"\"Maybe it's because the way you stopped looked a lot like something I used to want to do, but never dared.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼看向他。","en":"Genki looked toward him."},{"cn":"碧吉把濕手抹在衣服上，語氣變得輕快一點，像想把沉重推開。","en":"Aokichi wiped his wet hands on his clothes, his tone turning a little lighter, as if trying to push the heaviness away."},{"cn":"「你知道嗎？我們河童常被抓去當笑話。」","en":"\"You know, we kappa are often made into jokes.\""},{"cn":"「孩子們會拿我們嚇彼此，大人會說我們偷瓜、拉人下水。」","en":"\"Children use us to scare each other, grown-ups say we steal melons, pull people into the water.\""},{"cn":"「有時候，我真的會去偷瓜。」","en":"\"Sometimes, I really do steal melons.\""},{"cn":"他笑了。","en":"He laughed."},{"cn":"「因為那樣比較省事。」","en":"\"Because it's easier that way.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼明白。","en":"Genki understood."},{"cn":"當世界已經替你決定了樣子，","en":"When the world has already decided what shape you are,"},{"cn":"扮演那個樣子，比反抗輕鬆。","en":"playing that shape is easier than resisting it."},{"cn":"碧吉低頭看著水面。","en":"Aokichi looked down at the water."},{"cn":"「但有一次，有個小孩掉進河裡。」","en":"\"But once, a child fell into the river.\""},{"cn":"「我把他推回岸上。」","en":"\"I pushed him back up onto the bank.\""},{"cn":"他停了一下。","en":"He paused."},{"cn":"「第二天，全城都在傳——是碧吉拉人下水。」","en":"\"The next day, the whole town was saying — Aokichi pulled someone into the water.\""},{"cn":"他笑得有點難看。","en":"His laugh turned ugly."},{"cn":"「你說，我還要不要繼續做好事？」","en":"\"So tell me, should I keep doing good?\""},{"cn":"風從橋洞吹進來，帶著潮氣。","en":"Wind blew in through the arch of the bridge, carrying damp air."},{"cn":"玄鬼終於開口。","en":"Genki finally spoke."},{"cn":"「你留下來，是因為你厭倦被定義。」","en":"\"You stayed because you're tired of being defined.\""},{"cn":"碧吉抬頭。","en":"Aokichi looked up."},{"cn":"「那你呢？」","en":"\"And you?\""},{"cn":"玄鬼沉默。","en":"Genki was silent."},{"cn":"「我厭倦定義別人。」","en":"\"I'm tired of defining others.\""},{"cn":"兩句話落下，河水輕響。","en":"The two lines fell, and the river water rippled softly."},{"cn":"那不是誓言。","en":"It was not a vow."},{"cn":"只是兩個被貼上標籤的存在，在白日裡說出一句實話。","en":"Only two labeled beings, speaking one true thing in the daylight."},{"cn":"午後，天氣轉陰。","en":"In the afternoon, the sky turned overcast."},{"cn":"日本橋附近開始流傳新的說法。","en":"Near Nihonbashi, a new rumor began to spread."},{"cn":"「昨夜鬼沒有走。」","en":"\"The oni didn't leave last night.\""},{"cn":"「恐懼滯留，是凶兆。」","en":"\"Fear lingering — that's an ill omen.\""},{"cn":"「一定是水邊有不乾淨的東西。」","en":"\"There must be something unclean by the water.\""},{"cn":"人類找出口的速度，比妖怪想像的還快。","en":"Humans found their outlets faster than any yokai could imagine."},{"cn":"到了傍晚，有人提議——","en":"By evening, someone proposed —"},{"cn":"「把碧吉趕走。」","en":"\"Drive Aokichi out.\""},{"cn":"碧吉第一次真正感到寒意。","en":"For the first time, Aokichi truly felt a chill."},{"cn":"夜裡被恐懼指名是一回事。","en":"Being named by fear at night was one thing."},{"cn":"白日裡被理性指名，是另一回事。","en":"Being named by reason in daylight was another."},{"cn":"「他們找的是我。」碧吉低聲說。","en":"\"They're after me,\" Aokichi said quietly."},{"cn":"玄鬼站起身。","en":"Genki rose to his feet."},{"cn":"遠處橋頭聚了幾個男人，手裡拿著網與棍。","en":"In the distance, several men had gathered at the bridgehead, holding nets and clubs."},{"cn":"不是為了捕魚。","en":"Not for fishing."},{"cn":"碧吉往後退了一步。","en":"Aokichi stepped back."},{"cn":"「你說過，不回應。」他提醒。","en":"\"You said — do not answer,\" he reminded him."},{"cn":"玄鬼看著那些人。","en":"Genki looked at the men."},{"cn":"他沒有走向他們。","en":"He did not walk toward them."},{"cn":"他只是站在橋前。","en":"He only stood before the bridge."},{"cn":"當人群靠近時，他們看不見玄鬼。","en":"As the crowd drew near, they could not see Genki."},{"cn":"因為他們現在還沒有真正的恐懼——","en":"Because they did not yet carry true fear —"},{"cn":"只有憤怒與自我保護。","en":"only anger and self-protection."},{"cn":"但當他們看向橋下時，恐懼浮起。","en":"But when they looked beneath the bridge, fear rose up."},{"cn":"碧吉縮在陰影裡，皿裡的水晃動得厲害。","en":"Aokichi shrank into the shadows, the water in his dish shaking hard."},{"cn":"一個男人忽然停下腳步。","en":"One man suddenly stopped walking."},{"cn":"他心裡閃過昨夜聽到的聲音、牆角的影子、版畫上的鬼臉。","en":"Through his mind flashed the sounds he had heard the night before, the shadow at the wall's corner, the oni face on a woodblock print."},{"cn":"恐懼從憤怒裡浮出來。","en":"Fear rose up out of anger."},{"cn":"他看見了。","en":"He saw."},{"cn":"玄鬼站在橋前。","en":"Genki stood before the bridge."},{"cn":"高大、沉默、不可忽視。","en":"Tall, silent, impossible to ignore."},{"cn":"男人的呼吸一滯。","en":"The man's breath caught."},{"cn":"「……鬼。」","en":"\"…An oni.\""},{"cn":"其他人順著他的視線看去。","en":"The others followed his gaze."},{"cn":"有人看見，有人看不見。","en":"Some saw, some did not."},{"cn":"看見的人後退一步。","en":"Those who saw stepped back."},{"cn":"看不見的人困惑。","en":"Those who could not see were confused."},{"cn":"這就是恐懼的門檻。","en":"This was the threshold of fear."},{"cn":"玄鬼沒有動手。","en":"Genki did not raise a hand."},{"cn":"他只是站著。","en":"He only stood."},{"cn":"站在碧吉與人群之間。","en":"Standing between Aokichi and the crowd."},{"cn":"不是威嚇。","en":"Not a threat."},{"cn":"不是攻擊。","en":"Not an attack."},{"cn":"只是存在。","en":"Only presence."},{"cn":"男人們的腳步亂了。","en":"The men's footing broke into disorder."},{"cn":"不是被打退，而是被自己心裡浮起的恐懼絆住。","en":"Not driven back by force, but tripped by the fear rising in their own hearts."},{"cn":"最後，他們退開了。","en":"In the end, they retreated."},{"cn":"不是因為善。","en":"Not out of goodness."},{"cn":"而是因為不敢。","en":"But out of not daring."},{"cn":"碧吉長長吐出一口氣，膝蓋發軟。","en":"Aokichi let out a long breath, his knees going weak."},{"cn":"「你剛才……」","en":"\"Just now, you…\""},{"cn":"「我沒有替你承擔。」玄鬼說。","en":"\"I did not bear it for you,\" Genki said."},{"cn":"碧吉愣住。","en":"Aokichi froze."},{"cn":"玄鬼繼續道：","en":"Genki went on:"},{"cn":"「他們退開，是因為他們看見自己怕。」","en":"\"They retreated because they saw their own fear.\""},{"cn":"碧吉慢慢理解。","en":"Aokichi slowly understood."},{"cn":"玄鬼沒有吞下那份恐懼。","en":"Genki had not swallowed that fear."},{"cn":"沒有把怒氣吸進自己身上。","en":"Had not drawn the anger into himself."},{"cn":"他只是讓恐懼顯形。","en":"He had only let the fear take visible shape."},{"cn":"那需要更大的力量。","en":"That required a greater strength."},{"cn":"不是外在的。","en":"Not an outward one."},{"cn":"是內在的。","en":"An inward one."},{"cn":"屋脊之上，白蓮靜靜看著。","en":"Above on the roof ridge, Byakuren watched quietly."},{"cn":"她的眼神少了些試探，多了些衡量。","en":"Her gaze held less testing now, more weighing."},{"cn":"第一條：不為證明而動。","en":"The First Precept: Do not act to prove yourself."},{"cn":"第二條：承受質疑。","en":"The Second Precept: Bear doubt."},{"cn":"第三條：不為他人背負。","en":"The Third Precept: Do not carry what belongs to others."},{"cn":"玄鬼過了。","en":"Genki had passed."},{"cn":"但修行還遠遠不夠。","en":"But the Practice was still far from complete."},{"cn":"黑縁坐在另一側屋瓦，尾巴輕輕拍打。","en":"Kuroberi sat on the tiles of the other eave, tail tapping lightly."},{"cn":"「你救了他。」她說。","en":"\"You saved him,\" she said."},{"cn":"玄鬼搖頭。","en":"Genki shook his head."},{"cn":"「我只是沒有讓他成為出口。」","en":"\"I only kept him from becoming an outlet.\""},{"cn":"黑縁沉默了一會兒。","en":"Kuroberi was silent a moment."},{"cn":"然後輕聲說：","en":"Then she said softly:"},{"cn":"「那你呢？」","en":"\"And you?\""},{"cn":"這句話落下，空氣又冷了一寸。","en":"The words fell, and the air grew an inch colder."},{"cn":"如果有一天，所有人都停止把惡塞給鬼，","en":"If, one day, everyone stopped stuffing evil into the oni,"},{"cn":"鬼會成為什麼？","en":"what would the oni become?"},{"cn":"玄鬼望向河面。","en":"Genki looked out at the river's surface."},{"cn":"水面平靜。","en":"The water was calm."},{"cn":"倒映出天空，也倒映出他。","en":"It reflected the sky, and it reflected him."},{"cn":"可那倒影，沒有角。","en":"But that reflection had no horns."},{"cn":"沒有紅色。","en":"No red."},{"cn":"只有一個沉重的輪廓。","en":"Only a heavy outline."},{"cn":"他忽然感到一種極細微的空。","en":"He suddenly felt an emptiness, faint and fine."},{"cn":"如果有一天，他不再被需要，","en":"If, one day, he was no longer needed,"},{"cn":"他會走向哪裡？","en":"where would he go?"},{"cn":"白蓮在屋脊上低聲念出那個名字。","en":"On the roof ridge, Byakuren spoke that name in a low voice."},{"cn":"「無垢界。」","en":"\"The Immaculate Realm.\""},{"cn":"碧吉聽不清。","en":"Aokichi could not hear it clearly."},{"cn":"黑縁卻聽見了。","en":"But Kuroberi heard."},{"cn":"「那是什麼？」","en":"\"What is that?\""},{"cn":"白蓮沒有解釋。","en":"Byakuren did not explain."},{"cn":"她只是看著玄鬼。","en":"She only looked at Genki."},{"cn":"而玄鬼第一次，沒有立刻排斥這個詞。","en":"And Genki, for the first time, did not reject the word at once."},{"cn":"夕陽落下。","en":"The sun went down."},{"cn":"夜又將來臨。","en":"Night was coming again."},{"cn":"這一次，留下來的不只一個。","en":"This time, more than one would stay behind."},{"cn":"而百鬼夜行，在遠處蠢動。","en":"And the Night Parade, far off, stirred."},{"cn":"（第四章完）","en":"(End of Chapter 4)"},{"cn":"第一部｜百鬼夜行","en":"Part One — The Night Parade"}]},{"id":"ch05","n":5,"title_cn":"第五章｜不回應的代價","title_en":"Chapter 5 — The Price of Not Answering","lines":[{"cn":"夜再度降臨。","en":"Night fell again."},{"cn":"這一夜，江戶比往常更早熄燈。","en":"This night, Edo put out its lights earlier than usual."},{"cn":"謠言比風更快。","en":"Rumor traveled faster than wind."},{"cn":"「鬼沒有離開。」","en":"\"The oni hasn't left.\""},{"cn":"「河邊不乾淨。」","en":"\"The riverside is unclean.\""},{"cn":"「昨夜的影子還在。」","en":"\"Last night's shadow is still there.\""},{"cn":"人們白日裡退去，夜裡卻補回恐懼。","en":"By day people's fear withdrew, but at night it came flooding back."},{"cn":"恐懼一旦被提起名字，就會自行生長。","en":"Once fear is given a name, it grows on its own."},{"cn":"玄鬼站在橋上。","en":"Genki stood on the bridge."},{"cn":"碧吉縮在橋洞陰影裡。","en":"Aokichi huddled in the shadow of the bridge's arch."},{"cn":"黑縁蹲在屋瓦。","en":"Kuroberi crouched on the roof tiles."},{"cn":"白蓮不見蹤影。","en":"Byakuren was nowhere to be seen."},{"cn":"空氣緊得像繃著的弦。","en":"The air pulled taut as a drawn string."},{"cn":"「今晚不對。」黑縁低聲說。","en":"\"Something's wrong tonight,\" Kuroberi said quietly."},{"cn":"玄鬼早已感覺到。","en":"Genki had already felt it."},{"cn":"夜行還未出現。","en":"The Night Parade had not yet appeared."},{"cn":"但某種更散亂的東西正在城市裡游走——不是整齊的隊伍，而是碎裂的恐懼，各自尋找形體。","en":"But something more scattered was moving through the city — not a tidy column, but shattered fragments of fear, each seeking its own shape."},{"cn":"第一聲尖叫從遠處傳來。","en":"The first scream came from far off."},{"cn":"不是被攻擊。","en":"Not from an attack."},{"cn":"是被自己嚇到。","en":"From someone frightening themselves."},{"cn":"一戶人家屋裡的燈籠翻倒，火焰燒上紙門。","en":"Inside one house a lantern tipped over, flame catching the paper door."},{"cn":"火光扭曲成怪異的形狀。","en":"The firelight twisted into strange shapes."},{"cn":"人群慌亂奔出巷口。","en":"The crowd fled the alley mouth in panic."},{"cn":"恐懼被點燃時，會彼此感染。","en":"Fear, once lit, spreads by contagion."},{"cn":"碧吉探出頭。","en":"Aokichi poked his head out."},{"cn":"「那是我們的人嗎？」","en":"\"Is that one of ours?\""},{"cn":"玄鬼搖頭。","en":"Genki shook his head."},{"cn":"那不是妖怪。","en":"It was not a yokai."},{"cn":"是人類互相傳播的恐慌。","en":"It was human panic, spreading among themselves."},{"cn":"火光映紅半條街。","en":"Firelight lit half the street red."},{"cn":"有人高喊：","en":"Someone shouted:"},{"cn":"「是鬼作祟！」","en":"\"It's the oni's doing!\""},{"cn":"這一句話，比火更危險。","en":"That sentence was more dangerous than the fire."},{"cn":"玄鬼看見黑暗再次凝聚。","en":"Genki saw the darkness gathering again."},{"cn":"不是單一一團，而是數十個細碎的影子，在火光裡搖晃。","en":"Not one single mass, but dozens of small fractured shadows, swaying in the firelight."},{"cn":"如果他不動，它們會自己成形。","en":"If he did not move, they would take shape on their own."},{"cn":"如果他動，他便再次成為出口。","en":"If he moved, he would become an outlet again."},{"cn":"碧吉握緊拳頭。","en":"Aokichi clenched his fists."},{"cn":"「我們怎麼辦？」","en":"\"What do we do?\""},{"cn":"玄鬼沒有回答。","en":"Genki did not answer."},{"cn":"他往前一步。","en":"He stepped forward."},{"cn":"不是走向火。","en":"Not toward the fire."},{"cn":"而是站在人群與黑影之間。","en":"But to stand between the crowd and the dark shadows."},{"cn":"他沒有釋放威壓。","en":"He released no pressure."},{"cn":"沒有顯露鬼形。","en":"He showed no oni shape."},{"cn":"他只是讓恐懼者看見他。","en":"He only let those who feared see him."},{"cn":"第一個看見的是那個點火失手的男人。","en":"The first to see him was the man who had fumbled and lit the fire."},{"cn":"他轉身時，眼睛與玄鬼對上。","en":"As he turned, his eyes met Genki's."},{"cn":"恐懼在那一瞬間凝固。","en":"Fear froze in that instant."},{"cn":"不是因為鬼可怕。","en":"Not because the oni was terrifying."},{"cn":"而是因為——","en":"But because —"},{"cn":"他知道火是自己打翻的。","en":"he knew the fire was his own doing."},{"cn":"他知道。","en":"He knew it."},{"cn":"那份羞愧在胸口擴散，轉化為更猛烈的指責。","en":"That shame spread through his chest, and turned into fiercer accusation."},{"cn":"「是鬼！」他吼。","en":"\"It's the oni!\" he roared."},{"cn":"「鬼在那裡！」","en":"\"The oni's there!\""},{"cn":"更多人看過來。","en":"More people looked over."},{"cn":"看見的人更慌。","en":"Those who saw grew more frightened."},{"cn":"看不見的人更憤怒。","en":"Those who could not see grew more angry."},{"cn":"石頭飛了過來。","en":"A stone flew through the air."},{"cn":"不是砸中玄鬼。","en":"It did not strike Genki."},{"cn":"而是穿過他，落在橋面。","en":"It passed through him and struck the bridge deck."},{"cn":"但碧吉看見了。","en":"But Aokichi saw it."},{"cn":"「他們在攻擊你！」","en":"\"They're attacking you!\""},{"cn":"玄鬼沒有動。","en":"Genki did not move."},{"cn":"第二顆石頭飛來。","en":"A second stone flew."},{"cn":"第三顆。","en":"Then a third."},{"cn":"黑縁的耳朵壓低。","en":"Kuroberi's ears flattened."},{"cn":"「你不反擊？」","en":"\"You won't fight back?\""},{"cn":"玄鬼低聲說：","en":"Genki said quietly:"},{"cn":"「他們還在選擇。」","en":"\"They are still choosing.\""},{"cn":"他們可以選擇停下。","en":"They could choose to stop."},{"cn":"也可以選擇把錯全推給鬼。","en":"Or they could choose to push all the blame onto the oni."},{"cn":"這是一個極細的分界。","en":"This was an exceedingly fine line."},{"cn":"火焰越燒越高。","en":"The flames burned higher."},{"cn":"恐懼變得更濃。","en":"Fear grew thicker."},{"cn":"就在這時——","en":"Just then —"},{"cn":"一個孩子跌倒在火光邊緣。","en":"a child stumbled at the edge of the firelight."},{"cn":"碧吉猛地站起。","en":"Aokichi shot to his feet."},{"cn":"「不行！」","en":"\"No!\""},{"cn":"他忘了規則。","en":"He forgot the rule."},{"cn":"忘了不回應。","en":"Forgot not to answer."},{"cn":"他衝出橋洞。","en":"He rushed out from beneath the bridge."},{"cn":"人群裡有人看見一抹濕綠色影子竄出。","en":"In the crowd, someone saw a streak of wet green dart out."},{"cn":"「碧吉！」","en":"\"Aokichi!\""},{"cn":"棍棒揮下。","en":"A club swung down."},{"cn":"碧吉推開孩子，卻來不及躲開那一下。","en":"Aokichi pushed the child clear, but had no time to dodge the blow himself."},{"cn":"木棍重重砸在他背上。","en":"The club struck hard across his back."},{"cn":"皿裡的水晃出大半。","en":"Most of the water in his dish sloshed out."},{"cn":"碧吉跌在地上，呼吸亂掉。","en":"Aokichi fell to the ground, his breath ragged."},{"cn":"人群更加騷動。","en":"The crowd stirred more violently."},{"cn":"「看！就是牠！」","en":"\"Look! It's him!\""},{"cn":"這一瞬間，恐懼找到了出口。","en":"In that instant, fear found its outlet."},{"cn":"黑暗的碎影迅速往碧吉身上聚。","en":"The dark, fractured shadows converged swiftly onto Aokichi."},{"cn":"玄鬼終於動了。","en":"At last, Genki moved."},{"cn":"他不是攻擊人群。","en":"He did not attack the crowd."},{"cn":"他是走向碧吉。","en":"He walked toward Aokichi."},{"cn":"每一步，都像壓在石頭上。","en":"Each step fell like a weight pressed onto stone."},{"cn":"黑影纏上碧吉的手臂。","en":"The dark shadow wound around Aokichi's arm."},{"cn":"碧吉痛得發抖。","en":"Aokichi trembled with pain."},{"cn":"「我只是……救人……」","en":"\"I was only… saving someone…\""},{"cn":"他的聲音很輕。","en":"His voice was very faint."},{"cn":"玄鬼蹲下，手掌覆上那些黑影。","en":"Genki crouched, laying his hand over the shadows."},{"cn":"這一次，他不能只讓它們失形。","en":"This time, he could not simply let them lose shape."},{"cn":"因為它們已經找到容器。","en":"Because they had already found a vessel."},{"cn":"黑影不再只是偏見。","en":"The shadow was no longer only prejudice."},{"cn":"它們已經成為指名。","en":"It had already become a Naming."},{"cn":"玄鬼閉上眼。","en":"Genki closed his eyes."},{"cn":"他聽見黑影裡的聲音：","en":"He heard voices within the shadow:"},{"cn":"「河童本來就拉人下水。」","en":"\"Kappa have always pulled people into the water.\""},{"cn":"「河童天生壞。」","en":"\"Kappa are born wicked.\""},{"cn":"「牠們不值得相信。」","en":"\"They can't be trusted.\""},{"cn":"每一句，都像針。","en":"Each word was like a needle."},{"cn":"玄鬼的手微微顫抖。","en":"Genki's hand trembled faintly."},{"cn":"如果他吞下這些話，碧吉就會被放過。","en":"If he swallowed these words, Aokichi would be let go."},{"cn":"人群會安靜。","en":"The crowd would fall quiet."},{"cn":"故事會結束。","en":"The story would end."},{"cn":"他沒有。","en":"He did not."},{"cn":"他用力把黑影從碧吉身上撕開。","en":"He tore the shadow off Aokichi by force."},{"cn":"那撕裂的感覺，比吞下更痛。","en":"That tearing hurt more than swallowing would have."},{"cn":"黑影在空中尖叫，失去依附。","en":"The shadow screamed in the air, losing its hold."},{"cn":"人群只看見火光裡有什麼東西翻動。","en":"The crowd only saw something turning over in the firelight."},{"cn":"恐懼一瞬間失去方向。","en":"Fear, in that instant, lost its direction."},{"cn":"棍棒停下。","en":"The clubs stopped."},{"cn":"有人後退。","en":"Some stepped back."},{"cn":"火勢終於被水桶撲滅。","en":"The fire was at last put out with buckets of water."},{"cn":"夜色慢慢恢復。","en":"The night slowly settled again."},{"cn":"碧吉躺在地上，喘得厲害。","en":"Aokichi lay on the ground, breathing hard."},{"cn":"皿裡的水幾乎乾了。","en":"The water in his dish had almost dried away."},{"cn":"玄鬼把他扶起。","en":"Genki lifted him up."},{"cn":"碧吉勉強笑了一下。","en":"Aokichi managed a weak smile."},{"cn":"「我是不是……犯規了？」","en":"\"Did I… break the rule?\""},{"cn":"玄鬼低聲說：","en":"Genki said quietly:"},{"cn":"「不是。」","en":"\"No.\""},{"cn":"他第一次把手放在碧吉肩上。","en":"For the first time, he placed his hand on Aokichi's shoulder."},{"cn":"不是命令。","en":"Not a command."},{"cn":"不是拉扯。","en":"Not a pull."},{"cn":"是支撐。","en":"A support."},{"cn":"黑縁從屋瓦跳下。","en":"Kuroberi leapt down from the tiles."},{"cn":"「這算什麼？」她低聲問。","en":"\"What do you call this?\" she asked quietly."},{"cn":"「修行？」","en":"\"The Practice?\""},{"cn":"白蓮從黑暗中走出。","en":"Byakuren stepped out from the darkness."},{"cn":"她看著碧吉背上的傷，又看向玄鬼。","en":"She looked at the wound on Aokichi's back, then at Genki."},{"cn":"「第一個代價。」她說。","en":"\"The first cost,\" she said."},{"cn":"「留下來，不只是你一個人的痛。」","en":"\"Staying is not only your pain to bear.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼沉默。","en":"Genki was silent."},{"cn":"白蓮繼續道：","en":"Byakuren went on:"},{"cn":"「修行的第四條。」","en":"\"The Fourth Precept of the Practice.\""},{"cn":"「即使失敗，也不後悔。」","en":"\"Even in failure, no regret.\""},{"cn":"碧吉抬頭。","en":"Aokichi looked up."},{"cn":"「這算失敗嗎？」","en":"\"Was this a failure?\""},{"cn":"白蓮點頭。","en":"Byakuren nodded."},{"cn":"「你讓他們再次指名了你。」","en":"\"You let them name you again.\""},{"cn":"碧吉的笑容黯了一瞬。","en":"Aokichi's smile dimmed for a moment."},{"cn":"玄鬼卻說：","en":"But Genki said:"},{"cn":"「但他沒有後退。」","en":"\"But he did not step back.\""},{"cn":"白蓮看著玄鬼。","en":"Byakuren looked at Genki."},{"cn":"眼神第一次柔了一點。","en":"Her gaze softened, for the first time, a little."},{"cn":"「很好。」","en":"\"Good.\""},{"cn":"遠處，百鬼夜行的步伐再度響起。","en":"Far off, the tread of the Night Parade sounded once more."},{"cn":"這一次，比前幾夜更重。","en":"This time, heavier than the nights before."},{"cn":"夜行感知到裂縫。","en":"The Parade had sensed the crack."},{"cn":"它正在靠近。","en":"It was drawing near."},{"cn":"玄鬼抬頭。","en":"Genki raised his head."},{"cn":"他知道——","en":"He knew —"},{"cn":"真正的試煉，才要開始。","en":"the true trial was only beginning."},{"cn":"（第五章完）","en":"(End of Chapter 5)"},{"cn":"⸻","en":"⸻"},{"cn":"第一部｜百鬼夜行","en":"Part One — The Night Parade"}]},{"id":"ch06","n":6,"title_cn":"第六章｜王的視線","title_en":"Chapter 6 — The King's Gaze","lines":[{"cn":"夜行這一次來得比往常早。","en":"This time the Night Parade came earlier than usual."},{"cn":"不是深夜。","en":"Not deep night."},{"cn":"而是剛入戌時。","en":"Just past the hour of the Dog."},{"cn":"江戶的燈還亮著。","en":"Edo's lamps were still lit."},{"cn":"人們尚未完全躲進屋內。","en":"People had not yet fully retreated indoors."},{"cn":"恐懼尚未沉澱。","en":"Fear had not yet settled."},{"cn":"但步伐已經響起。","en":"But the tread had already begun to sound."},{"cn":"不是整齊的潮水。","en":"Not a tide moving in order."},{"cn":"而是更沉、更慢的震動。","en":"But a heavier, slower tremor."},{"cn":"玄鬼立在橋中央。","en":"Genki stood at the center of the bridge."},{"cn":"碧吉傷未癒，卻仍站在他身側。","en":"Aokichi's wound had not healed, yet he still stood at his side."},{"cn":"黑縁不再玩笑，尾巴緊繃。","en":"Kuroberi no longer joked, her tail drawn taut."},{"cn":"白蓮的目光比以往更冷。","en":"Byakuren's gaze was colder than before."},{"cn":"「它生氣了。」黑縁低聲說。","en":"\"It's angry,\" Kuroberi said quietly."},{"cn":"夜行並非有情緒。","en":"The Night Parade did not have feelings."},{"cn":"它是規律。","en":"It was a regularity."},{"cn":"可當規律被破壞，","en":"But when that regularity was broken,"},{"cn":"它會試圖恢復平衡。","en":"it would try to restore its balance."},{"cn":"街道盡頭，黑影開始聚攏。","en":"At the end of the street, shadows began to gather."},{"cn":"這次不是碎裂的恐懼。","en":"This time it was not shattered fear."},{"cn":"而是熟悉的形體——","en":"But a familiar form —"},{"cn":"高大的輪廓。","en":"a tall silhouette."},{"cn":"火焰般的氣息。","en":"A presence like flame."},{"cn":"壓迫得讓瓦片都輕顫。","en":"Pressing down so hard the roof tiles trembled faintly."},{"cn":"碧吉吞了口口水。","en":"Aokichi swallowed."},{"cn":"「那個……不像普通的。」","en":"\"That one… doesn't feel ordinary.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼沒有回答。","en":"Genki did not answer."},{"cn":"他知道那氣息。","en":"He knew that presence."},{"cn":"大江炎馬－酒吞童子。","en":"Ōe Enma — the Shuten-dōji."},{"cn":"夜行最古老的重量之一。","en":"One of the oldest weights within the Night Parade."},{"cn":"火焰般的長髮垂落肩頭，","en":"Hair like flame trailing down over his shoulders,"},{"cn":"身軀魁梧如山石。","en":"his frame massive as a mountain stone."},{"cn":"他不是走來。","en":"He did not walk forward."},{"cn":"是讓空氣讓開。","en":"He made the air itself give way."},{"cn":"「玄鬼。」","en":"\"Genki.\""},{"cn":"他的聲音低沉，像酒罈滾動。","en":"His voice was low, like a sake jar rolling."},{"cn":"「你讓夜行變慢。」","en":"\"You're slowing the Parade down.\""},{"cn":"不是質問。","en":"Not a question."},{"cn":"是陳述。","en":"A statement."},{"cn":"玄鬼與他對視。","en":"Genki met his gaze."},{"cn":"「夜行不該只是吞噬。」","en":"\"The Parade should not only devour.\""},{"cn":"炎馬笑了。","en":"Enma laughed."},{"cn":"那笑不是輕蔑。","en":"That laugh held no contempt."},{"cn":"是某種疲憊的共鳴。","en":"It held some weary resonance."},{"cn":"「你終於說出來了。」","en":"\"So you finally said it.\""},{"cn":"白蓮眼神微動。","en":"Byakuren's eyes flickered."},{"cn":"這不是她預期的反應。","en":"This was not the response she had expected."},{"cn":"炎馬走近一步。","en":"Enma took a step closer."},{"cn":"人群遠處已經開始躁動。","en":"Far off, the crowd had already begun to stir."},{"cn":"有些人看見，有些人看不見。","en":"Some could see, some could not."},{"cn":"恐懼門檻開始升高。","en":"The threshold of fear began to rise."},{"cn":"「你以為停止回應，就能改變什麼？」炎馬問。","en":"\"You think that by refusing to answer, you can change something?\" Enma asked."},{"cn":"玄鬼回答：","en":"Genki answered:"},{"cn":"「我不知道。」","en":"\"I don't know.\""},{"cn":"炎馬又笑。","en":"Enma laughed again."},{"cn":"「很好。」","en":"\"Good.\""},{"cn":"他忽然抬手。","en":"He suddenly raised his hand."},{"cn":"不是攻擊玄鬼。","en":"Not to attack Genki."},{"cn":"而是抓住空氣。","en":"But to seize the air itself."},{"cn":"那團尚未成形的夜行黑影，在他手中凝成一顆暗紅色的球體。","en":"The still-unformed shadow of the Night Parade condensed in his hand into a dark red sphere."},{"cn":"「你不吞，我來吞。」","en":"\"If you won't swallow it, I will.\""},{"cn":"他張口，將黑影吸入。","en":"He opened his mouth and drew the shadow in."},{"cn":"街道瞬間安靜。","en":"The street fell silent in an instant."},{"cn":"恐懼被回收。","en":"The fear was reclaimed."},{"cn":"人群像突然醒來，困惑地看著四周。","en":"The crowd looked around, dazed, as if suddenly woken."},{"cn":"規律恢復。","en":"Order was restored."},{"cn":"炎馬吐出一口熱氣。","en":"Enma breathed out a mouthful of heat."},{"cn":"「看見了嗎？」他說。","en":"\"See that?\" he said."},{"cn":"「夜行不需要你。」","en":"\"The Parade doesn't need you.\""},{"cn":"這句話比挑釁更沉。","en":"Those words landed heavier than any taunt."},{"cn":"玄鬼沒有動。","en":"Genki did not move."},{"cn":"炎馬看著他。","en":"Enma looked at him."},{"cn":"「你要改變規律？」","en":"\"You want to change the regularity?\""},{"cn":"「那就承擔比我更多的重量。」","en":"\"Then bear a heavier weight than mine.\""},{"cn":"說完，他轉身。","en":"With that, he turned."},{"cn":"夜行的步伐重新整齊。","en":"The Parade's tread fell back into order."},{"cn":"裂縫似乎被暫時縫合。","en":"The crack seemed, for now, sewn shut."},{"cn":"碧吉愣住。","en":"Aokichi stood frozen."},{"cn":"「他……幫我們？」","en":"\"Did he… help us?\""},{"cn":"白蓮低聲說：","en":"Byakuren said quietly:"},{"cn":"「不。」","en":"\"No.\""},{"cn":"「他只是維持秩序。」","en":"\"He was only maintaining order.\""},{"cn":"黑縁看著玄鬼。","en":"Kuroberi looked at Genki."},{"cn":"「你還要繼續嗎？」","en":"\"Will you keep going?\""},{"cn":"玄鬼望著遠去的炎馬。","en":"Genki watched Enma recede into the distance."},{"cn":"他明白了一件事。","en":"He understood one thing."},{"cn":"夜行不是單一存在。","en":"The Night Parade was not a single being."},{"cn":"它由許多重量構成。","en":"It was made of many weights."},{"cn":"而其中最重的——","en":"And the heaviest among them —"},{"cn":"是那些早已習慣規律的王。","en":"were the kings who had long grown used to the regularity."},{"cn":"炎馬沒有反對他。","en":"Enma had not opposed him."},{"cn":"卻用行動證明：","en":"Yet by his action he had proven:"},{"cn":"你若不承擔，別人會承擔。","en":"if you do not bear it, someone else will."},{"cn":"可那並不代表規律正確。","en":"But that did not mean the regularity was right."},{"cn":"玄鬼低聲說：","en":"Genki said quietly:"},{"cn":"「他厭倦了。」","en":"\"He's grown weary of it.\""},{"cn":"白蓮抬眼。","en":"Byakuren raised her eyes."},{"cn":"「什麼？」","en":"\"What?\""},{"cn":"「他吞下時，沒有喜悅。」","en":"\"When he swallowed it, there was no joy in him.\""},{"cn":"白蓮沉默。","en":"Byakuren said nothing."},{"cn":"她看見了。","en":"She had seen it too."},{"cn":"炎馬吞噬恐懼時，眼神空洞。","en":"When Enma devoured the fear, his gaze had been hollow."},{"cn":"不是權力。","en":"Not power."},{"cn":"不是驕傲。","en":"Not pride."},{"cn":"是長久重複後的疲憊。","en":"It was the exhaustion of long repetition."},{"cn":"這是第二幕真正的轉折。","en":"This was the true turning point of the second act."},{"cn":"玄鬼不是孤單的裂縫。","en":"Genki was not a lone crack."},{"cn":"規律內部，本身就有倦意。","en":"Within the regularity itself, there was already a weariness."},{"cn":"遠處，夜行完全遠去。","en":"Far off, the Night Parade withdrew entirely."},{"cn":"江戶恢復平靜。","en":"Edo returned to stillness."},{"cn":"可平靜不再完整。","en":"But the stillness was no longer whole."},{"cn":"白蓮輕聲說：","en":"Byakuren said softly:"},{"cn":"「下一次，不會這麼簡單。」","en":"\"Next time, it won't be this simple.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼點頭。","en":"Genki nodded."},{"cn":"他第一次真正理解修行的重量。","en":"For the first time, he truly understood the weight of the Practice."},{"cn":"不是對抗夜行。","en":"It was not to stand against the Night Parade."},{"cn":"而是——","en":"It was —"},{"cn":"讓夜行內部開始動搖。","en":"to make something within the Parade itself begin to waver."},{"cn":"（第六章完）","en":"(End of Chapter 6)"},{"cn":"⸻","en":"⸻"},{"cn":"第一部｜百鬼夜行","en":"Part One — The Night Parade"}]},{"id":"ch07","n":7,"title_cn":"第七章｜忠誠的牙","title_en":"Chapter 7 — The Fang of Loyalty","lines":[{"cn":"夜沒有立刻降臨。","en":"Night did not fall at once."},{"cn":"天色在黃昏與黑暗之間停滯，像一口未嚥下的氣。","en":"The sky hung stalled between dusk and dark, like a breath not yet swallowed."},{"cn":"炎馬離開後，江戶暫時恢復平衡。","en":"After Enma left, Edo returned for a time to balance."},{"cn":"恐懼被吞下，秩序被縫合。","en":"Fear was swallowed, order stitched shut."},{"cn":"可裂縫並沒有消失。","en":"But the crack did not vanish."},{"cn":"它只是往更深的地方移動。","en":"It only moved to somewhere deeper."},{"cn":"橋邊的風帶著濕氣。","en":"The wind off the bridge carried damp."},{"cn":"碧吉背上的傷還未痊癒，走路時仍有些僵硬。","en":"The wound on Aokichi's back had not healed; he still walked stiffly."},{"cn":"黑縁坐在河堤石階上，爪子在石面上輕輕刮著。","en":"Kuroberi sat on the stone steps of the embankment, claws scraping lightly at the stone."},{"cn":"白蓮站得更遠些，像在等待某個必然的來者。","en":"Byakuren stood farther off, as if waiting for some arrival that was bound to come."},{"cn":"玄鬼知道誰會來。","en":"Genki knew who would come."},{"cn":"忠誠總是來得最快。","en":"Loyalty always arrived first."},{"cn":"夜色真正落下時，空氣忽然緊繃。","en":"When true night finally fell, the air turned suddenly taut."},{"cn":"不是沉重。","en":"Not heavy."},{"cn":"是鋒利。","en":"Sharp."},{"cn":"像某種東西正在逼近——","en":"As if something were closing in—"},{"cn":"不是潮水，而是刀鋒。","en":"not a tide, but a blade's edge."},{"cn":"一個身影從黑暗中踏出。","en":"A figure stepped out of the darkness."},{"cn":"茨木義牙。","en":"Ibaraki Giga."},{"cn":"他的步伐不像炎馬那樣穩重，","en":"His stride did not carry Enma's steadiness,"},{"cn":"也不像玄鬼那樣沉。","en":"nor Genki's weight."},{"cn":"他走得很直。","en":"He walked very straight."},{"cn":"很快。","en":"Very fast."},{"cn":"很不容質疑。","en":"Not to be questioned."},{"cn":"「玄鬼。」","en":"\"Genki.\""},{"cn":"聲音沒有寒暄。","en":"The voice held no greeting."},{"cn":"義牙的眼神像磨亮的刃。","en":"Giga's eyes were like a blade honed sharp."},{"cn":"「你讓炎馬大人親自出手。」","en":"\"You made Lord Enma act himself.\""},{"cn":"那不是質問。","en":"That was not a question."},{"cn":"那是指控。","en":"It was an accusation."},{"cn":"碧吉下意識後退一步。","en":"Aokichi stepped back without thinking."},{"cn":"黑縁站起身，尾巴立起。","en":"Kuroberi rose to his feet, tail lifting."},{"cn":"玄鬼沒有回避。","en":"Genki did not turn away."},{"cn":"「我沒有要求他。」","en":"\"I did not ask him to.\""},{"cn":"義牙冷笑。","en":"Giga sneered."},{"cn":"「正因如此。」","en":"\"That is exactly the problem.\""},{"cn":"他向前一步。","en":"He stepped forward."},{"cn":"氣壓壓低。","en":"The pressure in the air dropped low."},{"cn":"「你動搖了規律。」","en":"\"You have shaken the rhythm.\""},{"cn":"「炎馬大人本不必再吞噬那種重量。」","en":"\"Lord Enma should not have had to swallow that weight again.\""},{"cn":"白蓮靜靜看著。","en":"Byakuren watched in silence."},{"cn":"她知道這不是單純的忠誠。","en":"She knew this was not simple loyalty."},{"cn":"這是恐懼。","en":"This was fear."},{"cn":"若王疲憊，","en":"If the king grew weary,"},{"cn":"追隨者會更不安。","en":"his followers would grow more uneasy still."},{"cn":"義牙的手握緊。","en":"Giga's fist clenched."},{"cn":"「你以為停下來是高尚？」","en":"\"You think stopping is noble?\""},{"cn":"玄鬼沉聲回答：","en":"Genki answered in a low voice:"},{"cn":"「不是。」","en":"\"No.\""},{"cn":"義牙一瞬間愣住。","en":"Giga froze for an instant."},{"cn":"他預期反駁，","en":"He had expected defiance,"},{"cn":"預期辯解。","en":"expected justification."},{"cn":"卻沒有預期坦白。","en":"He had not expected honesty."},{"cn":"「那是什麼？」義牙逼問。","en":"\"Then what is it?\" Giga demanded."},{"cn":"玄鬼抬眼。","en":"Genki raised his eyes."},{"cn":"「厭倦。」","en":"\"Weariness.\""},{"cn":"這兩個字落下時，","en":"When those two words fell,"},{"cn":"義牙的呼吸一滯。","en":"Giga's breath caught."},{"cn":"因為那正是他最不敢承認的情緒。","en":"Because that was the very feeling he dared not admit to himself."},{"cn":"義牙一直追隨炎馬。","en":"Giga had followed Enma always."},{"cn":"從大江山，到無數次夜行。","en":"From Mount Ōe, through countless Night Parades."},{"cn":"他用牙撕裂恐懼，用力氣護住王。","en":"He had torn fear apart with his fangs, had guarded the king with his strength."},{"cn":"他不曾質疑。","en":"He had never questioned."},{"cn":"因為質疑意味著——","en":"Because to question meant—"},{"cn":"也許一切本可以不同。","en":"that perhaps things could have been otherwise."},{"cn":"「你沒有資格厭倦。」義牙低聲說。","en":"\"You have no right to weariness,\" Giga said, low."},{"cn":"「你的位置，是前端。」","en":"\"Your place is at the front.\""},{"cn":"「你若退後，秩序會亂。」","en":"\"If you fall back, order will fray.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼沒有動。","en":"Genki did not move."},{"cn":"「秩序若必須靠我維持，」","en":"\"If order must be held up by me alone,\""},{"cn":"他說，","en":"he said,"},{"cn":"「那秩序本就脆弱。」","en":"\"then order was fragile to begin with.\""},{"cn":"這句話，比挑戰更狠。","en":"That sentence cut deeper than any challenge."},{"cn":"義牙的瞳孔一縮。","en":"Giga's pupils contracted."},{"cn":"他出手了。","en":"He struck."},{"cn":"不是全力。","en":"Not with full force."},{"cn":"是試探。","en":"A test."},{"cn":"拳風掠過玄鬼側肩。","en":"The wind of his fist grazed Genki's shoulder."},{"cn":"石橋裂開一道細縫。","en":"A fine crack split the stone bridge."},{"cn":"碧吉驚叫。","en":"Aokichi cried out."},{"cn":"黑縁跳上牆頭。","en":"Kuroberi leapt to the wall's top."},{"cn":"白蓮沒有動。","en":"Byakuren did not move."},{"cn":"玄鬼沒有反擊。","en":"Genki did not strike back."},{"cn":"第二拳落下。","en":"A second blow fell."},{"cn":"玄鬼擋住。","en":"Genki blocked it."},{"cn":"石屑飛濺。","en":"Stone chips scattered."},{"cn":"義牙的眼裡燃起怒意。","en":"Anger kindled in Giga's eyes."},{"cn":"「反擊！」","en":"\"Strike back!\""},{"cn":"他吼。","en":"He roared."},{"cn":"「證明你仍有資格站在前面！」","en":"\"Prove you still have the right to stand at the front!\""},{"cn":"玄鬼沒有。","en":"Genki did not."},{"cn":"他只是穩穩承受。","en":"He only bore it, steady."},{"cn":"每一次衝擊，","en":"Each impact"},{"cn":"都讓橋面更碎。","en":"left the bridge more broken."},{"cn":"義牙的拳頭帶著怒。","en":"Giga's fists carried fury."},{"cn":"可怒底下，是恐懼。","en":"But beneath the fury was fear."},{"cn":"他怕炎馬動搖。","en":"He feared Enma faltering."},{"cn":"怕夜行失衡。","en":"Feared the Night Parade losing its balance."},{"cn":"怕自己追隨的一切，只是一場漫長的誤解。","en":"Feared that everything he had followed was only one long misunderstanding."},{"cn":"「你說厭倦——」","en":"\"You say weariness—\""},{"cn":"義牙低聲說，","en":"Giga said, low,"},{"cn":"「那你讓我們怎麼辦？」","en":"\"then what would you have us do?\""},{"cn":"這句話，比拳頭更重。","en":"That sentence weighed heavier than any blow."},{"cn":"玄鬼第一次看見義牙的動搖。","en":"For the first time, Genki saw Giga waver."},{"cn":"他沒有回以力量。","en":"He did not answer with strength."},{"cn":"他只是說：","en":"He only said:"},{"cn":"「你可以選擇。」","en":"\"You can choose.\""},{"cn":"義牙的動作停住。","en":"Giga's movement stopped."},{"cn":"選擇？","en":"Choose?"},{"cn":"忠誠之人最怕這兩個字。","en":"Those two words were what the loyal feared most."},{"cn":"因為忠誠本身，就是放棄選擇。","en":"Because loyalty itself was the surrender of choice."},{"cn":"義牙後退一步。","en":"Giga stepped back."},{"cn":"胸口劇烈起伏。","en":"His chest heaved violently."},{"cn":"他不再攻擊。","en":"He no longer attacked."},{"cn":"卻也沒有離開。","en":"Yet he did not leave either."},{"cn":"「你若錯，」","en":"\"If you are wrong,\""},{"cn":"他低聲說，","en":"he said, low,"},{"cn":"「炎馬大人會先崩。」","en":"\"Lord Enma will break first.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼回答：","en":"Genki answered:"},{"cn":"「若我錯，我會承擔。」","en":"\"If I am wrong, I will bear it.\""},{"cn":"義牙盯著他。","en":"Giga stared at him."},{"cn":"長久。","en":"A long while."},{"cn":"然後轉身。","en":"Then turned away."},{"cn":"「我會看著你。」","en":"\"I will be watching you.\""},{"cn":"他消失在夜裡。","en":"He vanished into the night."},{"cn":"橋上裂縫延伸。","en":"The crack on the bridge lengthened."},{"cn":"碧吉喘著氣。","en":"Aokichi gasped for breath."},{"cn":"「你為什麼不打回去？」","en":"\"Why didn't you strike back?\""},{"cn":"玄鬼看著破裂的石面。","en":"Genki looked at the broken stone."},{"cn":"「他不是敵人。」","en":"\"He is not an enemy.\""},{"cn":"黑縁低聲說：","en":"Kuroberi said, low:"},{"cn":"「他會讓你更難走。」","en":"\"He will make this harder for you.\""},{"cn":"白蓮走近。","en":"Byakuren drew near."},{"cn":"「很好。」","en":"\"Good.\""},{"cn":"她的聲音比夜更冷。","en":"Her voice was colder than the night."},{"cn":"「修行第五條。」","en":"\"The Fifth Precept.\""},{"cn":"「面對忠誠，不摧毀。」","en":"\"Faced with loyalty, do not destroy it.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼沒有回應。","en":"Genki did not answer."},{"cn":"他看著裂縫。","en":"He looked at the crack."},{"cn":"裂縫在橋上。","en":"The crack was in the bridge."},{"cn":"也在夜行裡。","en":"It was in the Night Parade too."},{"cn":"更在那些追隨王的人心裡。","en":"And deeper still, in the hearts of those who followed the king."},{"cn":"遠處，百鬼夜行再度蠢動。","en":"Far off, the Night Parade of a Hundred Demons stirred again."},{"cn":"但這一次，","en":"But this time,"},{"cn":"步伐並不齊整。","en":"its steps were not in step."},{"cn":"（第七章完）","en":"(End of Chapter 7)"},{"cn":"⸻","en":"⸻"},{"cn":"第一部｜百鬼夜行","en":"Part One — The Night Parade"}]},{"id":"ch08","n":8,"title_cn":"第八章｜怨的形狀","title_en":"Chapter 8 — The Shape of Resentment","lines":[{"cn":"江戶的夜，忽然變得安靜。","en":"Edo's night turned suddenly quiet."},{"cn":"不是沒有聲音。","en":"Not soundless."},{"cn":"而是聲音被壓低。","en":"But sound pressed low."},{"cn":"像有人把整座城放進水裡。","en":"As if someone had set the whole city down into water."},{"cn":"玄鬼站在橋中央時，就察覺到了。","en":"Genki felt it the moment he stood at the bridge's center."},{"cn":"這不是夜行的步伐。","en":"This was not the Parade's tread."},{"cn":"不是規律。","en":"Not the rhythm."},{"cn":"而是——情緒。","en":"It was—emotion."},{"cn":"純粹的、沒有秩序的情緒。","en":"Pure, unordered emotion."},{"cn":"碧吉打了個寒顫。","en":"Aokichi shivered."},{"cn":"「今晚……沒有隊伍。」","en":"\"Tonight… there's no procession.\""},{"cn":"黑縁的耳朵壓得很低。","en":"Kuroberi's ears flattened low."},{"cn":"「因為今晚不是規律在動。」","en":"\"Because tonight it is not the rhythm moving.\""},{"cn":"「是心。」","en":"\"It is the heart.\""},{"cn":"第一聲哭從遠處傳來。","en":"The first cry came from far off."},{"cn":"不是孩子。","en":"Not a child's."},{"cn":"是成年女人的聲音。","en":"A grown woman's voice."},{"cn":"壓抑過久的那種。","en":"The kind held down too long."},{"cn":"斷斷續續。","en":"Broken, halting."},{"cn":"像被掐住喉嚨。","en":"As if a hand were closing on her throat."},{"cn":"玄鬼轉身。","en":"Genki turned."},{"cn":"聲音來自一條巷子。","en":"The sound came from an alley."},{"cn":"白蓮沒有阻止。","en":"Byakuren did not stop him."},{"cn":"她只是低聲說：","en":"She only said, low:"},{"cn":"「來了。」","en":"\"It has come.\""},{"cn":"巷子裡沒有火。","en":"There was no fire in the alley."},{"cn":"沒有風。","en":"No wind."},{"cn":"只有一盞燈在搖。","en":"Only a single lantern, swaying."},{"cn":"燈下，站著一個女子。","en":"Beneath it stood a woman."},{"cn":"白衣，長髮垂落。","en":"White robes, long hair hanging loose."},{"cn":"臉上戴著半張面具。","en":"Half a mask covered her face."},{"cn":"般若-綾女。","en":"The hannya—Ayame."},{"cn":"她沒有看玄鬼。","en":"She did not look at Genki."},{"cn":"她看著自己的手。","en":"She looked at her own hands."},{"cn":"那雙手在發抖。","en":"Those hands were trembling."},{"cn":"「你知道嗎，」她輕聲說。","en":"\"Do you know,\" she said softly."},{"cn":"「我沒有想殺他。」","en":"\"I never meant to kill him.\""},{"cn":"聲音平靜得可怕。","en":"Her voice was calm in a terrible way."},{"cn":"碧吉往後退。","en":"Aokichi drew back."},{"cn":"黑縁的尾巴幾乎炸開。","en":"Kuroberi's tail nearly burst wide."},{"cn":"玄鬼走近一步。","en":"Genki stepped closer."},{"cn":"綾女抬起頭。","en":"Ayame lifted her head."},{"cn":"那半張面具下的眼睛通紅。","en":"Beneath that half mask, her eyes were red raw."},{"cn":"「我只是問他，」她說，","en":"\"I only asked him,\" she said,"},{"cn":"「為什麼？」","en":"\"why?\""},{"cn":"空氣開始扭曲。","en":"The air began to warp."},{"cn":"不是黑影。","en":"Not shadow."},{"cn":"是情緒本身具象化。","en":"Emotion itself, given form."},{"cn":"牆壁滲出水痕。","en":"Water seeped from the walls."},{"cn":"地面出現裂紋。","en":"Cracks opened in the ground."},{"cn":"綾女的聲音變得低沉。","en":"Ayame's voice sank lower."},{"cn":"「為什麼他可以說愛我，」","en":"\"Why could he say he loved me,\""},{"cn":"「卻在別人面前說我是怪物？」","en":"\"and call me a monster before others?\""},{"cn":"面具慢慢浮起一點點裂痕。","en":"Fine cracks began rising across the mask."},{"cn":"她不是來攻擊。","en":"She had not come to attack."},{"cn":"她是來崩潰。","en":"She had come to break apart."},{"cn":"玄鬼站在她面前。","en":"Genki stood before her."},{"cn":"沒有釋放威壓。","en":"He released no pressure."},{"cn":"沒有後退。","en":"He did not step back."},{"cn":"綾女看著他。","en":"Ayame looked at him."},{"cn":"「你說，不回應。」","en":"\"You say, do not answer.\""},{"cn":"「那我的怨呢？」","en":"\"Then what of my resentment?\""},{"cn":"「你要我吞下去？」","en":"\"You want me to swallow it?\""},{"cn":"玄鬼沒有回答。","en":"Genki did not answer."},{"cn":"因為這一次，他不能用理性。","en":"Because this time, he could not use reason."},{"cn":"綾女的怨不是偏見。","en":"Ayame's resentment was not prejudice."},{"cn":"不是流言。","en":"Not rumor."},{"cn":"是被背叛的真實。","en":"It was the truth of betrayal."},{"cn":"她往前一步。","en":"She stepped forward."},{"cn":"地面裂開。","en":"The ground split."},{"cn":"空氣像被刀切開。","en":"The air felt cut by a blade."},{"cn":"碧吉忍不住喊：","en":"Aokichi could not help but cry out:"},{"cn":"「她要失控了！」","en":"\"She's losing control!\""},{"cn":"黑縁低聲說：","en":"Kuroberi said, low:"},{"cn":"「她不是失控。」","en":"\"She is not losing control.\""},{"cn":"「她是在證明自己存在。」","en":"\"She is proving she exists.\""},{"cn":"綾女摘下面具。","en":"Ayame took off her mask."},{"cn":"那張臉沒有可怖的鬼相。","en":"That face held no fearsome demon look."},{"cn":"只有極深的疲憊。","en":"Only exhaustion, deep beyond measure."},{"cn":"「如果我不憤怒，」","en":"\"If I am not angry,\""},{"cn":"她低聲說，","en":"she said, low,"},{"cn":"「他們就會說我本來就不值得。」","en":"\"they will say I was never worth anything.\""},{"cn":"淚水滑下。","en":"Tears slid down."},{"cn":"不是血。","en":"Not blood."},{"cn":"不是火。","en":"Not fire."},{"cn":"只是淚。","en":"Only tears."},{"cn":"可那淚落在地上，卻燃起淡淡的紫色光。","en":"But where they struck the ground, a faint violet light kindled."},{"cn":"情緒一旦被壓太久，","en":"Once emotion has been pressed down too long,"},{"cn":"會成為力量。","en":"it becomes power."},{"cn":"玄鬼終於開口。","en":"Genki finally spoke."},{"cn":"「你的怨，不是錯。」","en":"\"Your resentment is not wrong.\""},{"cn":"綾女愣住。","en":"Ayame froze."},{"cn":"碧吉也愣住。","en":"Aokichi froze too."},{"cn":"白蓮的眼神微微一動。","en":"Something flickered faintly in Byakuren's eyes."},{"cn":"「但怨不是你全部。」","en":"\"But resentment is not all of you.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼繼續說。","en":"Genki went on."},{"cn":"綾女的呼吸亂了。","en":"Ayame's breath came ragged."},{"cn":"「他們說我是怪物。」","en":"\"They call me a monster.\""},{"cn":"「他們說女人若憤怒，就是妖。」","en":"\"They say a woman who grows angry is a yokai.\""},{"cn":"「那我就成妖給他們看。」","en":"\"Then I will become a yokai before their eyes.\""},{"cn":"空氣壓縮。","en":"The air compressed."},{"cn":"紫光擴散。","en":"The violet light spread."},{"cn":"如果她完全接受這個標籤，","en":"If she fully accepted that label,"},{"cn":"她就會真正成為夜行的一部分。","en":"she would truly become part of the Night Parade."},{"cn":"不是因為她壞。","en":"Not because she was evil."},{"cn":"而是因為她相信了那個定義。","en":"But because she had come to believe that definition."},{"cn":"玄鬼向前一步。","en":"Genki stepped forward."},{"cn":"不是壓制。","en":"Not to restrain."},{"cn":"不是阻止。","en":"Not to stop her."},{"cn":"他只是站得更近。","en":"He only stood closer."},{"cn":"「你不需要證明。」","en":"\"You do not need to prove anything.\""},{"cn":"綾女的瞳孔顫了一下。","en":"A tremor passed through Ayame's eyes."},{"cn":"「若你不憤怒，」","en":"\"If you are not angry,\""},{"cn":"玄鬼說，","en":"Genki said,"},{"cn":"「你仍然存在。」","en":"\"you still exist.\""},{"cn":"那句話很輕。","en":"The words were very light."},{"cn":"卻像敲在最深的地方。","en":"Yet they struck at the deepest place."},{"cn":"綾女的肩膀開始顫抖。","en":"Ayame's shoulders began to shake."},{"cn":"怨在她身邊旋轉。","en":"The resentment spun around her."},{"cn":"它不想消失。","en":"It did not want to vanish."},{"cn":"它想被承認。","en":"It wanted to be acknowledged."},{"cn":"白蓮終於出聲。","en":"Byakuren spoke at last."},{"cn":"「修行第六條。」","en":"\"The Sixth Precept.\""},{"cn":"她說。","en":"she said."},{"cn":"「承認情緒，而不被情緒定義。」","en":"\"Acknowledge emotion; do not be defined by it.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼伸出手。","en":"Genki held out his hand."},{"cn":"不是為了承擔。","en":"Not to bear it for her."},{"cn":"不是為了吞噬。","en":"Not to swallow it."},{"cn":"只是讓綾女看見——","en":"Only to let Ayame see—"},{"cn":"有人不因她的怨而退後。","en":"that someone would not step back from her resentment."},{"cn":"綾女的面具完全裂開。","en":"Ayame's mask broke apart completely."},{"cn":"碎片落地。","en":"The pieces fell to the ground."},{"cn":"紫光慢慢熄滅。","en":"The violet light slowly went out."},{"cn":"她跪在地上，哭得無聲。","en":"She knelt on the ground, weeping without a sound."},{"cn":"不是因為恨。","en":"Not from hatred."},{"cn":"而是因為——","en":"But because—"},{"cn":"她終於不需要繼續演那個怪物。","en":"she no longer had to go on playing the monster."},{"cn":"夜色恢復平靜。","en":"The night settled back into calm."},{"cn":"沒有戰鬥。","en":"No battle."},{"cn":"沒有爆裂。","en":"No eruption."},{"cn":"只有一種疲憊後的安靜。","en":"Only a stillness after exhaustion."},{"cn":"碧吉鬆了口氣。","en":"Aokichi let out a breath of relief."},{"cn":"黑縁低聲說：","en":"Kuroberi said, low:"},{"cn":"「這比打架難多了。」","en":"\"This is harder than any fight.\""},{"cn":"白蓮看著玄鬼。","en":"Byakuren looked at Genki."},{"cn":"她第一次真正確認：","en":"For the first time she was truly certain:"},{"cn":"這不是反抗。","en":"this was not defiance."},{"cn":"這是一條路。","en":"This was a path."},{"cn":"遠處，夜行的步伐沒有靠近。","en":"Far off, the Parade's steps did not draw near."},{"cn":"因為今夜，沒有新的鬼誕生。","en":"Because tonight, no new oni was born."},{"cn":"綾女坐在地上，輕聲問：","en":"Ayame, sitting on the ground, asked softly:"},{"cn":"「我可以留下嗎？」","en":"\"May I stay?\""},{"cn":"玄鬼沒有回答。","en":"Genki did not answer."},{"cn":"他只是站在她身旁。","en":"He only stood beside her."},{"cn":"那已經是答案。","en":"That was already the answer."},{"cn":"（第八章完）","en":"(End of Chapter 8)"},{"cn":"第一部｜百鬼夜行","en":"Part One — The Night Parade"}]},{"id":"ch09","n":9,"title_cn":"第九章｜秩序的壓力","title_en":"Chapter 9 — The Weight of Order","lines":[{"cn":"夜沒有風。","en":"There was no wind that night."},{"cn":"江戶的燈一盞盞滅下去。","en":"Edo's lamps went out one by one."},{"cn":"不是因為恐懼。","en":"Not from fear."},{"cn":"而是因為疲倦。","en":"From weariness."},{"cn":"連續幾夜的動盪，讓整座城的氣息變得低沉。","en":"Nights of unrest in succession had left the whole city's breath sunk low."},{"cn":"玄鬼站在橋上。","en":"Genki stood on the bridge."},{"cn":"碧吉靠著橋柱。","en":"Aokichi leaned against the bridge post."},{"cn":"綾女靜靜坐在河邊，面具碎片仍在她腳旁。","en":"Ayame sat quietly by the river, the shards of her mask still at her feet."},{"cn":"黑縁躍上屋脊。","en":"Kuroberi leapt onto the roof ridge."},{"cn":"白蓮站得更遠。","en":"Byakuren stood farther off."},{"cn":"這一次，夜行沒有預兆。","en":"This time, the Night Parade gave no warning."},{"cn":"也沒有隊伍。","en":"And brought no procession."},{"cn":"空氣忽然變得乾淨。","en":"The air suddenly turned clean."},{"cn":"乾淨得不自然。","en":"Clean in a way that was not natural."},{"cn":"像有人把所有雜音抽走。","en":"As if someone had drawn out every stray sound."},{"cn":"然後——","en":"Then—"},{"cn":"一道白色的身影自空中落下。","en":"a white figure dropped from the sky."},{"cn":"不是墜落。","en":"Not a fall."},{"cn":"是降臨。","en":"A descent."},{"cn":"鞍馬白嶺－大天狗。","en":"Kurama Hakurei—the daitengu."},{"cn":"衣袍如雪，目光如山。","en":"Robes like snow, gaze like a mountain."},{"cn":"他沒有帶怒。","en":"He carried no anger."},{"cn":"也沒有帶質問。","en":"Nor any accusation."},{"cn":"只有秩序。","en":"Only order."},{"cn":"「裂縫擴大。」","en":"\"The crack is widening.\""},{"cn":"他的聲音不像炎馬那樣沉。","en":"His voice did not carry Enma's weight."},{"cn":"而是清。","en":"It was clear."},{"cn":"清得讓人無法躲避。","en":"So clear no one could turn from it."},{"cn":"玄鬼與他對視。","en":"Genki met his gaze."},{"cn":"白嶺的視線掃過在場的每一個。","en":"Hakurei's eyes swept over everyone present."},{"cn":"碧吉感到背脊發冷。","en":"A chill ran down Aokichi's spine."},{"cn":"綾女本能地想戴回面具。","en":"Ayame reached instinctively for her mask."},{"cn":"黑縁尾巴低垂。","en":"Kuroberi's tail dropped low."},{"cn":"白蓮卻沒有動。","en":"Byakuren alone did not move."},{"cn":"白嶺最後把目光落在玄鬼身上。","en":"Hakurei's gaze settled at last on Genki."},{"cn":"「你改變了流程。」","en":"\"You have changed the procedure.\""},{"cn":"不是批評。","en":"Not a criticism."},{"cn":"是確認。","en":"A confirmation."},{"cn":"玄鬼沒有否認。","en":"Genki did not deny it."},{"cn":"「是。」","en":"\"Yes.\""},{"cn":"白嶺微微點頭。","en":"Hakurei nodded slightly."},{"cn":"「結果。」","en":"\"The result.\""},{"cn":"他問。","en":"He asked."},{"cn":"玄鬼沉默。","en":"Genki was silent."},{"cn":"結果是什麼？","en":"What was the result?"},{"cn":"夜行變慢。","en":"The Parade had slowed."},{"cn":"王動搖。","en":"The king had faltered."},{"cn":"忠誠受震。","en":"Loyalty had been shaken."},{"cn":"怨沒有成鬼。","en":"Resentment had not become an oni."},{"cn":"白嶺等著。","en":"Hakurei waited."},{"cn":"玄鬼說：","en":"Genki said:"},{"cn":"「還在發生。」","en":"\"It is still happening.\""},{"cn":"白嶺的眼神沒有波動。","en":"No ripple crossed Hakurei's eyes."},{"cn":"「秩序不是實驗。」","en":"\"Order is not an experiment.\""},{"cn":"他說。","en":"He said."},{"cn":"「秩序是承重。」","en":"\"Order is a bearing of weight.\""},{"cn":"他向前一步。","en":"He stepped forward."},{"cn":"空氣更冷。","en":"The air grew colder."},{"cn":"「百鬼夜行存在，不是為了恐嚇。」","en":"\"The Night Parade of a Hundred Demons does not exist to frighten.\""},{"cn":"「而是為了平衡。」","en":"\"It exists for balance.\""},{"cn":"「若無夜行，恐懼會在城中自行滋長。」","en":"\"Without the Parade, fear would grow wild through the city on its own.\""},{"cn":"「若無承擔者，偏見會尋找無辜。」","en":"\"Without one to bear it, prejudice would go hunting for the innocent.\""},{"cn":"他的目光掃過碧吉。","en":"His gaze passed over Aokichi."},{"cn":"「你讓承擔變得不確定。」","en":"\"You have made the bearing uncertain.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼低聲問：","en":"Genki asked, low:"},{"cn":"「承擔，必須固定嗎？」","en":"\"Must the bearing be fixed?\""},{"cn":"白嶺看著他。","en":"Hakurei looked at him."},{"cn":"「必須。」","en":"\"It must.\""},{"cn":"沒有猶豫。","en":"No hesitation."},{"cn":"「因為不確定，比恐懼更危險。」","en":"\"Because uncertainty is more dangerous than fear.\""},{"cn":"這句話落下，連白蓮都微微側目。","en":"When that sentence fell, even Byakuren's eyes shifted slightly."},{"cn":"白嶺繼續：","en":"Hakurei went on."},{"cn":"「人類需要知道惡在哪裡。」","en":"\"Humans need to know where evil lies.\""},{"cn":"「若惡模糊，世界會失控。」","en":"\"If evil is unclear, the world will spin out of control.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼看著橋下的水。","en":"Genki looked down at the water beneath the bridge."},{"cn":"「那若惡本就在他們心裡呢？」","en":"\"And if evil was always inside them?\""},{"cn":"白嶺沒有動怒。","en":"Hakurei did not grow angry."},{"cn":"他只是說：","en":"He only said:"},{"cn":"「那也必須有形體。」","en":"\"Then it must still have a shape.\""},{"cn":"「否則他們會互相撕裂。」","en":"\"Or they will tear each other apart.\""},{"cn":"這不是辯論。","en":"This was not a debate."},{"cn":"這是兩種世界觀的對峙。","en":"It was two views of the world, standing face to face."},{"cn":"白蓮終於開口。","en":"Byakuren spoke at last."},{"cn":"「你怕的不是混亂。」","en":"\"What you fear is not chaos.\""},{"cn":"她說。","en":"she said."},{"cn":"「你怕的是秩序失去角色。」","en":"\"What you fear is order losing its role.\""},{"cn":"白嶺的視線落在她身上。","en":"Hakurei's gaze fell on her."},{"cn":"「你一直在觀察。」","en":"\"You have been watching all along.\""},{"cn":"「是。」","en":"\"Yes.\""},{"cn":"「那你也該明白。」","en":"\"Then you should understand too.\""},{"cn":"白嶺轉回玄鬼。","en":"Hakurei turned back to Genki."},{"cn":"「若你成功，百鬼夜行將消失。」","en":"\"If you succeed, the Night Parade of a Hundred Demons will vanish.\""},{"cn":"碧吉愣住。","en":"Aokichi froze."},{"cn":"綾女抬頭。","en":"Ayame looked up."},{"cn":"黑縁瞳孔收縮。","en":"Kuroberi's pupils contracted."},{"cn":"白嶺的聲音沒有情緒。","en":"Hakurei's voice held no emotion."},{"cn":"「那意味著，我們之中，多數將失去存在理由。」","en":"\"That means most of us will lose our reason to exist.\""},{"cn":"空氣沉得幾乎無法呼吸。","en":"The air grew so heavy it was hard to breathe."},{"cn":"玄鬼第一次真正理解這件事。","en":"For the first time, Genki truly understood."},{"cn":"若無鬼。","en":"If there is no oni."},{"cn":"若無承擔者。","en":"If there is no one to bear it."},{"cn":"若無恐懼的容器。","en":"If there is no vessel for fear."},{"cn":"那麼——","en":"then—"},{"cn":"夜行中的大半存在，都將不再需要。","en":"most of what exists within the Night Parade will no longer be needed."},{"cn":"白嶺不是在保護規律。","en":"Hakurei was not protecting the rhythm."},{"cn":"他在保護「存在」。","en":"He was protecting \"existence.\""},{"cn":"「你要的不是修行。」","en":"\"What you want is not the Practice.\""},{"cn":"白嶺說。","en":"Hakurei said."},{"cn":"「你要的是終結。」","en":"\"What you want is an ending.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼沉默。","en":"Genki was silent."},{"cn":"這句話刺得比義牙的拳頭更深。","en":"That sentence cut deeper than any of Giga's blows."},{"cn":"白蓮低聲說：","en":"Byakuren said, low:"},{"cn":"「終結，未必是毀滅。」","en":"\"An ending need not be destruction.\""},{"cn":"白嶺沒有反駁。","en":"Hakurei did not argue."},{"cn":"他只是說：","en":"He only said:"},{"cn":"「若你要走這條路。」","en":"\"If you mean to walk this road.\""},{"cn":"「你必須承擔所有消失。」","en":"\"You must bear all that vanishes with it.\""},{"cn":"這一句話，終於帶上重量。","en":"This sentence, at last, carried weight."},{"cn":"不是威脅。","en":"Not a threat."},{"cn":"是預告。","en":"A foretelling."},{"cn":"白嶺轉身。","en":"Hakurei turned."},{"cn":"「炎馬會讓夜行加重。」","en":"\"Enma will make the Parade heavier.\""},{"cn":"「烏嶽會監視。」","en":"\"Ugaku will watch.\""},{"cn":"「義牙會測試。」","en":"\"Giga will test you.\""},{"cn":"「而我——」","en":"\"And I—\""},{"cn":"他停了一瞬。","en":"He paused a moment."},{"cn":"「會在你失控時，斬斷。」","en":"\"Will cut you down, if you lose control.\""},{"cn":"說完，他消失在夜色中。","en":"With that, he vanished into the night."},{"cn":"空氣恢復。","en":"The air returned."},{"cn":"卻比之前更沉。","en":"But it hung heavier than before."},{"cn":"碧吉小聲問：","en":"Aokichi asked in a small voice:"},{"cn":"「他說的……是真的嗎？」","en":"\"What he said… was it true?\""},{"cn":"玄鬼沒有立刻回答。","en":"Genki did not answer at once."},{"cn":"綾女低聲說：","en":"Ayame said, low:"},{"cn":"「如果我們不再被需要……」","en":"\"If we are no longer needed…\""},{"cn":"黑縁冷笑。","en":"Kuroberi sneered."},{"cn":"「那不正是你們想要的？」","en":"\"Isn't that exactly what you all wanted?\""},{"cn":"白蓮看著玄鬼。","en":"Byakuren looked at Genki."},{"cn":"這是關鍵。","en":"This was the crux."},{"cn":"如果玄鬼動搖。","en":"If Genki wavered."},{"cn":"修行就會崩。","en":"The Practice would collapse."},{"cn":"玄鬼望向遠方。","en":"Genki looked into the distance."},{"cn":"「若消失是代價。」","en":"\"If vanishing is the price,\""},{"cn":"他說。","en":"he said."},{"cn":"「那我會最後一個。」","en":"\"then I will be the last to go.\""},{"cn":"這句話落下。","en":"That sentence fell."},{"cn":"白蓮的眼神第一次出現真正的波動。","en":"For the first time, real emotion stirred in Byakuren's eyes."},{"cn":"不是懷疑。","en":"Not doubt."},{"cn":"是預感。","en":"A premonition."},{"cn":"她知道——","en":"She knew—"},{"cn":"這不是宣言。","en":"this was not a declaration."},{"cn":"這是命運的種子。","en":"This was the seed of a fate."},{"cn":"夜色再次安靜。","en":"The night grew quiet again."},{"cn":"百鬼夜行在遠處沉重地走著。","en":"Far off, the Night Parade of a Hundred Demons walked on, heavy."},{"cn":"卻第一次，步伐帶著猶豫。","en":"But for the first time, its steps carried hesitation."},{"cn":"（第九章完）","en":"(End of Chapter 9)"},{"cn":"第一部｜百鬼夜行","en":"Part One — The Night Parade"}]},{"id":"ch10","n":10,"title_cn":"第十章｜夜行的意識","title_en":"Chapter 10 — The Parade's Mind","lines":[{"cn":"那一夜，沒有風。","en":"That night, there was no wind."},{"cn":"連河水都靜得不像活物。","en":"Even the river lay still, unlike a living thing."},{"cn":"江戶城上方的雲層低垂，像壓著一口看不見的鍋。","en":"The clouds hung low over Edo, like the lid pressing down on a pot no one could see."},{"cn":"玄鬼站在橋中央。","en":"Genki stood at the center of the bridge."},{"cn":"他能感覺到。","en":"He could feel it."},{"cn":"不是腳步聲。","en":"Not footsteps."},{"cn":"不是壓迫。","en":"Not pressure."},{"cn":"而是——凝視。","en":"But — a gaze."},{"cn":"百鬼夜行沒有出現。","en":"The Night Parade of a Hundred Demons had not appeared."},{"cn":"卻無處不在。","en":"And yet it was everywhere."},{"cn":"碧吉縮在橋下，皿裡的水莫名泛起細微波紋。","en":"Aokichi shrank beneath the bridge, the water in his dish rippling with no cause."},{"cn":"黑縁尾巴僵直。","en":"Kuroberi's tail went rigid."},{"cn":"綾女下意識抱緊雙臂。","en":"Ayame hugged her own arms without thinking."},{"cn":"白蓮輕聲說：","en":"Byakuren said softly:"},{"cn":"「它看見你了。」","en":"\"It has seen you.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼沒有問「它是誰」。","en":"Genki did not ask \"who is it.\""},{"cn":"他知道。","en":"He knew."},{"cn":"夜行不是某個個體。","en":"The Parade was not any single being."},{"cn":"不是炎馬。","en":"Not Enma."},{"cn":"不是白嶺。","en":"Not Hakurei."},{"cn":"不是任何一位妖怪。","en":"Not any one yokai."},{"cn":"夜行是集合。","en":"The Parade was a collection."},{"cn":"是千百年來恐懼運作的方式。","en":"It was the way fear had operated for a thousand years."},{"cn":"是人類與妖怪之間反覆確認的秩序。","en":"It was the order repeatedly confirmed between humans and yokai."},{"cn":"而現在——","en":"And now —"},{"cn":"它開始感到威脅。","en":"it had begun to feel threatened."},{"cn":"空氣忽然變得厚重。","en":"The air suddenly grew heavy."},{"cn":"不是壓力。","en":"Not pressure."},{"cn":"而是密度。","en":"But density."},{"cn":"像整座城被浸入看不見的水裡。","en":"As if the whole city had been submerged in unseen water."},{"cn":"然後，橋下的水面開始變黑。","en":"Then, beneath the bridge, the water's surface began to blacken."},{"cn":"不是墨。","en":"Not ink."},{"cn":"不是影。","en":"Not shadow."},{"cn":"而是流動的記憶。","en":"But flowing memory."},{"cn":"玄鬼低頭。","en":"Genki lowered his head."},{"cn":"水面浮現出畫面。","en":"Images rose on the water's surface."},{"cn":"不是倒影。","en":"Not reflections."},{"cn":"而是過去。","en":"But the past."},{"cn":"無數次夜行。","en":"Countless Parades."},{"cn":"無數次他走在最前面。","en":"Countless times he had walked at the front."},{"cn":"無數次人類指名、尖叫、咒罵。","en":"Countless times humans had named, screamed, cursed."},{"cn":"每一次，他都完成流程。","en":"Every time, he had completed the rite."},{"cn":"水面翻動。","en":"The water's surface churned."},{"cn":"畫面變化。","en":"The images changed."},{"cn":"如果沒有夜行——","en":"If there were no Parade —"},{"cn":"火災失控。","en":"fires would rage out of control."},{"cn":"暴動蔓延。","en":"Riots would spread."},{"cn":"指控彼此。","en":"People would accuse one another."},{"cn":"人類互相撕裂。","en":"Humans would tear each other apart."},{"cn":"沒有容器的惡，會尋找最近的血肉。","en":"Evil with no vessel would seek out the nearest flesh and blood."},{"cn":"碧吉顫聲說：","en":"Aokichi said in a trembling voice:"},{"cn":"「那是……如果沒有我們？」","en":"\"That is… if there were no us?\""},{"cn":"白蓮的眼神沉了。","en":"Byakuren's gaze deepened."},{"cn":"「不是如果。」","en":"\"Not if.\""},{"cn":"她說。","en":"she said."},{"cn":"「是可能。」","en":"\"Possibility.\""},{"cn":"水面忽然裂開。","en":"The water's surface suddenly split open."},{"cn":"黑影從水中站起。","en":"A black shadow rose up out of the water."},{"cn":"不是炎馬的形體。","en":"Not Enma's form."},{"cn":"不是任何妖怪。","en":"Not any yokai."},{"cn":"是一道沒有輪廓的巨大陰影。","en":"It was a vast shadow with no outline."},{"cn":"沒有眼。","en":"No eyes."},{"cn":"沒有口。","en":"No mouth."},{"cn":"只有聲音。","en":"Only a voice."},{"cn":"那聲音不是在耳邊。","en":"That voice was not beside his ear."},{"cn":"是在骨頭裡。","en":"It was inside his bones."},{"cn":"——你是秩序的一部分。","en":"——You are part of the order."},{"cn":"玄鬼站穩。","en":"Genki stood firm."},{"cn":"——你拒絕角色。","en":"——You refuse your role."},{"cn":"——你破壞平衡。","en":"——You break the balance."},{"cn":"玄鬼沒有回答。","en":"Genki did not answer."},{"cn":"——若無夜行，人將自相殘殺。","en":"——Without the Parade, humans will destroy each other."},{"cn":"——若無鬼，惡將無形。","en":"——Without the oni, evil will have no shape."},{"cn":"水面翻騰。","en":"The water's surface roiled."},{"cn":"城市的未來在水中閃動。","en":"The city's future flickered on the water."},{"cn":"孩子哭喊。","en":"A child cried out."},{"cn":"男人揮刀。","en":"A man swung a blade."},{"cn":"女人被指名。","en":"A woman was named."},{"cn":"沒有鬼。","en":"No oni."},{"cn":"卻更殘酷。","en":"And yet crueler."},{"cn":"碧吉低聲說：","en":"Aokichi said in a low voice:"},{"cn":"「它說的……不全是假。」","en":"\"What it says… isn't all false.\""},{"cn":"黑縁牙關緊咬。","en":"Kuroberi clenched his jaw."},{"cn":"綾女低下頭。","en":"Ayame bowed her head."},{"cn":"白蓮沒有否認。","en":"Byakuren did not deny it."},{"cn":"玄鬼向前一步。","en":"Genki stepped forward."},{"cn":"水沒過腳踝。","en":"The water rose over his ankles."},{"cn":"冰冷刺骨。","en":"Cold to the bone."},{"cn":"「你不是神。」他說。","en":"\"You are not a god.\" he said."},{"cn":"陰影沉默了一瞬。","en":"The shadow was silent for a moment."},{"cn":"——我是結果。","en":"——I am a result."},{"cn":"——我是人類選擇的形狀。","en":"——I am the shape of what humans have chosen."},{"cn":"玄鬼的胸口微微收緊。","en":"Genki's chest tightened slightly."},{"cn":"這不是敵人。","en":"This was not an enemy."},{"cn":"這是結論。","en":"This was a conclusion."},{"cn":"夜行不是暴力。","en":"The Parade was not violence."},{"cn":"它是妥協。","en":"It was compromise."},{"cn":"是人類與妖怪之間達成的默契：","en":"It was the tacit understanding reached between humans and yokai:"},{"cn":"把惡交給鬼，","en":"hand evil over to the oni,"},{"cn":"讓人類維持體面。","en":"and let humans keep their dignity."},{"cn":"——你要奪走出口。","en":"——You would take away the outlet."},{"cn":"——你要讓人直面自己。","en":"——You would make people face themselves."},{"cn":"——你知道那會帶來什麼？","en":"——Do you know what that will bring?"},{"cn":"畫面再次翻動。","en":"The images churned again."},{"cn":"不是混亂。","en":"Not chaos."},{"cn":"而是空。","en":"But emptiness."},{"cn":"沒有夜行。","en":"No Parade."},{"cn":"沒有妖怪。","en":"No yokai."},{"cn":"沒有恐懼的容器。","en":"No vessel for fear."},{"cn":"只剩沉默的城市。","en":"Only a silent city remained."},{"cn":"而玄鬼站在空城之中。","en":"And Genki stood in the midst of the empty city."},{"cn":"獨自一人。","en":"Alone."},{"cn":"——你將最後留下。","en":"——You will be the last one left."},{"cn":"那句話不是威脅。","en":"That was not a threat."},{"cn":"是推演。","en":"It was a deduction."},{"cn":"玄鬼的手握緊。","en":"Genki's hand clenched."},{"cn":"「若必須有人留下。」","en":"\"If someone must remain.\""},{"cn":"他說。","en":"he said."},{"cn":"「那是我。」","en":"\"Let it be me.\""},{"cn":"水面忽然炸開。","en":"The water's surface suddenly burst open."},{"cn":"陰影向他壓來。","en":"The shadow pressed toward him."},{"cn":"不是攻擊。","en":"Not an attack."},{"cn":"是融合。","en":"A fusion."},{"cn":"它要證明——","en":"It meant to prove —"},{"cn":"玄鬼仍屬於它。","en":"that Genki still belonged to it."},{"cn":"黑縁驚叫。","en":"Kuroberi cried out."},{"cn":"碧吉想衝出。","en":"Aokichi tried to rush forward."},{"cn":"白蓮抬手，卻沒有出手。","en":"Byakuren raised her hand, but did not strike."},{"cn":"這一刻不能被打斷。","en":"This moment could not be interrupted."},{"cn":"陰影包裹玄鬼。","en":"The shadow enveloped Genki."},{"cn":"畫面湧入。","en":"Images poured in."},{"cn":"無數次夜行的重量。","en":"The weight of countless Parades."},{"cn":"無數次承擔的記憶。","en":"The memory of countless bearings."},{"cn":"無數次人類說：","en":"Countless times humans had said:"},{"cn":"「鬼本來就該如此。」","en":"\"That's simply how an oni ought to be.\""},{"cn":"他的膝蓋微微彎曲。","en":"His knees bent slightly."},{"cn":"不是因為打擊。","en":"Not from a blow."},{"cn":"而是重量。","en":"But from the weight."},{"cn":"——你無法切割自己。","en":"——You cannot cut yourself away."},{"cn":"——你由恐懼塑成。","en":"——You were shaped by fear."},{"cn":"玄鬼閉上眼。","en":"Genki closed his eyes."},{"cn":"他沒有反抗。","en":"He did not resist."},{"cn":"他只是站著。","en":"He only stood."},{"cn":"任由那些聲音穿過。","en":"Letting those voices pass through him."},{"cn":"他忽然明白——","en":"He suddenly understood —"},{"cn":"夜行不是外在之物。","en":"the Parade was not something outside him."},{"cn":"它也在他體內。","en":"It was inside him too."},{"cn":"他若否定夜行，","en":"If he denied the Parade,"},{"cn":"便是否定自己。","en":"he denied himself."},{"cn":"他若消滅規律，","en":"If he destroyed the pattern,"},{"cn":"也會消滅自身。","en":"he would also destroy himself."},{"cn":"這不是戰鬥。","en":"This was not a battle."},{"cn":"是自我分離。","en":"It was a separation of self."},{"cn":"白蓮的聲音很輕。","en":"Byakuren's voice was very light."},{"cn":"「修行第七條。」","en":"\"The Seventh Precept.\""},{"cn":"「不否認過去。」","en":"\"Do not deny the past.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼睜開眼。","en":"Genki opened his eyes."},{"cn":"他沒有推開陰影。","en":"He did not push the shadow away."},{"cn":"他只是說：","en":"He only said:"},{"cn":"「你是結果。」","en":"\"You are a result.\""},{"cn":"「但不是唯一的結果。」","en":"\"But not the only result.\""},{"cn":"陰影停滯。","en":"The shadow stilled."},{"cn":"玄鬼繼續：","en":"Genki went on:"},{"cn":"「人類選擇過你。」","en":"\"Humans have chosen you before.\""},{"cn":"「但他們也可以選擇別的。」","en":"\"But they can choose otherwise.\""},{"cn":"水面震盪。","en":"The water's surface shuddered."},{"cn":"——別的形狀？","en":"——A different shape?"},{"cn":"「承認。」","en":"\"Acknowledgment.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼說。","en":"Genki said."},{"cn":"「不是怪罪。」","en":"\"Not blame.\""},{"cn":"陰影開始鬆動。","en":"The shadow began to loosen."},{"cn":"不是崩解。","en":"Not collapse."},{"cn":"而是動搖。","en":"But waver."},{"cn":"——那意味著減少。","en":"——That means diminishment."},{"cn":"——那意味著消失。","en":"——That means disappearance."},{"cn":"玄鬼沒有否認。","en":"Genki did not deny it."},{"cn":"「是。」","en":"\"Yes.\""},{"cn":"水面安靜下來。","en":"The water's surface grew quiet."},{"cn":"陰影沒有完全退去。","en":"The shadow did not fully retreat."},{"cn":"它只是重新沉入水底。","en":"It only sank back beneath the water."},{"cn":"最後一句聲音低低響起：","en":"One last voice sounded low:"},{"cn":"——若你失敗。","en":"——If you fail."},{"cn":"——我將更重。","en":"——I will grow heavier still."},{"cn":"水面恢復平靜。","en":"The water's surface returned to calm."},{"cn":"橋上安靜得只剩呼吸。","en":"On the bridge, nothing remained but breathing."},{"cn":"碧吉衝出來扶住玄鬼。","en":"Aokichi rushed out to steady Genki."},{"cn":"「你還在嗎？」","en":"\"Are you still there?\""},{"cn":"玄鬼站穩。","en":"Genki stood firm."},{"cn":"「在。」","en":"\"I am.\""},{"cn":"黑縁低聲說：","en":"Kuroberi said in a low voice:"},{"cn":"「它承認你了。」","en":"\"It has acknowledged you.\""},{"cn":"白蓮看著他。","en":"Byakuren looked at him."},{"cn":"「不。」","en":"\"No.\""},{"cn":"她說。","en":"she said."},{"cn":"「它開始計算你。」","en":"\"It has begun to calculate you.\""},{"cn":"夜行沒有消失。","en":"The Parade had not vanished."},{"cn":"但它第一次與玄鬼對話。","en":"But for the first time, it had spoken with Genki."},{"cn":"不是透過王。","en":"Not through a king."},{"cn":"不是透過秩序。","en":"Not through the order."},{"cn":"而是直接。","en":"But directly."},{"cn":"遠方，百鬼夜行的步伐再次響起。","en":"Far off, the tread of the Night Parade of a Hundred Demons sounded again."},{"cn":"這一次——","en":"This time —"},{"cn":"沉重。","en":"heavy."},{"cn":"卻不再完全一致。","en":"But no longer entirely of one accord."},{"cn":"（第十章完）","en":"(End of Chapter 10)"},{"cn":"第一部｜百鬼夜行","en":"Part One — The Night Parade"}]},{"id":"ch11","n":11,"title_cn":"第十一章｜有人必須留下","title_en":"Chapter 11 — Someone Must Remain","lines":[{"cn":"夜行這一次沒有隱藏。","en":"This time the Parade did not hide."},{"cn":"它從城門之外推進。","en":"It advanced from beyond the city gates."},{"cn":"整齊。","en":"Orderly."},{"cn":"沉重。","en":"Heavy."},{"cn":"毫不猶豫。","en":"Without hesitation."},{"cn":"像一場宣告。","en":"Like a declaration."},{"cn":"江戶的犬忽然同時吠叫。","en":"The dogs of Edo suddenly barked all at once."},{"cn":"燈火一盞盞熄滅。","en":"Lanterns went out, one by one."},{"cn":"這不是日常流程。","en":"This was not the ordinary course."},{"cn":"這是回應。","en":"This was a response."},{"cn":"白嶺沒有再觀察。","en":"Hakurei no longer merely watched."},{"cn":"炎馬沒有再沉默。","en":"Enma no longer stayed silent."},{"cn":"規律決定加重。","en":"The order had decided to press harder."},{"cn":"橋上，玄鬼已經站好。","en":"On the bridge, Genki was already standing ready."},{"cn":"碧吉在他左側。","en":"Aokichi was at his left."},{"cn":"綾女在他右側。","en":"Ayame was at his right."},{"cn":"黑縁伏在屋脊。","en":"Kuroberi crouched on the roof ridge."},{"cn":"白蓮站在最後。","en":"Byakuren stood at the rear."},{"cn":"夜行逼近。","en":"The Parade drew near."},{"cn":"這一次，不是由某位王領隊。","en":"This time, no single king led it."},{"cn":"而是所有重量同時前壓。","en":"Instead, the whole weight pressed forward at once."},{"cn":"火焰、影子、獸形、怨氣、哭聲——","en":"Flame, shadow, beast-shape, grievance, weeping —"},{"cn":"不是個體。","en":"not individuals."},{"cn":"是歷史。","en":"History itself."},{"cn":"玄鬼能感覺到。","en":"Genki could feel it."},{"cn":"這不是針對某一人。","en":"This was not aimed at any one person."},{"cn":"而是規律在問：","en":"It was the order itself asking:"},{"cn":"你要改變我們？","en":"you would change us?"},{"cn":"那麼承受全部。","en":"Then bear it all."},{"cn":"第一波壓力落下。","en":"The first wave of pressure fell."},{"cn":"不是打擊。","en":"Not a blow."},{"cn":"是恐懼同時升起。","en":"Fear rising all at once."},{"cn":"城中數百戶人家，","en":"In hundreds of households across the city,"},{"cn":"同時想起自己曾經推給鬼的事。","en":"people remembered, all together, what they had once pushed onto the oni."},{"cn":"嫉妒。","en":"Envy."},{"cn":"謊言。","en":"Lies."},{"cn":"怨恨。","en":"Resentment."},{"cn":"背叛。","en":"Betrayal."},{"cn":"夜行把它們帶出來。","en":"The Parade drew them out."},{"cn":"碧吉雙腿發軟。","en":"Aokichi's legs went weak."},{"cn":"「這太多了……」","en":"\"This is too much…\""},{"cn":"綾女捂住胸口。","en":"Ayame pressed a hand to her chest."},{"cn":"黑縁幾乎站不穩。","en":"Kuroberi could barely stand."},{"cn":"白蓮低聲說：","en":"Byakuren said in a low voice:"},{"cn":"「它在證明——」","en":"\"It is trying to prove —\""},{"cn":"「沒有容器，人會崩。」","en":"\"that without a vessel, people will break.\""},{"cn":"炎馬從隊伍中走出。","en":"Enma stepped out from the column."},{"cn":"他沒有笑。","en":"He was not smiling."},{"cn":"「玄鬼。」","en":"\"Genki.\""},{"cn":"「你說承認。」","en":"\"You spoke of acknowledgment.\""},{"cn":"「現在讓他們承認。」","en":"\"Now let them acknowledge it.\""},{"cn":"城中開始騷動。","en":"Unrest stirred through the city."},{"cn":"有人哭。","en":"Some wept."},{"cn":"有人喊。","en":"Some cried out."},{"cn":"有人互相指責。","en":"Some turned on one another with accusations."},{"cn":"恐懼不再集中。","en":"Fear no longer stayed gathered."},{"cn":"它四散。","en":"It scattered."},{"cn":"這是夜行給出的對照。","en":"This was the contrast the Parade offered."},{"cn":"玄鬼站在風暴中央。","en":"Genki stood at the center of the storm."},{"cn":"如果他現在出手。","en":"If he acted now."},{"cn":"吞下。","en":"Swallowed it down."},{"cn":"一切會恢復。","en":"Everything would be restored."},{"cn":"如果他不動。","en":"If he did not move."},{"cn":"人類會短暫失序。","en":"Humans would fall briefly into disorder."},{"cn":"他閉上眼。","en":"He closed his eyes."},{"cn":"不是為了拒絕。","en":"Not to refuse."},{"cn":"而是為了選擇。","en":"But to choose."},{"cn":"「白蓮。」","en":"\"Byakuren.\""},{"cn":"他低聲說。","en":"he said quietly."},{"cn":"「現在。」","en":"\"Now.\""},{"cn":"白蓮抬起手。","en":"Byakuren raised her hand."},{"cn":"她不是對抗夜行。","en":"She was not fighting the Parade."},{"cn":"她只是輕聲說：","en":"She only said, softly:"},{"cn":"「承認，不是爆發。」","en":"\"Acknowledgment is not eruption.\""},{"cn":"她的聲音不大。","en":"Her voice was not loud."},{"cn":"卻像一道細線，","en":"Yet it was like a thin thread,"},{"cn":"穿過城中每一戶。","en":"passing through every household in the city."},{"cn":"不是強迫。","en":"Not forcing."},{"cn":"只是提醒。","en":"Only reminding."},{"cn":"——你可以看見。","en":"——You may see it."},{"cn":"——你可以承認。","en":"——You may acknowledge it."},{"cn":"恐懼沒有立刻消失。","en":"The fear did not vanish at once."},{"cn":"但有人停下來。","en":"But some people stopped."},{"cn":"一個父親放下手中的棍子。","en":"A father set down the stick in his hand."},{"cn":"一個女人停止咒罵。","en":"A woman stopped cursing."},{"cn":"一個少年低下頭。","en":"A young man lowered his head."},{"cn":"不是全部。","en":"Not everyone."},{"cn":"卻是開始。","en":"But a beginning."},{"cn":"夜行的重量忽然出現微小空隙。","en":"The Parade's weight suddenly showed a small gap."},{"cn":"炎馬瞳孔微縮。","en":"Enma's pupils narrowed slightly."},{"cn":"白嶺在遠處凝視。","en":"Hakurei watched intently from afar."},{"cn":"規律第一次出現缺口。","en":"For the first time, the order showed a fissure."},{"cn":"就在此時——","en":"And just then —"},{"cn":"綾女忽然倒下。","en":"Ayame suddenly collapsed."},{"cn":"她的身體發出淡淡的光。","en":"Her body gave off a faint light."},{"cn":"不是紫。","en":"Not violet."},{"cn":"不是怨。","en":"Not resentment."},{"cn":"是金色。","en":"It was gold."},{"cn":"非常細微。","en":"Very faint."},{"cn":"像晨光第一縷。","en":"Like the first thread of dawn light."},{"cn":"碧吉驚叫。","en":"Aokichi cried out."},{"cn":"「她怎麼了？！」","en":"\"What's happening to her?!\""},{"cn":"白蓮的呼吸停了一瞬。","en":"Byakuren's breath caught for an instant."},{"cn":"「她沒有再把怨當作自己。」","en":"\"She no longer takes resentment as herself.\""},{"cn":"綾女的身體開始變得透明。","en":"Ayame's body began to turn translucent."},{"cn":"不是消失。","en":"Not vanishing."},{"cn":"是褪去重量。","en":"But shedding its weight."},{"cn":"她看向玄鬼。","en":"She looked toward Genki."},{"cn":"沒有悲傷。","en":"No sorrow."},{"cn":"只有平靜。","en":"Only calm."},{"cn":"「原來……」","en":"\"So this is it…\""},{"cn":"她輕聲說，","en":"she said softly,"},{"cn":"「不需要證明。」","en":"\"there was no need to prove anything.\""},{"cn":"金色光芒在她周圍擴散。","en":"The golden light spread out around her."},{"cn":"夜行的壓力無法再觸及她。","en":"The Parade's pressure could no longer touch her."},{"cn":"炎馬第一次真正沉默。","en":"For the first time, Enma fell truly silent."},{"cn":"白嶺的目光變得銳利。","en":"Hakurei's gaze sharpened."},{"cn":"這不是破壞。","en":"This was not destruction."},{"cn":"這是脫離。","en":"This was release."},{"cn":"綾女站起。","en":"Ayame rose to her feet."},{"cn":"腳下沒有影子。","en":"No shadow lay beneath her."},{"cn":"她回頭看玄鬼。","en":"She turned back to look at Genki."},{"cn":"「謝謝。」","en":"\"Thank you.\""},{"cn":"光芒升起。","en":"The light rose."},{"cn":"沒有爆炸。","en":"No explosion."},{"cn":"沒有聲響。","en":"No sound."},{"cn":"只有一種極靜的溫柔。","en":"Only a gentleness of utter stillness."},{"cn":"然後——","en":"Then —"},{"cn":"她不見了。","en":"she was gone."},{"cn":"不是被吞噬。","en":"Not consumed."},{"cn":"不是被斬斷。","en":"Not severed."},{"cn":"而是離開。","en":"But departed."},{"cn":"白蓮低聲念出那個詞：","en":"Byakuren spoke the word softly:"},{"cn":"「金寂。」","en":"\"Golden Stillness.\""},{"cn":"夜行忽然震動。","en":"The Parade suddenly shuddered."},{"cn":"不是因為失去一個妖怪。","en":"Not because it had lost one yokai."},{"cn":"而是因為——","en":"But because —"},{"cn":"它的總量，減少了。","en":"its total weight had diminished."},{"cn":"炎馬抬頭看向天空。","en":"Enma raised his head to the sky."},{"cn":"「原來如此。」","en":"\"So this is how it is.\""},{"cn":"白嶺的聲音從遠處傳來。","en":"Hakurei's voice carried from afar."},{"cn":"「第一個。」","en":"\"The first one.\""},{"cn":"碧吉跪在地上，眼淚止不住。","en":"Aokichi knelt on the ground, tears streaming without end."},{"cn":"「她不是死了吧？」","en":"\"She isn't dead, is she?\""},{"cn":"玄鬼搖頭。","en":"Genki shook his head."},{"cn":"「不是。」","en":"\"No.\""},{"cn":"他的聲音低。","en":"His voice was low."},{"cn":"卻穩。","en":"But steady."},{"cn":"夜行的壓力逐漸退去。","en":"The Parade's pressure gradually withdrew."},{"cn":"不是失敗。","en":"Not defeat."},{"cn":"是重新計算。","en":"A recalculation."},{"cn":"炎馬看著玄鬼。","en":"Enma looked at Genki."},{"cn":"「你真的要走到底？」","en":"\"Will you truly see this through to the end?\""},{"cn":"玄鬼回答：","en":"Genki answered:"},{"cn":"「是。」","en":"\"Yes.\""},{"cn":"炎馬沒有再阻止。","en":"Enma did not try to stop him again."},{"cn":"他轉身。","en":"He turned away."},{"cn":"夜行後退。","en":"The Parade drew back."},{"cn":"規律沒有崩。","en":"The order had not broken."},{"cn":"卻被撬開一塊。","en":"But a piece had been pried loose."},{"cn":"橋上只剩幾人。","en":"Only a few remained on the bridge."},{"cn":"黑縁低聲說：","en":"Kuroberi said in a low voice:"},{"cn":"「真的會消失。」","en":"\"She really can disappear.\""},{"cn":"白蓮看著玄鬼。","en":"Byakuren looked at Genki."},{"cn":"「有人必須留下。」","en":"\"Someone must remain.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼望向夜色。","en":"Genki gazed out into the night."},{"cn":"「我知道。」","en":"\"I know.\""},{"cn":"遠處的夜行，比以往更沉。","en":"The Parade in the distance was heavier than ever before."},{"cn":"但也比以往更少。","en":"But also, for the first time, fewer."},{"cn":"（第十一章完）","en":"(End of Chapter 11)"},{"cn":"第一部｜百鬼夜行","en":"Part One — The Night Parade"}]},{"id":"ch12","n":12,"title_cn":"第十二章｜最後的承擔","title_en":"Chapter 12 — The Last Bearing","lines":[{"cn":"綾女離開之後，江戶變得異常安靜。","en":"After Ayame left, Edo turned strangely quiet."},{"cn":"不是平靜。","en":"Not calm."},{"cn":"而是一種不習慣的空。","en":"An unaccustomed emptiness."},{"cn":"夜行後退了。","en":"The Night Parade had withdrawn."},{"cn":"但沒有消失。","en":"But it had not vanished."},{"cn":"炎馬沒有再出聲。","en":"Enma had not spoken again."},{"cn":"白嶺沒有再宣告。","en":"Hakurei had not proclaimed again."},{"cn":"規律沒有立即反撲。","en":"Order had not struck back at once."},{"cn":"這種沉默，比壓境更讓人不安。","en":"This silence was more unsettling than any advance."},{"cn":"三日。","en":"Three days."},{"cn":"整整三日，沒有夜行。","en":"Three full days, and no Night Parade."},{"cn":"江戶城第一次在夜裡沒有潮水般的腳步。","en":"For the first time, Edo's nights held no tidelike tread."},{"cn":"人們睡得更淺。","en":"People slept more lightly."},{"cn":"因為少了某種熟悉的重量。","en":"Because a certain familiar weight was missing."},{"cn":"恐懼沒有被帶走。","en":"The fear had not been carried off."},{"cn":"卻也沒有爆發。","en":"But it had not broken out either."},{"cn":"它在城中流動。","en":"It moved through the city."},{"cn":"像一條還沒找到出口的河。","en":"Like a river that had not yet found its outlet."},{"cn":"碧吉的傷好了些。","en":"Aokichi's wound had healed a little."},{"cn":"但他變得沉默。","en":"But he had grown quiet."},{"cn":"「她真的到那裡了嗎？」他問。","en":"\"Did she really reach it?\" he asked."},{"cn":"白蓮點頭。","en":"Byakuren nodded."},{"cn":"「無垢界。」","en":"\"The Immaculate Realm.\""},{"cn":"黑縁低聲說：","en":"Kuroberi said low:"},{"cn":"「那聽起來不像消失。」","en":"\"That doesn't sound like vanishing.\""},{"cn":"白蓮回答：","en":"Byakuren answered:"},{"cn":"「不是消失。」","en":"\"Not vanishing.\""},{"cn":"「是褪去。」","en":"\"Fading.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼坐在橋邊，看著水面。","en":"Genki sat by the bridge, watching the water."},{"cn":"他知道——","en":"He knew —"},{"cn":"夜行正在計算。","en":"the Night Parade was calculating."},{"cn":"綾女的離開不是意外。","en":"Ayame's leaving was no accident."},{"cn":"那是一個證明。","en":"It was a proof."},{"cn":"證明修行可以減少重量。","en":"Proof that the Practice could lessen the weight."},{"cn":"而重量一旦減少，","en":"And once the weight lessened,"},{"cn":"夜行就會變得不穩。","en":"the Night Parade would grow unstable."},{"cn":"第四夜。","en":"The fourth night."},{"cn":"風起。","en":"Wind rose."},{"cn":"不是冷。","en":"Not cold."},{"cn":"是空。","en":"Empty."},{"cn":"遠方傳來腳步。","en":"Footsteps came from far off."},{"cn":"卻不是潮水。","en":"But not like a tide."},{"cn":"是整齊、沉穩、緩慢。","en":"Orderly, steady, slow."},{"cn":"炎馬走在最前。","en":"Enma walked at the front."},{"cn":"白嶺在其側。","en":"Hakurei at his side."},{"cn":"義牙隨後。","en":"Giga behind."},{"cn":"烏嶽在空中。","en":"Ugaku in the air."},{"cn":"不是壓境。","en":"Not an advance."},{"cn":"是會面。","en":"A meeting."},{"cn":"玄鬼站起。","en":"Genki stood."},{"cn":"碧吉下意識靠近他。","en":"Aokichi drew close to him without thinking."},{"cn":"黑縁伏低。","en":"Kuroberi crouched low."},{"cn":"白蓮沒有後退。","en":"Byakuren did not step back."},{"cn":"炎馬停在橋前。","en":"Enma stopped before the bridge."},{"cn":"他看著玄鬼。","en":"He looked at Genki."},{"cn":"沒有敵意。","en":"No hostility."},{"cn":"沒有怒。","en":"No anger."},{"cn":"「我們討論過。」","en":"\"We have discussed it.\""},{"cn":"他說。","en":"he said."},{"cn":"這句話很重。","en":"The words carried weight."},{"cn":"代表夜行不是單一意志。","en":"They meant the Night Parade was not a single will."},{"cn":"白嶺接著說：","en":"Hakurei went on:"},{"cn":"「若修行成立。」","en":"\"If the Practice holds.\""},{"cn":"「夜行將逐年減少。」","en":"\"The Night Parade will shrink, year by year.\""},{"cn":"義牙握緊拳。","en":"Giga clenched his fist."},{"cn":"「而我們，將逐一離開。」","en":"\"And we — will leave, one by one.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼沒有打斷。","en":"Genki did not interrupt."},{"cn":"炎馬看著他。","en":"Enma looked at him."},{"cn":"「你願意最後一個走。」","en":"\"You are willing to be the last to go.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼點頭。","en":"Genki nodded."},{"cn":"「是。」","en":"\"Yes.\""},{"cn":"炎馬沉默片刻。","en":"Enma fell silent a moment."},{"cn":"「那你可知最後意味著什麼？」","en":"\"Then do you know what last means?\""},{"cn":"玄鬼沒有回避。","en":"Genki did not look away."},{"cn":"「所有剩餘的重量。」","en":"\"All the remaining weight.\""},{"cn":"白嶺微微點頭。","en":"Hakurei nodded slightly."},{"cn":"「以及——」","en":"\"And —\""},{"cn":"「人類最後一次，會將全部指向你。」","en":"\"The last time, humanity will point everything at you.\""},{"cn":"空氣忽然變得更冷。","en":"The air suddenly grew colder."},{"cn":"碧吉顫聲問：","en":"Aokichi asked, voice trembling:"},{"cn":"「全部？」","en":"\"Everything?\""},{"cn":"義牙低聲說：","en":"Giga said low:"},{"cn":"「當鬼只剩一個。」","en":"\"When only one oni is left.\""},{"cn":"「那個鬼會成為一切。」","en":"\"That oni will become everything.\""},{"cn":"所有嫉妒。","en":"All the envy."},{"cn":"所有謊言。","en":"All the lies."},{"cn":"所有不願承認的事。","en":"All the things no one will admit."},{"cn":"都會指向他。","en":"Will all point at him."},{"cn":"玄鬼沒有退。","en":"Genki did not retreat."},{"cn":"「我知道。」","en":"\"I know.\""},{"cn":"炎馬看著他很久。","en":"Enma looked at him a long while."},{"cn":"「你不是王。」","en":"\"You are not a king.\""},{"cn":"他說。","en":"he said."},{"cn":"「卻選擇了王的結局。」","en":"\"Yet you have chosen a king's ending.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼回答：","en":"Genki answered:"},{"cn":"「我不是王。」","en":"\"I am not a king.\""},{"cn":"「我只是留下。」","en":"\"I am only staying.\""},{"cn":"這句話，讓義牙第一次垂下目光。","en":"At these words, Giga lowered his eyes for the first time."},{"cn":"白嶺最後開口：","en":"Hakurei spoke last:"},{"cn":"「我們不阻止。」","en":"\"We will not stop you.\""},{"cn":"「但我們不會幫。」","en":"\"But we will not help.\""},{"cn":"這不是威脅。","en":"This was not a threat."},{"cn":"是規則。","en":"It was a rule."},{"cn":"夜行不能自毀。","en":"The Night Parade could not destroy itself."},{"cn":"必須由人類減少。","en":"It had to be lessened by humans."},{"cn":"必須由妖怪褪去。","en":"It had to fade through the yokai."},{"cn":"玄鬼點頭。","en":"Genki nodded."},{"cn":"炎馬轉身。","en":"Enma turned."},{"cn":"「那就開始。」","en":"\"Then let it begin.\""},{"cn":"夜行沒有壓境。","en":"The Night Parade did not advance."},{"cn":"它只是重新啟動。","en":"It only began again."},{"cn":"但這一次——","en":"But this time —"},{"cn":"重量減少了一絲。","en":"the weight had lessened by a thread."},{"cn":"接下來的日子，開始變化。","en":"In the days that followed, things began to change."},{"cn":"不是劇烈。","en":"Not sharply."},{"cn":"是細微。","en":"Finely."},{"cn":"有人在怒時停下。","en":"Some people stopped in the middle of their anger."},{"cn":"有人在怪罪時猶豫。","en":"Some hesitated before laying blame."},{"cn":"不是全部。","en":"Not everyone."},{"cn":"但越來越多。","en":"But more and more."},{"cn":"每一次有人承認，","en":"Every time someone admitted,"},{"cn":"夜行就輕一分。","en":"the Night Parade grew one part lighter."},{"cn":"而每一次承認，","en":"And every time someone admitted,"},{"cn":"玄鬼的肩，就重一分。","en":"Genki's shoulders grew one part heavier."},{"cn":"因為剩餘的，","en":"Because what remained"},{"cn":"都落在他身上。","en":"fell all upon him."},{"cn":"一夜。","en":"One night."},{"cn":"橋上。","en":"On the bridge."},{"cn":"玄鬼忽然跪下。","en":"Genki suddenly dropped to his knees."},{"cn":"不是被攻擊。","en":"Not from attack."},{"cn":"是重量。","en":"From weight."},{"cn":"碧吉驚慌。","en":"Aokichi panicked."},{"cn":"「你怎麼了？」","en":"\"What's wrong?\""},{"cn":"玄鬼的呼吸沉重。","en":"Genki's breath came heavy."},{"cn":"「它們在集中。」","en":"\"They are gathering.\""},{"cn":"黑縁瞳孔收縮。","en":"Kuroberi's pupils contracted."},{"cn":"遠方，人類最後一次大規模恐懼爆發。","en":"Far off, humanity's fear broke out one last time, in full."},{"cn":"流言四起。","en":"Rumors rose on every side."},{"cn":"「所有不幸，都是那隻鬼。」","en":"\"All the misfortune — it's that oni.\""},{"cn":"「只剩他了。」","en":"\"He's the only one left.\""},{"cn":"「殺了他，一切會好。」","en":"\"Kill him, and all will be well.\""},{"cn":"最後的指名。","en":"The last Naming."},{"cn":"終於來了。","en":"It had come at last."},{"cn":"玄鬼站起。","en":"Genki stood."},{"cn":"「這是最後一夜。」","en":"\"This is the last night.\""},{"cn":"白蓮的聲音很輕。","en":"Byakuren's voice was very light."},{"cn":"「修行第八條。」","en":"\"The Eighth Precept.\""},{"cn":"「不怨。」","en":"\"Do not resent.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼點頭。","en":"Genki nodded."},{"cn":"他沒有恨。","en":"He held no hatred."},{"cn":"沒有憤怒。","en":"No anger."},{"cn":"只有準備。","en":"Only readiness."},{"cn":"遠處火把亮起。","en":"Torches lit in the distance."},{"cn":"人群聚集。","en":"A crowd gathered."},{"cn":"不是夜行。","en":"Not the Night Parade."},{"cn":"是人。","en":"People."},{"cn":"當妖怪減少，","en":"When the yokai grew fewer,"},{"cn":"人會把最後的恐懼全部集中。","en":"people would gather all their last fear into one place."},{"cn":"玄鬼看著火光。","en":"Genki looked at the torchlight."},{"cn":"「我去。」","en":"\"I will go.\""},{"cn":"碧吉抓住他。","en":"Aokichi caught hold of him."},{"cn":"「那你會——」","en":"\"Then you will —\""},{"cn":"玄鬼輕輕把他的手移開。","en":"Genki gently moved his hand away."},{"cn":"「有人必須留下。」","en":"\"Someone must remain.\""},{"cn":"他走向火光。","en":"He walked toward the torchlight."},{"cn":"背影高大。","en":"His back was tall."},{"cn":"卻孤單。","en":"And alone."},{"cn":"夜色壓低。","en":"The night pressed low."},{"cn":"白蓮低聲念：","en":"Byakuren murmured:"},{"cn":"「金寂，最後一門。」","en":"\"Golden Stillness, the last gate.\""},{"cn":"火光包圍橋頭。","en":"Torchlight surrounded the bridgehead."},{"cn":"人群怒吼。","en":"The crowd roared."},{"cn":"玄鬼站在中央。","en":"Genki stood at the center."},{"cn":"沒有反擊。","en":"No striking back."},{"cn":"沒有辯解。","en":"No pleading his case."},{"cn":"火把落下。","en":"The torches fell."},{"cn":"火焰升起。","en":"Flame rose."},{"cn":"不是燃燒。","en":"It was not burning."},{"cn":"是承擔。","en":"It was bearing."},{"cn":"所有剩餘的惡，","en":"All the remaining evil,"},{"cn":"像潮水般湧向他。","en":"surged toward him like a tide."},{"cn":"他沒有吞。","en":"He did not swallow it."},{"cn":"也沒有推。","en":"Nor did he push it away."},{"cn":"他只是站著。","en":"He only stood."},{"cn":"承認它們存在。","en":"Acknowledging that it existed."},{"cn":"承認自己是最後的容器。","en":"Acknowledging that he was the last vessel."},{"cn":"火焰之中，","en":"Within the flame,"},{"cn":"他的輪廓開始變得不穩。","en":"his outline began to waver."},{"cn":"不是消散。","en":"Not dissolving."},{"cn":"而是——","en":"But —"},{"cn":"沉靜。","en":"settling still."},{"cn":"遠處，炎馬低聲說：","en":"Far off, Enma said low:"},{"cn":"「開始了。」","en":"\"It has begun.\""},{"cn":"白嶺閉上眼。","en":"Hakurei closed his eyes."},{"cn":"夜行停住。","en":"The Night Parade stopped."},{"cn":"江戶的風停止。","en":"The wind of Edo stilled."},{"cn":"火焰忽然熄滅。","en":"The flame suddenly went out."},{"cn":"不是因為水。","en":"Not because of water."},{"cn":"是因為恐懼失去形體。","en":"Because the fear had lost its shape."},{"cn":"人群愣住。","en":"The crowd stood dazed."},{"cn":"他們忽然不知道該再怪誰。","en":"They suddenly did not know whom to blame anymore."},{"cn":"橋中央。","en":"At the bridge's center."},{"cn":"玄鬼仍站著。","en":"Genki still stood."},{"cn":"卻變得極為安靜。","en":"But he had grown utterly quiet."},{"cn":"極為沉。","en":"Utterly heavy."},{"cn":"極為孤獨。","en":"Utterly alone."},{"cn":"白蓮看著他。","en":"Byakuren looked at him."},{"cn":"「還沒結束。」","en":"\"It is not over.\""},{"cn":"她低聲說。","en":"she said softly."},{"cn":"「還有最後一章。」","en":"\"There is still one chapter left.\""},{"cn":"（第十二章完）","en":"(End of Chapter 12)"},{"cn":"第一部｜百鬼夜行","en":"Part One — The Night Parade"}]},{"id":"ch13","n":13,"title_cn":"第十三章｜金寂","title_en":"Chapter 13 — Golden Stillness","lines":[{"cn":"火熄滅後，江戶沒有歡呼。","en":"After the flame went out, Edo did not cheer."},{"cn":"沒有勝利。","en":"No victory."},{"cn":"沒有慶賀。","en":"No celebration."},{"cn":"人群站在橋頭，茫然。","en":"The crowd stood at the bridgehead, lost."},{"cn":"他們本以為——","en":"They had thought —"},{"cn":"只要把最後的鬼逼出來，一切就會恢復。","en":"that once the last oni was driven out, everything would be restored."},{"cn":"可當火焰散去，","en":"But when the flame scattered,"},{"cn":"橋上只剩一個沉默的身影。","en":"only a silent figure remained on the bridge."},{"cn":"玄鬼沒有倒下。","en":"Genki had not fallen."},{"cn":"也沒有消失。","en":"Nor had he vanished."},{"cn":"他仍然站著。","en":"He still stood."},{"cn":"只是——","en":"Only —"},{"cn":"角淡了。","en":"his horns had faded."},{"cn":"紅色褪去。","en":"The red had gone out of him."},{"cn":"他的輪廓變得不像傳說裡的樣子。","en":"His outline no longer looked like the one from the legends."},{"cn":"人群看著他。","en":"The crowd looked at him."},{"cn":"第一次，沒有恐懼。","en":"For the first time, no fear."},{"cn":"只有不確定。","en":"Only uncertainty."},{"cn":"「……他還是鬼嗎？」","en":"\"…Is he still an oni?\""},{"cn":"沒有人回答。","en":"No one answered."},{"cn":"因為沒有誰真正知道鬼是什麼。","en":"Because no one truly knew what an oni was."},{"cn":"夜色壓低。","en":"The night pressed low."},{"cn":"人群慢慢散去。","en":"The crowd drifted slowly away."},{"cn":"沒有再丟石頭。","en":"No more stones thrown."},{"cn":"沒有再舉火把。","en":"No more torches raised."},{"cn":"當最後一個人離開橋頭時，","en":"When the last person left the bridgehead,"},{"cn":"江戶的夜變得異常安靜。","en":"Edo's night grew strangely quiet."},{"cn":"不是壓抑。","en":"Not oppressive."},{"cn":"而是空。","en":"Empty."},{"cn":"玄鬼站在橋中央。","en":"Genki stood at the bridge's center."},{"cn":"風穿過他。","en":"Wind passed through him."},{"cn":"像穿過山。","en":"As through a mountain."},{"cn":"碧吉顫著走上前。","en":"Aokichi walked up, trembling."},{"cn":"「你還在嗎？」","en":"\"Are you still there?\""},{"cn":"玄鬼看著他。","en":"Genki looked at him."},{"cn":"那雙眼睛裡，不再有血色的沉重。","en":"In those eyes, the blood-red weight was gone."},{"cn":"只剩極深的平靜。","en":"Only a very deep calm remained."},{"cn":"「在。」","en":"\"I am.\""},{"cn":"聲音低。","en":"His voice was low."},{"cn":"卻輕。","en":"But light."},{"cn":"黑縁站在橋邊。","en":"Kuroberi stood at the bridge's edge."},{"cn":"她想說什麼。","en":"She wanted to say something."},{"cn":"卻說不出口。","en":"But could not find the words."},{"cn":"白蓮最後走近。","en":"Byakuren was the last to approach."},{"cn":"她的目光第一次不再冷靜。","en":"For the first time, her gaze was not cool."},{"cn":"「重量如何？」","en":"\"How is the weight?\""},{"cn":"她問。","en":"she asked."},{"cn":"玄鬼沉默片刻。","en":"Genki was silent a moment."},{"cn":"「很重。」","en":"\"Heavy.\""},{"cn":"他說。","en":"he said."},{"cn":"「但不再刺。」","en":"\"But it no longer stings.\""},{"cn":"那不是承受。","en":"That was not bearing."},{"cn":"那是——","en":"That was —"},{"cn":"沉澱。","en":"settling."},{"cn":"夜行在遠方沒有再動。","en":"Far off, the Night Parade did not stir again."},{"cn":"炎馬站在城門外。","en":"Enma stood outside the city gate."},{"cn":"義牙站在他身後。","en":"Giga stood behind him."},{"cn":"白嶺在更高處。","en":"Hakurei stood higher still."},{"cn":"他們都看著橋。","en":"They all watched the bridge."},{"cn":"他們知道——","en":"They knew —"},{"cn":"此刻，夜行的總量，降到最低。","en":"that at this moment, the Night Parade's total had fallen to its lowest."},{"cn":"因為最後的指名，已經沒有回音。","en":"Because the last Naming had gone unanswered."},{"cn":"人群回家。","en":"The crowd went home."},{"cn":"有人坐在屋裡發呆。","en":"Some sat in their rooms, staring at nothing."},{"cn":"有人第一次想起自己做過的事。","en":"Some, for the first time, remembered what they themselves had done."},{"cn":"沒有鬼可怪。","en":"No oni left to blame."},{"cn":"沒有容器可丟。","en":"No vessel left to cast off into."},{"cn":"那份不安，轉成沉默。","en":"That unease turned into silence."},{"cn":"沉默，比恐懼更難受。","en":"Silence was harder to bear than fear."},{"cn":"但沉默，會慢慢生出理解。","en":"But silence would, slowly, give rise to understanding."},{"cn":"橋上。","en":"On the bridge."},{"cn":"玄鬼的身體開始發出極細微的金色光。","en":"Genki's body began to give off a faint gold light."},{"cn":"不是爆發。","en":"Not a burst."},{"cn":"是從內而外。","en":"From within, outward."},{"cn":"碧吉後退一步。","en":"Aokichi stepped back."},{"cn":"「你也要走了？」","en":"\"Are you leaving too?\""},{"cn":"玄鬼搖頭。","en":"Genki shook his head."},{"cn":"「還不到。」","en":"\"Not yet.\""},{"cn":"白蓮低聲說：","en":"Byakuren said low:"},{"cn":"「金寂不是逃離。」","en":"\"Golden Stillness is not an escape.\""},{"cn":"「是純淨。」","en":"\"It is purity.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼閉上眼。","en":"Genki closed his eyes."},{"cn":"他看見綾女離開時的光。","en":"He saw the light of Ayame's leaving."},{"cn":"那種無負的輕。","en":"That unburdened lightness."},{"cn":"他知道自己也會走向那裡。","en":"He knew he too would walk toward it."},{"cn":"但不是現在。","en":"But not now."},{"cn":"他還有最後一份重量。","en":"He still had one last weight to carry."},{"cn":"——留下。","en":"— To remain."},{"cn":"不是因為被指名。","en":"Not because he had been Named."},{"cn":"而是因為選擇。","en":"But because he chose it."},{"cn":"炎馬忽然開口。","en":"Enma suddenly spoke."},{"cn":"聲音低低傳來。","en":"His voice came low."},{"cn":"「夜行，停。」","en":"\"Night Parade — stop.\""},{"cn":"那不是命令。","en":"That was not a command."},{"cn":"是確認。","en":"It was a confirmation."},{"cn":"白嶺閉上眼。","en":"Hakurei closed his eyes."},{"cn":"「秩序重組。」","en":"\"Order, reordered.\""},{"cn":"義牙垂下頭。","en":"Giga bowed his head."},{"cn":"他第一次明白——","en":"For the first time he understood —"},{"cn":"忠誠不是盲從。","en":"loyalty was not blind obedience."},{"cn":"而是理解何時放手。","en":"It was knowing when to let go."},{"cn":"夜行沒有再啟動。","en":"The Night Parade did not start again."},{"cn":"因為已經沒有那麼多惡需要被搬運。","en":"Because there was no longer so much evil left to carry."},{"cn":"橋上只剩玄鬼。","en":"Only Genki remained on the bridge."},{"cn":"風穿過他的身體。","en":"Wind passed through his body."},{"cn":"金色光芒一點點擴散。","en":"The gold light spread, little by little."},{"cn":"不是吞噬他。","en":"It did not devour him."},{"cn":"而是洗去。","en":"It washed him clean."},{"cn":"角完全消失。","en":"His horns vanished entirely."},{"cn":"紅色完全退去。","en":"The red faded entirely away."},{"cn":"他看起來——","en":"He looked —"},{"cn":"幾乎像一個普通的人。","en":"almost like an ordinary man."},{"cn":"碧吉忽然哭了。","en":"Aokichi suddenly wept."},{"cn":"不是大聲。","en":"Not loudly."},{"cn":"只是眼淚止不住。","en":"His tears simply would not stop."},{"cn":"「你會很孤單。」","en":"\"You will be very lonely.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼輕輕笑了一下。","en":"Genki smiled gently."},{"cn":"那是第一次。","en":"It was the first time."},{"cn":"真正的笑。","en":"A true smile."},{"cn":"「不。」","en":"\"No.\""},{"cn":"他說。","en":"he said."},{"cn":"「我只是晚一點。」","en":"\"I am only a little behind.\""},{"cn":"白蓮走到他面前。","en":"Byakuren came before him."},{"cn":"「無垢界在彼岸。」","en":"\"The Immaculate Realm lies on the far shore.\""},{"cn":"她說。","en":"she said."},{"cn":"「但彼岸不在遠方。」","en":"\"But the far shore is not far away.\""},{"cn":"玄鬼望向江戶。","en":"Genki looked out over Edo."},{"cn":"燈火零星。","en":"The lamps scattered, few."},{"cn":"人聲低落。","en":"Human voices, low."},{"cn":"沒有夜行。","en":"No Night Parade."},{"cn":"沒有潮水。","en":"No tide."},{"cn":"只有風。","en":"Only wind."},{"cn":"他坐在橋上。","en":"He sat on the bridge."},{"cn":"像一座守門人。","en":"Like a gatekeeper."},{"cn":"不是守恐懼。","en":"Not guarding against fear."},{"cn":"而是守選擇。","en":"But guarding a choice."},{"cn":"時間慢慢過去。","en":"Time passed slowly."},{"cn":"一年。","en":"One year."},{"cn":"兩年。","en":"Two years."},{"cn":"夜行越來越輕。","en":"The Night Parade grew lighter and lighter."},{"cn":"炎馬離開。","en":"Enma departed."},{"cn":"義牙離開。","en":"Giga departed."},{"cn":"烏嶽離開。","en":"Ugaku departed."},{"cn":"白嶺最後一次回頭。","en":"Hakurei looked back one last time."},{"cn":"然後也消失於金色光中。","en":"Then he too vanished into gold light."},{"cn":"碧吉有一天醒來，","en":"Aokichi woke one day"},{"cn":"發現自己不再需要躲水。","en":"to find he no longer needed to hide from water."},{"cn":"黑縁在某個清晨，靜靜化作光。","en":"Kuroberi, one quiet morning, turned softly into light."},{"cn":"白蓮最後站在橋上。","en":"Byakuren stood on the bridge for the last time."},{"cn":"她看著玄鬼。","en":"She looked at Genki."},{"cn":"「快了。」","en":"\"Soon.\""},{"cn":"她說。","en":"she said."},{"cn":"玄鬼點頭。","en":"Genki nodded."},{"cn":"「嗯。」","en":"\"Mm.\""},{"cn":"她沒有說再見。","en":"She did not say goodbye."},{"cn":"因為她知道——","en":"Because she knew —"},{"cn":"那不是終點。","en":"this was not an ending."},{"cn":"金色光芒在她腳下升起。","en":"Gold light rose beneath her feet."},{"cn":"無聲。","en":"Soundless."},{"cn":"極靜。","en":"Utterly still."},{"cn":"她走入其中。","en":"She walked into it."},{"cn":"橋上只剩玄鬼。","en":"Only Genki remained on the bridge."},{"cn":"最後的鬼。","en":"The last oni."},{"cn":"最後的承擔。","en":"The last bearing."},{"cn":"最後的重量。","en":"The last weight."},{"cn":"夜色極輕。","en":"The night was very light."},{"cn":"江戶已不再需要夜行。","en":"Edo no longer needed the Night Parade."},{"cn":"人們仍會犯錯。","en":"People would still err."},{"cn":"仍會憤怒。","en":"Would still grow angry."},{"cn":"仍會說謊。","en":"Would still lie."},{"cn":"但不再第一時間怪鬼。","en":"But they no longer blamed the oni first."},{"cn":"玄鬼坐在橋上。","en":"Genki sat on the bridge."},{"cn":"風吹過。","en":"The wind blew through."},{"cn":"他閉上眼。","en":"He closed his eyes."},{"cn":"所有重量，","en":"All the weight,"},{"cn":"終於沉到底。","en":"settled at last to the bottom."},{"cn":"不是壓。","en":"Not pressing down."},{"cn":"是寂。","en":"Stillness."},{"cn":"極寂。","en":"Utter stillness."},{"cn":"純金。","en":"Pure gold."},{"cn":"金寂。","en":"Golden Stillness."},{"cn":"金色光芒從他身上慢慢浮起。","en":"Gold light rose slowly from his body."},{"cn":"沒有誰看見。","en":"No one saw it."},{"cn":"沒有誰送別。","en":"No one saw him off."},{"cn":"他站起身。","en":"He rose to his feet."},{"cn":"看了一眼江戶。","en":"Looked once at Edo."},{"cn":"不是留戀。","en":"Not longing."},{"cn":"是確認。","en":"Confirming."},{"cn":"然後——","en":"Then —"},{"cn":"光芒吞沒他的輪廓。","en":"the light swallowed his outline."},{"cn":"橋上空了。","en":"The bridge stood empty."},{"cn":"沒有鬼。","en":"No oni."},{"cn":"沒有夜行。","en":"No Night Parade."},{"cn":"只有風。","en":"Only wind."},{"cn":"而彼岸，","en":"And on the far shore,"},{"cn":"不再黑暗。","en":"darkness was no more."},{"cn":"是純金無瑕的光。","en":"It was light of flawless, pure gold."},{"cn":"（第一部 完）","en":"(End of Part One)"}]}],"archetypes":[{"cn":"重力型","en":"Gravity","key":"gravity","color":"#8b2f28","color2":"#c0453b"},{"cn":"理性型","en":"Reason","key":"reason","color":"#4f7398","color2":"#9cc0e0"},{"cn":"情緒型","en":"Emotion","key":"emotion","color":"#7d5aa6","color2":"#b992e0"},{"cn":"野性型","en":"Feral","key":"feral","color":"#c0682a","color2":"#eb9a44"},{"cn":"游離型","en":"Drifting","key":"drifting","color":"#3f8a6e","color2":"#5fb894"},{"cn":"存在型","en":"Presence","key":"presence","color":"#8f8672","color2":"#cdbfa6"},{"cn":"母性型","en":"Maternal","key":"maternal","color":"#a97b3c","color2":"#d6ab63"},{"cn":"記憶型","en":"Memory","key":"memory","color":"#5a5560","color2":"#c19240"}]};
